every little design detail until it matches the rest of your page. The result is an eye-catching YouTube channel that represents your brand and blows the competition out of the water. ",Sr=[{description:"<p>PicsArt’s free YouTube banner templates are easy to use and a great way to take your YouTube cooking channel to the next level. What’s more, you don’t have to spend any money on getting it done. When it comes to YouTube banners for your cooking channel, it’s important to capture your signature personality the way your delicious recipes do. After all, it’s the first thing fans are greeted with when they subscribe to your page. We have tons of eye-catching (and mouth-watering) YouTube banner templates — created specially for all things food— that will capture your attention and palate. We know a chef’s creative direction can change from time to time, so should you need to update any elements in your YouTube banner art, you can do so in minutes. </p>",title:"Serve up Creativity for Your YouTube Cooking Channel",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/20694932781388595461.png",imageAlt:"cookie recipes to satisfy your sweet tooth - positive cookies on a coral background ",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s YouTube banner templates are a great way to utilize all the design options available for your vlog on YouTube. With them, you don’t need a lot of time or any professional experience, so you can get it done and focus on your work. Whether your vlog is all about food, fashion, travel, beauty, sports, music, or any other topic, you will find the perfect, and free, YouTube banner template. Our designs run the gamut from bold and eye-catching to subtle and neutral to sleek and professional. Once you settle on the YouTube banner art template that speaks to your personality and aesthetic, the rest of the process is quick and painless. If you ever need to make changes to your YouTube banner, you can save all your previous designs and go back when necessary. </p>",title:"Take Your YouTube Vlog to the Next Level",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/97749538694375232506.png",imageAlt:"youtube vlog banner template for beauty and make up",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>If you’re an influencer in the fashion game, it’s especially vital for your YouTube channel to be as stylish as your head-to-toe outfits. PicsArt’s fashionable YouTube banner templates don’t disappoint. Forego paying thousands for a professional to design your YouTube channel art and do it on your own from your home. Customizing all the little design details won’t be a problem with a discerning eye. With PicsArt’s free YouTube banner templates, you’ll never have a shortage of inspiring ideas to match the chic look of your YouTube channel. Our talented in-house artists have already done all the designing, so all you have to do is choose one that you and your followers will love.  </p>",title:"Elevate Your Fashion Channel With Stylish YouTube Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/42614859202067545318.png",imageAlt:"curl your hair in 5 minutes - youtube banner template for fashion channel",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p> For those in the world of DIY tutorials — be it home decor, fashion, gardening, or beauty — customizing your YouTube banner template should come easy. Because of your creative nature, it’ll take no time for you to choose the right template for your YouTube channel, then personalize it to fit your signature look. Each YouTube banner template can be fully edited by changing the background colors and text with over 200 unique fonts. You can even add your own image and layer on as many free stickers as you want. You can also use one of PicsArt millions of <a href="/images" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="Youtube Banner Templates hypertext">high-quality #FreetoEdit images</a> to perfect YouTube DIY channel art. </p>',title:"Give Your DIY Tutorials an Equally Impressive Look",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/77313116505955917123.png",imageAlt:"diy pillows and decorative materials youtube banner template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}}],Cr="youtube_banner_templates",Rr={description:"<p>Make your YouTube channel stand out from a sea of competition with our easy-to-use YouTube banner templates.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s YouTube Banner Templates Are Spotlight-Worthy",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/71115962414492831655.png",imageAlt:"peaceful mind grateful heart - man and woman doing yoga",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},Ir=!0,Ur="template",Mr=[{imgUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/98337318983068438115.png",thumbnailUrl:"/design-templates/invitation",templateLabel:"Invitation",bgColor:"softGrey"},{imgUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/03638786483471061914.png",thumbnailUrl:"/design-templates/collage",templateLabel:"Collage",bgColor:"softOrange"},{imgUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/07932247588508911501.png",thumbnailUrl:"/youtube-banner-maker",templateLabel:"YouTube",bgColor:"softRed"},{imgUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/07660612245876059354.png",thumbnailUrl:"/design-templates/flyer",templateLabel:"Flyer",bgColor:"softPurple"},{imgUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/61043252304051932316.png",thumbnailUrl:"/design-templates/brochure",templateLabel:"Brochure",bgColor:"softOrange"},{imgUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/32562087888817688596.png",thu