que font."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Change up the positioning of specific elements."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],Un=[{description:"<p>If you’re looking for a sleek business card that conveys the ultimate professionalism, PicsArt has a ton of business card templates that are right for you. We’ve got various color schemes, designs, and fonts that will speak to the look and feel you’re going for. No matter your industry, you will find something worth showing off to potential clients and partners. Just search our library of free business card templates to get started. Once you choose the perfect template for you, then it’s time to customize it to match your personal details. But don’t worry, personalization doesn’t equal painful. With our handy editing tools, you will get the job done in a few minutes. </p>",title:"Our Professional Business Cards Mean Business",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/06262095743088579812.png",imageAlt:"web designer creative business card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>If you’re in the real state business, we’ve got endless real estate business cards that will impress your clients and potential buyers. When you’re ready to create a beautiful business card, turn to PicsArt’s free business card templates to get you started. Pick the template that you prefer, then edit the details to personalize it. Add your name, business phone number, email address, website, and any other information you would like to share with your clients. With PicsArt’s business card templates, you won’t spend hours designing something worth sharing. In just minutes, you’ll have something beautiful at your fingertips. </p>",title:"Real Estate Business Cards Will Impress Potential Buyers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/83091615628271881892.png",imageAlt:"real estate agency business card template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Business cards come in a variety of colors, sizes, and designs. It all depends on your profession and desired aesthetic. If you’re in the market for a business card that is luxurious and modern (this includes sleek black business cards), then PicsArt is the place for you. We house tons of styles: minimalist, modern, simple, photo, and creative. These business card templates are ideal for restaurant business cards, barber business cards, and beauty business cards, but can work for any industry. Black business cards are particularly cutting-edge and eye-catching, so if you want to give off edge and capture attention, that’s a good option for you.</p>",title:"Luxury Business Cards That Speak Volumes",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/07491954728869162804.png",imageAlt:"beauty and spa center business card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>If you want your business card to stand out from the rest, artistic business cards are the way to go. PicsArt has a bunch of artistic business card templates that will help you achieve the look and design you’re going for in minutes. These templates are ideal for musicians, DJs, or any creative profession. Makeup artists, designers and craftsmen can also take advantage of our artistic business card templates. Our designers have made sure to create templates that will make your business card pop. To personalize things further, you can use our one-of-a-kind tools to add your own touches.</p>",title:"Artistic Business Cards Cater to Creative Types",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/34047711078715013988.png",imageAlt:"dj creative business card template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>If you have your own business, personal business cards are right up your alley. From simple to bold, we have tons of business card templates that will work for your industry and aesthetic. Go through our free business card templates to pick the one you like, then customize it to include your name, phone number, email address, website, and anything else you’d like to include to attract potential customers and partners.</p>",title:"Personal Business Cards Are Ready for the Entrepreneur",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/90307228349104150675.png",imageAlt:"yoga teacher business card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>If you’re in the construction industry, PicsArt has endless simple and cool business card templates that will match your profession. First, pick the template that speaks to your look, then personalize it by adding your details like your name, phone number, email address, and website. With PicsArt’s business card templates, you won’t spend hours designing a business card. Within minutes, you’ll come up with a business card that you’ll be proud to share with the world.</p>",title:"Construction Business Cards Are Simple and Cool",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/10577970654952121055.png",imageAlt:"construction business card template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>With tons of business card templates, including chic black business cards, in no time you’ll be promoting yourself and your business in style. Beauticians and makeup artists will enjoy our simple business card templates that are super sleek and modern. No matter if you’re working at a salon or have your own business, you won’t spend a penny with PicsArt’s free business card templates. Personalize the details by adding your information, then add fun details like designer fonts and stickers.</p>",title:"Modern Business Cards for Beauticians and Makeup Artists",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/68321649609846993493.png",imageAlt:"neon nail art business card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"8"}}],Mn={description:"<p>Our business card templates are so easy to use — make as many as you need!</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Business Card Templates Are Polished & Professional",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/56728642919274617121.png",imageAlt:"marketing manager business card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Business Card",gtmValue:"1"}},Wn="business_card_template",Dn=!0,Fn="template",Ln=o(41),Vn=o.n(Ln),zn=function(e,t){var o={};for(var r in e)Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(e,r)&&t.indexOf(r)<0&&(o[r]=e[r]);if(null!=e&&"function"==typeof Object.getOwnPropertySymbols){var n=0;for(r=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(e);n<r.length;n++)t.indexOf(r[n])<0&&Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable.call(e,r[n])&&(o[r[n]]=e[r[n]])}return o},qn=function(e){var t=e.sectionClassName,o=void 0===t?"":t,r=e.className,n=void 0===r?"":r,a=e.title,i=e.data;zn(e,["sectionClassName","className","title","data"]);return l.a.createElement("div",{className:Vn.a.container},l.a.createElement(io,{className:o+" "+Vn.a.section},l.a.createElement("h2",{className:Vn.a.title},a),l.a.createElement("div",{className:Vn.a.pointlistContainer},i.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement("ul",{key:t+"-"+(e[0]&&e[0].index),className:n+" "+Vn.a.stepsList},e.map((function(e){return l.a.createElement("li",{className:Vn.a.stepsListItem,key:e.index},l.a.createElement("div",