na,va=aa,ka=ia,wa=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(va),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,ga({},ba,{screenName:va,isPremium:ka,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"To go along with your impressive YouTube channel, you’ll need an equally standout YouTube thumbnail to capture your audience’s attention. That’s where PicsArt comes in and helps you achieve something spectacular within minutes. With our YouTube thumbnail maker, you don’t need any professional experience or even a design background. Our thumbnail maker makes it easy for you to make a thumbnail to go along with any of your videos. How to make a thumbnail with PicsArt? Use our intuitive editing tools to customize your YouTube thumbnail in no time. Add trendy effects, bold backgrounds, fun stickers, and stylish text to make your videos pop.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:ya,screenName:va,isPremium:ka,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a YouTube Thumbnail",data:fa}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Pa=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open PicsArt’s Sticker Maker tool."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload the photo you want to turn into a sticker."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Remove its background by clicking Object or Person. "}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Tap Apply."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Tap Download to save your Thanksgiving sticker! "}]],Ea=[{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Thanksgiving stickers make the perfect companion for your social media posts. They’re a fast and free way to spice up your social feed to reflect your joyful spirit. Just add an eye-catching thankful sticker or a cute turkey sticker to any of your photos or videos and share them with your followers. From playful and cartoon-y Thanksgiving stickers to realistic and inspiring Thanksgiving stickers, you’ll discover a variety of designs and graphics to choose from. Layer as many happy Thanksgiving stickers as you wish and watch your content go from basic to festive in minutes.</p>",title:"For Social Media",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/92209418544875423060.png",imageAlt:"thanksgiving themed image of happy girls taking selfie",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Looking to create a Thanksgiving-inspired digital flyer or poster for your small business or brand? PicsArt can provide the perfect finishing touch with a large collection of happy Thanksgiving stickers. Search for the Thanksgiving sticker that speaks to your brand’s aesthetic and signature style, then layer as many as you want onto your promotional flyer or poster. You can even choose to print out your personalized creation to display it for clients and guests to admire at your event.</p>",title:"For Flyers & Posters",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/65951227157157685737.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"thanksgiving themed table with plate pumpkin and napkin with happy thanksgiving text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>When putting together a special Thanksgiving dinner or charity event, you need an equally special invitation to get the word out in style. PicsArt has all the editing tools you need to create a one-of-a-kind digital invite, like an extensive collection of Thanksgiving stickers. All it takes is a few happy Thanksgiving stickers and inspirational grateful quote stickers to turn your plain photo and video edits into something truly spectacular. For something subtle and simple, pick one or two Thanksgiving stickers. For a bolder, more eye-catching aesthetic, choose a handful of Thanksgiving stickers that coordinate with one another. The creative possibilities are endless when it comes to making a unique Thanksgiving day invitation with PicsArt.</p>",title:"For Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/38787648824550334131.png",imageAlt:"thanksgiving themed invitation template with give thanks text on it",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Did you know that you can use PicsArt’s high-quality Thanksgiving stickers as decorations to dress up your home and office for the food-filled holiday? All you have to do is print your favorite stickers out to frame them or hang them on your walls. You can also add Thanksgiving stickers to your laptop or phone case to show your festive spirit. From colorful leaves to plush pumpkins to grateful quotes and so many more creative designs, you’ll want to add them all to everything from your walls to your windows. Use fun Thanksgiving stickers and PicsArt-made edits as decorations and you’re guaranteed to stand out from a sea of typical turkey images.</p>",title:"For Decorations",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/87763247135908543936.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"thanksgiving themed table with thanksgiving themed turkey, heart and cup stickers",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Thanksgiving stickers come in all shapes, styles, and sizes. Whether you’re looking for a Thanksgiving sticker for professional or personal purposes, there is something that will speak to your specific style. Want something cutesy and playful for a casual invite? Go for funny cartoon turkey stickers. Need a Thanksgiving sticker for a professional flyer? Pick a beautiful cornucopia creation or a sticker frame featuring plush fall leaves. From simple to bold, PicsArt has a Thanksgiving sticker that will take your Thanksgiving images from simple to stunning.</p>",title:"Stickers for All Styles",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/46372418539505162972.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl with thanksgiving themed pumpkin stickers on hair",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>Looking to get extra creative for Thanksgiving? You can make your very own Thanksgiving stickers in just minutes using PicsArt’s all-in-one photo and video editor. Just use the quick & easy <a href="/sticker-maker" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="sticker-maker-tool-hypertext">Sticker Maker tool</a> to turn any photo — yes, any photo — into a sticker! All you have to do is upload the photo you want to turn into a sticker to the tool and let PicsArt do the rest. Download your new creation and start adding it to your edits for a truly customized experience.</p>',title:"Personalized Thanksgiving Stickers",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/71355451694064825183.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"happy girl in orange sweater with thanksgiving themed pumpkin, irish green hat and turkey stickers",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Make Stickers",gtmValue:"7"}}],xa={description:"<p>PicsArt’s happy Thanksgiving stickers add an instant festive flair to digital flyers, virtual invites, social posts, and more.</p>",title:"Thanksgiving Stickers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/31015715410451568916.png",imageAlt:"thanksgiving themed image of a happy girl with pumpkin sticker",bgImage:!1,lightText:!1,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"1"}},Ta="thanksgiving_stickers",Aa=!0,Na=function(){return(Na=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Oa=Pa,_a=Ea,ja=xa,Sa=Ta,Ca=Aa,Ra=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Sa),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Na({screenName:Sa,isPremium:Ca},ja,{isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Thanksgiving stickers are a quick and easy way to get into the festive mood during a season that gives thanks to family and friends, scrumptious turkey, and so much more. Anytime you want to add major fun to your Thanksgiving photos and videos, try dressing them up with PicsArt’s happy Thanksgiving stickers. They work on everything from personal to professional posts. Layer them on top of digital flyers and posters, virtual invitations, menu cards, social media posts, and more. You can even print your favorites — like turkey stickers or thankful stickers — to spotlight them on your home or office walls.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:_a,screenName:Sa,isPremium:Ca,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make Your Own Thanksgiving Stickers",data:Oa}))},Ia=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload the video you want to subtitle."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Transcribe your captions."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Easily adjust subtitles to fit your style."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download the subtitled video and share!"}]],Ua=[{description:"Add subtitles to videos easily on any browser. PicsArt’s subtitle creator allows you to quickly add, correct, and customize captions. No muss, no fuss.",title:"Seamless Editing"},{description:"PicsArt subtitle maker sets no limits when it comes to selecting fonts, their size, position, color and background. Tweak the settings to your liking and make your subtitles stand out at all times.",title:"Library of Fonts"},{description:"Not only do videos with subtitles have a wider reach, but they also accelerate click, reaction, and share rates. Up your game with PicsArt.",title:"Higher Engagement"}],Ma=[{description:"<p>Make your videos more accessible to a wider audience by adding subtitles. Think of it this way - captions act as gateways to your content for all sorts of individuals, that otherwise can’t watch your videos.. Many people consume content on the go and they never turn on the audio. Others have hearing impairments and can only watch videos that have captions. And one more thing to consider - not everyone speaks your language. Add captions to your videos in the languages of your target audience to communicate your messages much more clearly</p>",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/23114458665186717458.png",imageAlt:"man in glasses running an online course",title:"Expand Your Audience",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Subtitles to Video",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>Subtitles if used and designed well, can become an effective way to capture people’s attention. Social media is filled with video content and the ones without subtitles get 26% less CTA clicks than videos that do have subtitles. This means that if your content is promotional, it needs to have subtitles to bring you better ROI. The same applies if you just want to attract more attention to your vlogs on Youtube. Learning how to add subtitles to youtube videos with PicsArt is easy, then simply <a href="/resize-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="adjust-the-size-of-your-video-hypertext">adjust the size of your video</a> to optimize it for the platform, <a href="/add-music-to-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="add-background-music-video-hypertext">add background music</a> and share your content with the world.</p>',imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/53382064415843540247.png",imageAlt:"curly hair girl playing guitar",title:"Add Subtitles to Videos for Social Media",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Subtitles to Video",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>You can bring your tutorials or professional presentations to a whole new level by adding subtitles to them. Informative videos can be hard to follow, but you can make them much more accessible by adding captions. If you are going for a more simple slideshow, you can use PicsArt’s <a href="/slideshow-maker" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="dedicated-tool-hypertext">dedicated tool</a> for that, then simply <a href="/add-text-to-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="add-text-to-your-video-hypertext">add text to your video</a> and you’re good to go. But if you are working on something more complex and you already know how to put subtitles on a video, then PicsArt’s subtitle maker is exactly what you’re looking for. Once you have finished editing, download your presentation and share it with your colleagues.</p>',imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/79565327787166207346.png",imageAlt:"sweet crepes with raspberries and blackberries",title:"Create Tutorials With Subtitles",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Subtitles to Video",gtmValue:"4"}}],Wa="subtitles_for_video",Da={description:"<p>Easily add subtitles to videos online and make your content accessible to a wider audience.</p>",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/55927053212448459145.png",title:"Add Subtitles to Videos With Picsart",imageAlt:"packing a gift box with ropes",lightText:!1,bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Subtitles to Video",gtmValue:"1"}},Fa=!0,La=o(63),Va=o.n(La),za=function(e){var t=e.featuresData;return l.a.createElement("div",{className:Va.a.container},l.a.createElement(io,{className:Va.a.sectionContent},l.a.createElement("ul",{className:Va.a.list},t&&t.map((function(e){return l.a.createElement("li",{key:e.title,className:Va.a.featureContainer},e.title&&l.