ut did you know that most of the video content on social feeds is muted by default? In fact, more than 85% of video content on Facebook is viewed without any audio. So, to convey the message of your content, you will need to add subtitles to videos. PicsArt allows you to seamlessly add subtitles to videos online and make your content accessible to a larger audience. Simply upload your footage to our",l.a.createElement("a",{href:"/video-editor",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"video-editor-hypertext"}," video editor"),", add subtitles to your video and download your file!"),isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Ka,screenName:$a,isPremium:Za,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{dataTests:{title:"title data test",description:"description data test"},title:"Benefits",isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Ya,{featuresData:Qa,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Add Subtitles to a Video",data:Xa,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},ti=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose one of our invitation templates."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a new picture or choose one from our #FreetoEdit images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Add your own text to the template."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work and share!"}]],oi=[{description:"<p>A great way to put PicsArt’s online templates to use is for business purposes. When you need to shout your message from the social-media rooftops, these templates will make your brand stand out from a sea of competitors. Having an online sale? Need to announce a work holiday party? There are plenty of free invitation templates that will get the job done, and simultaneously impress your clients and employees alike. Pick the one that works for your theme, then customize it to speak to your brand’s voice and aesthetic.</p>",title:"Keep It Professional With Our Business Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/98619063885946995002.png",imageAlt:"couple standing with serious looks with sale text on the text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>You have the perfect theme for your birthday bash but now you need an equally pretty online invitation to get the word out to friends. With PicsArt’s free invitation templates, you can go above and beyond to set the right mood for the event. Opt to add your best selfie for extra impact, and switch up the text and font to suit your unique personal style.</p>",title:"Have All the Fun With Birthday Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/63830244075620187829.png",imageAlt:"happy mom and daughter",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Online wedding invitations are the ultimate way of going paperless and green. With all the money spent on weddings, it’s nice to cut costs wherever possible. Impress guests by creating a personalized invitation on PicsArt that speaks to your unique love story. There are endless romantic templates that will surely capture your heart.</p>",title:"Get Ultra Romantic With Beautiful Wedding Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/52969010180157995588.png",imageAlt:"happy bride and groom image on a pink frame",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Before the wedding comes the fun stuff, like the bridal shower and bachelorette party. It’s a time to gather with your closest friends to celebrate your love story, while feasting and having the best time. With PicsArt’s bridal-themed templates, you can create sweet online invitations to share with your invitees. Be sure to pull in a fun photo of yourself or a beautiful portrait of you and your fiance. </p>",title:"Help the Bride With Bridal Shower and Bachelorette Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/02025873236445611024.png",imageAlt:"party girls happily posing and drinking in club",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>If you’re opting to have an engagement party before you get married, you can also use PicsArt’s beautiful online invitation templates to send invites to your family and friends. There are also tons of romantic fonts that will match the blissful theme.</p>",title:"Keep the Love Alive With Engagement Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/87922453171772987432.png",imageAlt:"happy bride and groom in fields photo collage on a blue background",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>For themed parties for a holiday, like Valentine’s Day, Christmas, or prom, PicsArt features timely templates you can use to get people excited. Themed invitations around holidays are constantly updated to keep up with the latest consumer trends.</p>",title:"Celebrate Themed Holidays With Our Party Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/05915206886286867755.png",imageAlt:"happy family decorating christmas tree photo on a postcard for santa",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>Graduation parties are one of the most exciting times since it marks the end of an era. To match the excitement, you can find graduation-themed templates to get the word out about your big day. Even if you’re not having an official party, you can pick a template to announce the news of your graduation to family members.</p>",title:"Show You’re Proud With Graduation Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/35224669809205315825.png",imageAlt:"happy girl with a hat on a colorful background with 2020 graduate text on photo",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"8"}}],ri={description:"<p>Make your own invitations for all the special events in your life by easily designing invitations online.</p>",title:"Invitation Templates to Get the Word Out in Style",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/10365791358933725477.png",imageAlt:"happy smiling girl laying on bad with my birthday text on the photo",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},ni="invitation_templates",ai=!0,ii="template",si=function(){return(si=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},li=ti,ci=oi,ui=ri,pi=ni,di=ai,mi=ii,hi=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;It(pi,mi);var r="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,si({},ui,{landingCategory:mi,screenName:pi,isPremium:di,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Custom invitations are essential in getting the word out about upcoming special events and important announcements, so why not make them look beautiful while you’re at it? With PicsArt’s free invitation maker templates — all completely personalizable and editable — you’ll have fun designing an invite that speaks to your style and impresses guests. From birthdays to anniversaries to weddings to graduations to store openings, there is a stylish template that will speak to your theme. With a few quick custom editing steps, you’ll behold an invitation you’re proud to promote.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:pi,isPremium:di,isAmp:o,tag:"tags/invitation"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:mi,productData:ci,screenName:pi,isPremium:di,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create an Invitation",data:li}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:r,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},isAmp:o,productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,key:t})}))))},gi=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose Instagram Story template. "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload your own image or use one of our stock photos. "}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Customize your content by adding effects, stickers, text, and more. "},{index:4,pointDescription:"Once you’re done, download your finished content and share it. "}]],fi="PicsArt’s Instagram story maker is a fast and fun way to create one-of-a-kind content that will make you stand out from a sea of competition. Create Instagram stories that fit your signature aesthetic in mere minutes and without spending a single penny. Customize as many stories as you wish with our Instagram story editor by adding cool effects, fun stickers, text with stylish fonts, bold backgrounds, and way more. PicsArt’s exclusive tools and features will ensure that you create something truly spotlight-worthy. With the help of our impressive IG story maker, your Instagram stories will definitely make your followers take notice.",yi=[{description:"<p>When it comes to making amazing Instagram stories to spotlight your brand, you don’t need to spend a single penny with PicsArt. We have done the hard work of creating a fast and easy Instagram story maker that you can use completely for free. That means you can partake in all the creativity minus the headache. All you have to do is dream up an Instagram story design that speaks to your aesthetic and customize every little detail using our Instagram story maker. </p>",title:"Create Stunning Instagram Story Designs for Free",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/38104549987231388685.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl with white pants posing - sugar song cover",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Whether or not you know exactly what you’d like to create for your next Instagram story, you can turn to PicsArt’s Instagram story maker to help you fully personalize the experience. You can change the background of your story, add any effect you like, layer on stickers upon stickers, speak your mind with text using our stylish fonts, and do so much more. The only limit is your time and creativity. You can choose to keep your Instagram story nice and simple or you can go all out by working with all of our impressive tools. The creative world is truly your oyster when it comes to PicsArt’s Instagram story maker. </p>",title:"Our Instagram Story Maker is Completely Customizable",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/00496857288495432057.png",imageAlt:"young man profile photo with tattoo and red summer hat on a pink background with bees",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Sometimes you have your own photo you’d like to use for your Instagram story while other times you’d prefer to use stock photos. Lucky for you, PicsArt houses an extensive collection of high-quality stock photos that you can use for your Instagram stories. Search for the topic that speaks to your content (we’ve got a ton), then pull it into the Instagram story maker to start the personalizing process. There are no limits to how many stock photos you can use so let your imagination run wild.  </p>",title:"Access Free Stock Photos With Our Instagram Story Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/65399593156465437918.png",imageAlt:"image of a retro car in a nude color",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>The last thing you want when it comes to your social media content is to do what’s already been done. Standing out is the name of the game when it comes to Instagram stories and PicsArt’s IG story maker can help with that. When using our Instagram story creator, you're sure to create something that is truly one-of-a-kind. That’s because you’ll be using our exclusive tools and features to up your content game according to your look and aesthetic. Add effects, stickers, backgrounds, shapes, fonts, and way more to ensure that your brand’s Instagram stories pop and stick in the mind of your followers.  </p>",title:"Make Your Brand Pop With PicsArt’s Instagram Story Creator",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/05727217300301121312.png",imageAlt:"modern music plate image on a bright pink background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>If you’re an influencer, blogger, vlogger, or any other online personality with a big following, you know that it can be hard to keep your content fresh and fun when you’re posting so often. PicsArt’s Instagram story maker and Instagram story templates are perfect for influencers who need novel design ideas and don’t have a ton of time. Our talented designers have done the work of creating stunning templates for you to use at any time. Just plug in your own photos and logo into the Instagram story template of your choice and post away. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Instagram Story Maker Is Perfect for Influencers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/26389618139888236032.png",imageAlt:"photo collage of a yong happy girl taking selfie and posing as an instagram story",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>If you’re strapped for time but still want to create unique Instagram stories, look no further than PicsArt’s handy Instagram story templates. Our talented designers have created beautiful, ready-to-use templates just for you. You can use them to plug in your own photos and texts to make something even more special. What’s great about Instagram story templates is that we’ve done most of the creative work for you so you don’t have to worry about changing things up. If you do want to switch things up and personalize your Instagram story template, we won’t stop you. </p>",title:"Use Instagram Story Templates for a Fast and Fun Approach",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/54846633299967566251.png",imageAlt:"instagram story template of a curly hair girl image on a trendy background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"7"}}],bi={description:"<p>Create unique Instagram stories using our beautifully designed templates, then customize each template to fit your signature aesthetic with a handy Instagram story editor. </p>",title:"Up Your Social Game With PicsArt’s Instagram Story Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/56365374410775101751.png",imageAlt:"fashionable girl walking under the rain with yellow boots and yellow umbrella",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Story",gtmValue:"1"}},vi="instagram_story_maker",ki=!0,wi=function(){return(wi=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Pi=gi,Ei=fi,xi=yi,Ti=bi,Ai=vi,Ni=ki,Oi=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Ai),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,wi({},Ti,{screenName:Ai,isPremium:Ni,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"},isAmp:o})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},Ei),isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:xi,screenName:Ai,isPremium:Ni,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Make Instagram Stories With PicsArt",data:Pi,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},_i=[[{index:1,pointDescription:'Select Template Editor from our <a href="/create/chooser?redirect=editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="editing-tools-hypertext">Editing Tools</a>'},{index:2,pointDescription:"Type “Valentine” in the search bar at the top and press enter."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Select the template you want for your Valentine’s day card."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Upload your own image or stickers to personalize your card."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Click Download to save your Valentine’s day card."}]],ji=[{description:"<p>If you’re reading this close to Valentine’s day then you must be running out of time and every second counts. Which is why you’ll be glad to know that with PicsArt’s Valentine’s day card maker you’d be able to take your card from your imagination to reality in a snap. With truly a vast library of stock images and editing assets you’ll find exactly what you’re looking for and more without even breaking a sweat. PicsArt is designed from the ground up to render the entire editing process to be as smooth as possible. So that your experience from a blank canvas all the way to the final product is as quick and enjoyable as possible.</p>",title:"Make Your Own Valentine’s Day Card in Seconds",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/52364043958824548567.png",imageAlt:"couple holding hands on a valentine's day card with heart stickers",buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Valentine’s Card",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>We’ve all been there. You plan your approach every step of the way, down to the finest detail. What you’re about to say, the expression on your face, you visualize their response, over and over. The only thing we don’t plan for is how it all could go wrong. In the end, these things rarely go the way you plan them out to be. So, when you make your own Valentine’s card with PicsArt, you’ll remove every margin for error from this equation. And with that out of the way, you can completely focus on delivering the perfect card by expressing yourself to your heart’s content. <a href="/create/chooser?redirect=editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="picsArts-online-photo-editor-hypertext">PicsArt’s online photo editor</a> is equipped with all the tools you need to deliver the perfect romantic message to your significant other. With tons of unique fonts and premium stickers you can design a Valentine’s day card that will make sure the recipient knows exactly where your heart lies.</p>',title:"Release Your Inner Romantic and Set the Perfect Mood for the Evening",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/99726558277739117222.png",imageAlt:"happy couple on a valentine's day card with hearts stickers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Valentine’s Card",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Nothing says true love more than a Valentine’s day gift that both looks and feels personal to the two of you. A cutesy inside joke, a memorable quote, a snapshot of a memory. This year, you can make your own Valentine’s card extra special by making sure it’s completely personalized and unique to the recipient. Doing this with PicsArt’s Valentine’s day card maker is extremely easy. By creating your own stickers and uploading your own photos, you can make sure your card is both unique and speaks deep from your heart. Showing your Valentine’s day recipient that you remember and care about the small personal details that you two share, is the single best way of making them feel both valued and appreciated on this special romantic day.</p>",title:"Design from the Heart and Add the Perfect Personal Touch to Your Valentine’s Day Card",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/52927172339436161808.png",imageAlt:"happy couple on a valentine's day card with colorful flowers and hearts stickers",buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Valentine’s Card ",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>So you don’t know how to make a Valentine’s day card but you still want to provide your partner the beautiful card they deserve? Have no worries, cause we got you covered. Not only PicsArt’s online photo editor is extremely pick up and use, the real kicker is the Valentine’s day card templates that are waiting for you. The closer Valentine’s day gets, the more Valentine’s day templates you’ll see in your PicsArt feed. You can quickly Remix or Replay any of the edits you find appealing and make them work for you by adding a little of your personal touch. On top of that, once the Valentine’s day season is here, you’ll find tons of unique Valentine’s day templates designed by our very own artists and designers that you can quickly and easily grab, customize some of the elements, make your own Valentine’s card, and ultimately stun your partner with maximum romantic effect.</p>",title:"Easily Create Your Professional Looking Valentine’s Day Card With PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/03394527036871528369.png",imageAlt:"smiling girl with a white dog on a valentine's card with pink and red heart stickers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}}],Si={description:"<p>Design a Valentine’s day card and surprise your significant other with PicsArt’s Valentine’s day card maker.</p>",title:"Make a Valentine’s Card For That Special Someone",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/86997323325940342930.png",imageAlt:"lovely couple on a valentine's day card with heart and kiss stickers",buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Valentine’s Card",gtmValue:"1"}},Ci="valentines_card_maker",Ri="It’s always a special treat when the most romantic day of the year comes knocking on our doors. A fancy dinner, a romantic movie, flowers, gifts, the list goes on. But sometimes delivering the whole nine yards isn’t an option. So for whatever reason if you do find yourself empty handed, know that turning your Valentine’s day from 0 to 100 is always right at your fingertips with PicsArt. You don’t have to do the impossible to impress and show your loved one that you care, it’s the thought that counts. That’s why with PicsArt you can always make your own Valentine’s card and impress your partner with a tiny thoughtful gift that will feel personal to you both and make sure the romantic mood is lit for the rest of the day. So don’t waste any time and design a Valentine’s day card with PicsArt now.",Ii=!0,Ui=function(){return(Ui=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Mi=_i,Wi=ji,Di=Si,Fi=Ci,Li=Ri,Vi=Ii,zi=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Fi),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Ui({},Di,{dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"},screenName:Fi,isPremium:Vi,isAmp:o})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:Li,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Wi,screenName:Fi,isPremium:Vi,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Make a Valentine’s Day Card",data:Mi,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},qi=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose the Facebook Cover template."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload your own image to the template or use a stock photo."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Customize your content by adding effects, stickers, text, and more. "},{index:4,pointDescription:"Once you’re done, download your finished content and post it. "}]],Bi=[{description:"<p>Creating the perfect Facebook cover doesn’t have to cost you a fortune. With PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker, you can make as many cover designs as you wish without spending a single penny. That way you can focus on the creative aspects of finding and customizing a stunning Facebook cover that will attract your audience as soon as they visit your page. </p>",title:"Make the Perfect Facebook Cover for Free",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/61060222819012221633.png",imageAlt:"abstract image of a pink door in the forest that opens to sea - the other side of me",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>You can always count on PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker to help you completely customize your Facebook cover to make your page stand out from the rest. Create something truly one-of-a-kind using our fast and easy editing tools. Add cool effects, fun stickers, text using stylish fonts, bold backgrounds, and more. Not sure exactly what you want your Facebook cover to look like? Let our impressive and easy-to-use tools inspire you. You can get as creative as you want with your Facebook cover art and there is no limit to how many cover designs you can create with PicsArt. </p>",title:"This Facebook Cover Maker is Fully Customizable",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/52765073976856195348.png",imageAlt:"aim high dream big work hard",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>One of the best things about PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker is that you don’t have to spend hours scratching your head about formatting and sizing. We’ve done the hard math for you so all you have to do is focus on the creative aspects, like picking the Facebook cover art design that speaks to you and personalizing the details to fit your needs. When you work with PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker, rest assured that any Facebook cover art you design will fit your page’s sizing needs. </p>",title:"Don’t Worry About Sizing With Our Facebook Cover Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/03787125398791241606.png",imageAlt:"Image of a woman's shoulder on a plants shadow background",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>When it comes to PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker, you can choose to use your own images or you can access our awesome stock photos for free. We feature an extensive collection of high-quality stock photos that you can use for any of your Facebook cover designs. Search from a ton of topics that are available in our collection, then select the images that work for you. There is no limit to how many free stock photos you can use with PicsArt so choose as many as you need and start customizing the details to fit your specific design needs. </p>",title:"Try Free Stock Photos Always at Your Fingertips",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/22043898703597376888.png",imageAlt:"image of colorful fishes and skyscrapers under the sea",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Should you ever be low on time, you can turn to PicsArt’s Facebook cover templates to help you achieve something unique in no time. Our talented designers have created stunning, ready-to-use templates just for you. All you have to do is pick the design and colors that speak to you, then plug in your own photos, logos, and add text using our stylish fonts. Within minutes, you’ll have yourself a beautiful Facebook cover art that looks like it took hours to make. </p>",title:"Use Facebook Cover Templates for a Quick & Easy Approach",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/32837671933138273449.png",imageAlt:"boy playing an electric guitar in a music studio",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>When it comes to your brand, the last thing you want is to fit in with the competition. To create the most unique, eye-catching Facebook cover that will make your brand pop and capture your audience’s attention, turn to PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker. Even with zero professional experience, you can create something truly special using our fast and easy editing tools. Layer on cool effects, fun stickers, bold backgrounds, text with stylish fonts, and so much more. If you’re not sure what look you’re going for, no problem, just play around with our impressive tools and features and you’ll gain lots of inspiration. </p>",title:"Level up Your Brand With PicsArt’s Facebook Cover Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/51566559106888936698.png",imageAlt:"photo collage of interior details on a light pink background",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"7"}}],Hi="facebook_cover_maker",Yi={description:"<p>PicsArt’s fast and easy-to-use Facebook cover photo creator gives you the best tools to create a Facebook cover that speaks to your unique style and aesthetic. </p>",title:"Customize Your Page With PicsArt’s Facebook Cover Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/84705972510778860364.png",imageAlt:"facebook cover template of a trendy coffee image",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Facebook Cover",gtmValue:"1"}},Gi=!0,Xi=function(){return(Xi=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Qi=qi,Ki=Bi,$i=Yi,Ji=Hi,Zi=Gi,es=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Ji),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Xi({},$i,{screenName:Ji,isPremium:Zi,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"With PicsArt’s Facebook cover maker, it’s beyond easy — and fun — to create the perfect Facebook cover that speaks to your brand’s signature aesthetic. Anytime you need to create a fresh Facebook cover photo to turn up the volume on your page, just turn to PicsArt to help you take the guessing game out of the process. It will only take a few minutes. Begin by picking the Facebook cover template that works for your needs, then customize any of its details with our quick and easy editing tools to give your content a one-of-a-kind look. Add cool effects, bold colors, stylish fonts, and more. No professional experience required!")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Ki,screenName:Ji,isPremium:Zi,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a Facebook Cover",data:Qi}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},ts=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open PicsArt’s Template Editor. You can do this either online or in the app!"},{index:2,pointDescription:"Type “Halloween” in the search bar to see all the available templates."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Choose the template you like by clicking on it."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Edit the details of the template using the editing tools."},{index:5,pointDescription:"When done, click Download to save your work to your desktop. In-app, tap Next then Save to download to your phone."}]],os=[{description:'<p>PicsArt has many festive and ready-made <a class="inline-link" href="/create/editor" target="_blank" data-test="halloween-templates">Halloween templates</a> that you can use to make Halloween party posters, merchandise, pumpkin carvings, home decor, and social media digital designs. To see all the template designs available, just search for “Halloween” in the <a class="inline-link" href="/create/editor" target="_blank" data-test="template-editor">Template Editor</a> and pick the one that works best for your project. Download the template as is or use PicsArt’s quick & easy editing tools to customize away! You’ll have a final project done in just minutes!</p>',title:"PicsArt’s Halloween Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/59037025863243924043.png",imageAlt:"halloween template of a girl image with large wings",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"10"}}],rs=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open PicsArt’s Template Editor. "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a photo or choose from one of PicsArt’s #FreeToEdit images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Customize the image by using the editing tools."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Click Download to save your finished template to your desktop."}]],ns=[{description:"<p>Are you hosting this year’s Halloween haunted house bash or pumpkin carving contest? Then you’ll need a perfectly spooky invite to get the word out to your friends. PicsArt’s free Halloween templates (the pumpkin carving templates are a favorite!) will help you make the perfect invitation in mere minutes.</p>",title:"Halloween Party Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/73912419326766328032.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween scary party invitation template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>A scary movie marathon is a fun way to get into the festive Halloween vibe. Whether you’ll be screening “Scream,” “The Shining,” or “The Blair Witch Project,” invite your friends over by sending them a scary social media flyer using one of PicsArt’s unique Halloween templates.</p>",title:"Halloween Movie Marathon Poster",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/83707873346161394531.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween spooky night movie marathon poster",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Print banners, stickers, and other festive Halloween decals for the inside and outside of your home to show off your festive spirit with the neighborhood. From bats and spiders to ghouls and skulls, there’s no shortage of inspiration to be had with PicsArt.</p>",title:"Halloween Home Decorations",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/16222645788977765496.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween zombie party home decorations",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>If you’re looking to create a Halloween-inspired flyer to post online or to print out, turn to PicsArt’s Halloween flyer templates. Simply edit the details of the template to reflect your project or event and you’re set.</p>",title:"Halloween Flyers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/70503237036301121941.jpg",imageAlt:"happy halloween trick or treat flyers",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s high-quality Halloween templates and stickers make great Halloween merchandise. Show off your spirit by wearing your creation on your sleeve (or bag)! Trick or treating? Make your own custom bags to hold your candy haul!</p>",title:"Bags & Shirts",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/46085427648647316321.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween bags and shirts - get your spooky face on",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>Want ideas for your pumpkin carving project? Search <a class="inline-link" href="/images/" target="_blank" data-test="picsArts-freeToEdit-images">PicsArt’s FreeToEdit images</a> for unique pumpkin carving designs that you can turn into carving printables. Show off your awesome creation on social media using one of PicsArt’s Halloween templates.</p>',title:"Pumpkin Carvings",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/88625947799568638219.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween trick or treat pumpkin carving",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>Less tricks, more treats! A goodie bag filled with candy and slimy creatures is the perfect way to send off your guests! Print Halloween-inspired stickers to attach to your goodie bags for that festive touch.</p>",title:"Halloween Goodie Bags",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/99359064879812852534.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween goodie bags",bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:"<p>If you plan on posting about Halloween on your social media accounts, turn to PicsArt’s easy-to-use templates for unique design ideas. The best part is that you can choose a template according to the specific social channel: Instagram (story, square, portrait), Facebook (post or cover), and Pinterest.</p>",title:"Digital Design",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/15946467664934969911.jpg",imageAlt:"halloween spooky and scary make up",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"9"}}],as={description:"<p>PicsArt’s free Halloween templates are quick, spooky, and frighteningly easy to use.</p>",title:"Halloween Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/88696359387606366917.png",imageAlt:"girl image with halloween scary background and skulls",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=halloween",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},is="halloween_templates",ss=!0,ls="template",cs=function(){return(cs=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},us=ts,ps=os,ds=rs,ms=ns,hs=as,gs=is,fs=ss,ys=ls,bs=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;It(gs,ys);var r="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,cs({landingCategory:ys,screenName:gs,isPremium:fs},hs,{isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Halloween is arguably one of the most exciting — and scariest! — holidays of the year. Between over-the-top costumes, way-too-much candy, spooky home decor, pumpkin carving festivities, and haunted houses, there’s no shortage of fun to be had. When it comes to party invitations, posters, drink menus, party games, social media posts, and any other Halloween needs you may have, PicsArt’s Halloween templates are perfect and super easy to use!")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:gs,isPremium:fs,tag:"tags/halloween",isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:ys,productData:ps,screenName:gs,isPremium:fs,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"Follow these step-by-step instructions to customize your Halloween template",data:us,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{title:"Ideas for Halloween Templates",isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:ys,productData:ms,screenName:gs,isPremium:fs,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Create Your Own Halloween Template",data:ds,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{title:"Related Articles",isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{slidesToShow:r,autoplaySpeed:2e3,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,isAmp:o,key:t})}))))},vs=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Select your YouTube Banner template."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Edit the template details to customize it. Add your own photo, stickers, overlays, and text. "}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Download your YouTube banner."}]],ks=[{description:"<p>If you don’t want to create something from scratch, you can also use one of our handy YouTube banner templates to help your YouTube cover stand out from a sea of competitors. We have hundreds of eye-catching designs — all created by our talented in-house artists — that will speak to your brand’s one-of-a-kind aesthetic and personality. From bold to subtle and everything in between, the hardest part will be picking just one.</p>",title:"Create YouTube Banners in No Time",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/01838902314943572334.png",imageAlt:"traveling with retro cars text on a youtube banner template with a retro car photo on it",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>The biggest reason to forgo paying a professional to design your YouTube channel art is that you can save thousands of dollars. By creating your YouTube banner yourself (from the comfort of your own office or home), you have full control over every single design aspect, from start to finish. With so many easy-to-use tools at your fingertips, you won’t regret using PicsArt’s free YouTube Banner Maker.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s YouTube Banners Are Free",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/58369971236522897985.png",imageAlt:"make up course with lee text on a youtube pink banner with a girl's lips",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>The design possibilities are endless when it comes to PicsArt’s YouTube Banner Maker. You can turn up the volume by layering on stickers, shapes, and effects that will completely transform the look of your YouTube cover art. The idea is to make your YouTube cover stand out from the rest, so there is no time limit or creative barrier to what you can achieve with PicsArt’s banner maker.</p>",title:"Easily Customize Banners to Your Liking",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/53356411857809450491.png",imageAlt:"classic jazz beats on a youtube banner template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Getting your brand name or tagline across in a succinct — and stunning — way is highly important when it comes to your YouTube banner art. With over 200 unique fonts to choose from, you won’t have a shortage of ways to get your message across in style. Once you’re done picking the font that speaks to your aesthetic, you can change the color, outline, opacity, and shadow to get an even more personalized look. </p>",title:"Choose From Hundreds of Unique Fonts",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/71134801994599915370.png",imageAlt:"electro mood text on a youtube banner ",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Should you need to go back and make edits to your YouTube banner art, it’s totally possible and easy with PicsArt’s YouTube Banner Maker. This option is good for when you would like to update your look to give your YouTube channel a fresh makeover.</p>",title:"Go Back and Edit Later",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/92604657596947755721.png",imageAlt:"green eye girl with a serious look on a youtube banner temlate",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>Don\'t have an image handy? If you need ideas for images to use as the backdrop of your YouTube channel banner art, don’t worry, we have a plethora of ideas for you. Just browse through our community and partner contributed <a class="inline-link" target="_blank" href="/images" data-test="FreetoEdit-images-hypertext">#FreetoEdit images</a> to select the photo that will capture your YouTube audience. If you need photos for commercial use, we have a filter that lets you easily search for YouTube banner images that fit your needs.</p>',title:"Hundreds of thousands of photos",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/62974145008781769678.png",imageAlt:"best course for chefs text on a youtube banner template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>Congratulations! You’re all done with the fun part of making an epic cover art using our free YouTube Banner Maker. Now for the less fun (but equally important) part of saving it so all your hard work won’t go to waste. Download your YouTube banner art as JPEG or PNG, choose the image quality, then save it to your PicsArt profile or computer. All that’s left to do is to show it off on your YouTube channel!</p>",title:"Download or Share",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/33007485597040537745.png",imageAlt:"art text on a youtube banner template with colorful pencils on it",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"8"}}],ws={description:"<p>Our YouTube Banner Maker is free, fun, and an easy way to get creative with your channel.</p>",title:"Use PicsArt’s YouTube Banner Maker to Stand Out",imageUrl:"https://pastatic.picsart.com/47293881522988730169.png",imageAlt:"get moving text on a youtube banner template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=youtube_cover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Banner",gtmValue:"1"}},Ps="youtube_banner_maker",Es=!0,xs=function(){return(xs=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Ts=vs,As=ks,Ns=ws,Os=Ps,_s=Es,js=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;It(Os);var r="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,xs({},Ns,{screenName:Os,isPremium:_s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s YouTube Banner Maker is the only tool you need to take your YouTube channel to standout levels — and it’s possible without a penny or any professional help. Create a YouTube banner in next to no time (and for free!) using PicsArt’s handy, easy-to-use YouTube Banner Maker. Customize the look to fit your style with bold backgrounds, fun stickers, and hundreds of unique fonts — and never mess with the size. In mere minutes, you can create a YouTube banner that speaks to your personal style. Design your YouTube banner to fit your channel’s theme, whether it’s about food, fashion, travel, beauty, pets, or beyond.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:Os,isPremium:_s,isAmp:o,desktopCardsCount:8,tag:"tags/cover"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:As,screenName:Os,isPremium:_s,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a YouTube Banner",data:Ts}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:r,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},isAmp:o,productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,key:t})}))))},Ss=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Select Template Editor from our Editing Tools. "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Type “Christmas” in the search bar at the top, and press enter. "},{index:3,pointDescription:"Select the design you want for your Christmas card. "}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Customize your card with more images and stickers. "},{index:5,pointDescription:"Click Download to save your Christmas card. "}]],Cs="How to Make a Christmas Card",Rs="The holiday season is almost here and it’s the perfect time of the year to get in touch with all our loved ones and send them our most heartfelt messages and latest news with some precious Christmas cards. For the holiday season be the first in your family to make your own Christmas cards.You can design a Christmas card with ease using PicsArt and achieve results that both look and feel perfect for Christmas. So if you’re looking for something special and new to share with your family and friends, then you need to create custom Christmas cards and turn it into a brand new Christmas tradition.",Is=[{description:"<p>It doesn’t matter whether you’re a veteran of the editing game or just starting out, you don’t have to worry about your Christmas card design one bit. PicsArt is the true definition of easy-to-learn, hard to master, but we don’t stop there. When we say you can design a Christmas card in seconds, that’s not a marketing quip. Even if you have no idea on how to start, the second the holiday season’s underway, you’ll find a ton of premade Christmas themed templates for you to make your own Christmas cards. You can simply select one of our custom-made templates, add a simple text or sticker on top to make it truly yours, and share it with your loved ones. It’s that easy. </p>",title:"A Huge Library of Amazing Christmas Templates",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/29551669606917455848.png",imageAlt:"happy holidays card templates",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates"}},{description:"<p>One of the best things about the fast approaching holiday season is the sheer excitement you get from all the anticipation, the high expectations, and the overall positivity that’s so prevalent during this season. Sometimes when the going gets tough, we can’t help but wish to start the holiday season and wash away all the negativity around us. PicsArt’s Christmas card maker lets you bring the start of the cheery holiday season into your own hands. Simply design a Christmas card, and send your season’s greetings to all your friends, family, and loved ones. There’s nothing sweeter than being the one who officially marks the start of everyone’s favorite holiday season. </p>",title:"The Perfect Season’s Greetings Cards to Kickstart the Christmas Mood",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/96878530501447322965.png",imageAlt:"a very merry christmas red card template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a card"}},{description:"<p>When you dip your toes into making Christmas cards, you want to hit the ground running. As soon as you learn the basics on how to make one, it’s time to quickly take them to the next level by taking full advantage of PicsArt’s robust editing platform and easily make your own Christmas cards. Nothing makes the recipients happier than seeing the amount of effort and thought you’ve put into making your own Christmas card. With PicsArt, by using even the simplest of editing techniques you can transform your Christmas cards from generic to special. </p>",title:"Easily Customize and Make Unique Christmas Cards With PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/85705596142787782112.png",imageAlt:"Warm wishes christmas card template with a red teapot and red glowes",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a card"}},{description:"<p>Nothing comes close to the familiar intimacy of a close-knit family in the living room, next to a well-lit fireplace, with Christmas stockings right above it, filled with gifts. Sometimes capturing the perfect moment isn’t easy, or it simply doesn’t happen for one reason or another, but you shouldn’t give up on your grand Christmas card ideas. No matter the mood or setting you’re going for, we guarantee you’ll be able to recreate it using our endless library of high-res stock images. With millions of free-to-edit images at your fingertips you have infinite possibilities to create the perfect Christmas card.  </p>",title:"Design Stunning Christmas Cards Using Our Free Images ",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/32746216729508165313.png",imageAlt:"merry christmas card template with christmas tree, presents and sofa",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a card"}},{description:"<p>Whether you’re out of Christmas card ideas or don’t think you have the necessary editing know-how. Come the holiday season, your PicsArt home feed will be filled to the brim with countless Christmas themed edits that you can simply Replay or Remix to create your own. With Replay you can find other users’ Christmas card edits and recreate them on your own photos step-by-step with excellent results. By making full use of the PicsArt community’s Replays, free-to-edit images, custom Christmas stickers, on top of all the unique custom Christmas templates that you’ll receive from PicsArt’s professional designers, means that you’ll never run short of ready-made editing assets. With PicsArt, your dream Christmas card is only a few clicks away. </p>",title:"Creating Christmas Cards Was Never This Easy",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/17900779941477403296.png",imageAlt:"ho ho ho christmas card template with snowy firs",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Card"}}],Us={description:"<p>Create your own personalized Christmas cards for the upcoming holiday with PicsArt’s Christmas card maker. </p>",title:"Design a Christmas Card in Seconds",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/78154401563397957382.png",imageAlt:"creative merry christmas card template with sparkling stars",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Card"}},Ms="christmas_card_maker",Ws=!0,Ds=function(){return(Ds=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Fs=Ss,Ls=Cs,Vs=Rs,zs=Is,qs=Us,Bs=Ms,Hs=Ws,Ys=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Bs),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Ds({},qs,{screenName:Bs,isPremium:Hs,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"},isAmp:o})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},Vs),isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:zs,screenName:Bs,isPremium:Hs,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:Ls,data:Fs,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Gs=[[{index:1,pointDescription:'Select Twitter Cover from the <a href="/create" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="twitter-create-hypertext"> “Create a design” </a> section.'},{index:2,pointDescription:"You can select a premade template on the left side or design from scratch on the empty canvas."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Click Download to save your brand new Twitter header."}]],Xs="How to Make a Twitter Header",Qs="If you’re trying to shoot your shot making it on Twitter then you have to make sure your profile looks up to snuff. Whenever you post something that all of a sudden goes viral out of nowhere, whether that’s an unexpected comment, video, or a thread, one thing’s for sure, people will definitely click on your profile to check the backstory behind the viral post. It’s up to you to make sure the first impression you leave on your visitors is the best it could be. And the first thing people will see when visiting your profile, before they read your bio, your pinned post, or your profile picture, is the massive banner at the very top. In order to make your Twitter profile as appealing and eye-catching as possible from the very get-go you need yourself a reliable Twitter banner maker to get the job done. And if you’re not sure where to start and don’t know how to make Twitter headers, then you’re in the right place.",Ks=[{description:"<p>Finding the perfect tool for the job can mean many different things. Some people look for ease-of-use, some search for deep and tons of functionality, some are simply interested in software that’s free. Here at PicsArt we define the perfect tool by the one that delivers all three above at the same time. PicsArt’s Twitter banner maker is exactly that, incredibly easy-to-use, tons of functionality and tools provided by the editor in case you need any, and completely free. With this tool you’ll be able to make Twitter headers in no time. You need absolutely zero graphic design know-how to make full use of our Twitter cover photo maker, you can take your design from scratch and turn it into a beautiful header photo in minutes. Each step is easier than the next, and you’re guaranteed to come up with a beautiful design every time. The tool is very versatile and provides you with exactly what you need to get the job done and make your Twitter profile just that much better for it.</p>",title:"PicsArt Twitter Header Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/44591004551931483631.png",imageAlt:"short hair woman with closed eyes in the nature touching a flower with her cheek",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Twitter Header",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>It happens way too often that you finally get your hands on the perfect design or image that best reflects your personality and character. You go to your Twitter profile to set it up as your header photo and that’s when your typical problems start. Either the photo’s too small and you need to upload a new one, or it’s bigger than Twitter’s header layout and your hand picked image is cropped in ways that completely defeat the whole purpose. The solution is usually either manually resizing, chopping, and cropping in a photo editor until you have a decent looking version of the original image, or worse, coming up with an entirely new image. With our Twitter header maker with a single click of a button you can set up a canvas with the exact size of Twitter’s headers, and from there it’s simply a matter of grabbing your favorite photo and putting it in there.</p>",title:"Premade Twitter Header Layout",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/26448262322130027381.png",imageAlt:"personal trainer and life coach young woman standing in the nature",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Twitter Header",gtmValue:"3"},imageToRight:!0},{description:"<p>If you’re trying to make twitter headers in a short amount of time that are good looking, chances are you can’t afford to make entire new designs from scratch. If you’re in this situation then you simply need to grab a template off the shelf, edit it just enough that it contains your own unique personal touch, then set it as your Twitter header, and you’re good to go. But to do this, you need two things from your go-to Twitter banner maker, lots of premade templates that are specifically designed to make Twitter headers with, and the functionality that allows you to edit and customize every element of those templates. Thankfully, with PicsArt you can effortlessly do all these and more. Once you click on “Twitter Cover” you’ll receive an entire list of Twitter header templates that are designed ground-up by our own talented artists. And the best part is the fact that you can customize, change, and edit every single element of your selected template.</p>",title:"Unique and Customizable Twitter Header Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/01547532726515323447.png",imageAlt:"twitter header example about podcasts",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Twitter Header",gtmValue:"4"}}],$s={description:"<p>Turn your Twitter profile all the way up with our free Twitter header maker.</p>",title:"Get the Perfect Look With PicsArt’s Twitter Header Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/99613352803951019827.png",imageAlt:"starry night with mountains and dark pink sky",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Twitter Header",gtmValue:"1"}},Js="twitter_header_maker",Zs=!0,el=function(){return(el=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},tl=Gs,ol=Xs,rl=Qs,nl=Ks,al=$s,il=Js,sl=Zs,ll=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(il),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,el({},al,{screenName:il,isPremium:sl,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"},isAmp:o})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},rl),isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:nl,screenName:il,isPremium:sl,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:ol,data:tl,isAmp:o}))},cl=[[{index:1,pointDescription:'Select Template Editor from our <a href="/create" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="birthday-step-create-hypertext">Editing Tools.</a>'},{index:2,pointDescription:"Type “Birthday Card” in the search bar at the top, and press enter."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Select the design you want for your birthday card."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Customize your card with more images and stickers."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Click Download to save your birthday card."}]],ul="How to Make a Birthday Card",pl="Make a birthday card they’ll remember with PicsArt. Start with a photo from your own library or pick one of our high-quality #FreetoEdit images. Customize your birthday card using PicsArt’s quick & easy photo editing tools. Pick from a variety of dimensions. Add cool effects and filters, fun stickers, bold backgrounds, and so much more. Don’t forget to finish with a heartfelt birthday message using our handy Text tool with 200+ unique fonts. Making a one-of-a-kind birthday card with PicsArt will only take you minutes to do but will make an impression on your loved ones forever. Once you’re done with your special creation, download it to print out or send it out virtually.",dl=[{description:'<p>Want to know how to make a birthday card? PicsArt’s birthday card maker is the way to go. It’s fast, it’s free, and it’s fun! Make a beautiful, personalized birthday card for your friends, family, and colleagues without spending a single penny or wasting a lot of time. Instead of paying money to buy a generic birthday card at the store, let PicsArt help you create something truly unique for free. The best part is that you don’t need to have any design experience to design a birthday card that will make them smile. Simply use <a href="/photo-editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="birthday-photo-editor-hypertext">PicsArt’s quick & easy photo editor </a> to personalize your birthday card with fun details in no time. Pick from a variety of dimensions, then print out your creation or send it off virtually.</p>',title:"PicsArt’s Birthday Card Maker Is Fast & Free",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/87405829313552445582.png",imageAlt:"dinner and drinks text on a birthday card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a birthday card",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>No matter who you’re wishing a happy birthday to, PicsArt can help you make a personalized birthday card that stands out from the rest with its easy-to-use birthday card maker. Whether it’s a child’s, teenager’s, or adult’s birthday you’re celebrating, we have the perfect features to impress them. Using PicsArt’s quick & easy editing tools, you can truly customize your experience by layering effects, stickers, backgrounds, icons, text, and more. You don’t need any design experience to achieve something extraordinary with PicsArt. Say goodbye to basic and expensive birthday cards and start making personal birthday cards that will make your friends, family, and coworkers feel special.</p>",title:"Never Send a Boring Birthday Card Again",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/84604812153089181471.png",imageAlt:"birthday card template of a girl blowing her cake candles",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a birthday card",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Why send them a generic birthday card when you can pick out a personalized card that will speak to their style and heart? With PicsArt’s birthday card maker, you can make a one-of-a-kind birthday card in mere minutes and without spending a single penny. Upload a photo from your personal library to start or use one of our #FreetoEdit images. Next, use <a href="/editing-tools" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="birthday-editing-tools-hypertext">PicsArt’s quick & easy editing tools </a>to add special elements that reflect your loved one’s unique aesthetic. Layer on filter and effects, stickers, backgrounds, icons, and more. Finally, write your personal birthday message using our Text tool with 200+ stylish fonts. Now all that’s left to do is send it off. Once they open your customized birthday card, they will thank you for making them a birthday card that’s anything but basic.</p>',title:"Customize Birthday Cards With Easy Tools",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/79065310439563732434.png",imageAlt:"cream cupcakes birthday card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a birthday card",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Don’t have a lot of time but still want to send them a unique birthday card? PicsArt’s birthday card templates are the perfect alternative to the birthday card maker. Our in-house designers have created beautifully designed birthday card templates that will impress the recipient. Once you choose the birthday card template that works for you, you can customize any of its design details to reflect your loved one. Add their photo, layer on effects and stickers, and be sure to write a personalized message using our collection of beautiful fonts. Once you’re done, download your personalized birthday card and print it out or send it virtually.</p>",title:"Save Time With PicsArt’s Birthday Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/58487219275347872656.png",imageAlt:"girl hands holding birthday girl card template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a birthday card",gtmValue:"5"}}],ml={description:"<p>Our online birthday card maker is the perfect way to send a truly personalized birthday message to friends and family on their special day.</p>",title:"Create Beautiful Moments With PicsArt’s Birthday Card Maker ",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/79247306893448919544.png",imageAlt:"happy birthday card template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/chooser",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a birthday card",gtmValue:"1"}},hl="birthday_card_maker",gl=!0,fl=function(){return(fl=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},yl=cl,bl=ul,vl=pl,kl=dl,wl=ml,Pl=hl,El=gl,xl=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Pl),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,fl({},wl,{screenName:Pl,isPremium:El,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"},isAmp:o})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},vl),isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:kl,screenName:Pl,isPremium:El,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:bl,data:yl,isAmp:o}))},Tl=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open PicsArt’s Sticker Maker tool."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload the photo you want to turn into a sticker."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Remove its background by clicking on Object or Person."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Click Apply."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Click Download to save your sticker."}]],Al=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open the PicsArt Web Editor."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Click on Upload to upload a photo or find a festive Halloween background as the backdrop for your post."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Click Stickers from the editor bar on the left side of your screen. "},{index:4,pointDescription:"Search for the Halloween stickers you desire and click on them to add them to your photo. "}],[{index:5,pointDescription:"Place the stickers anywhere you’d like. You can adjust or blend them using the tools in the upper right side above your photo. "},{index:6,pointDescription:"To add Halloween-inspired effects or text, click Effects and Text from the left panel editor bar. "},{index:7,pointDescription:"Click on Download and Share when you’re done to save and export your finished Halloween masterpiece. "}]],Nl=[{description:'<p>PicsArt’s Halloween stickers are the perfect way to dress up your content in seconds. From spooky stickers to pumpkin stickers and more, you can lend instant pizazz to any post with just one or two or even a few Halloween stickers. Once you’ve found the ultimate Halloween stickers, it’s time to figure out how to actually use them! You can layer Halloween stickers on your own pictures to give them some spooky Halloween vibes or on top of PicsArt’s templates and festive <a href="/hashtag/halloween" class="inline-link" target="_parent">Halloween backgrounds.</a> You can also add Halloween <a href="https://picsart.app.link/LZckMNB8mab" class="inline-link" target="_parent">fonts</a> (like Double Feature, Buffied, and Pitchfork) and spooky <a href="https://picsart.app.link/Ixh2YwenAab" class="inline-link" target="_parent">effects</a> (like Lace, Broken Ice, and Spider Web masks) to create Halloween content that is truly one-of-a-kind. </p>',title:"Discover PicsArt’s Halloween Stickers",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/60398242754257885935.png",imageAlt:"purple hair girl with veil and halloween make up",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"2"}}],Ol=[{description:"<p>Halloween posters make for super cute and inspired wall art! Dress them up with as many scary stickers as your heart desires. You can print and display them on your front door or on your windows for trick or treaters to see. If you’d prefer to keep things virtual, you can download your Halloween poster file and share it on your social media profile. </p>",title:"For Posters",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/53808328376592949456.png",imageAlt:"short hair girl with a scary halloween make up in a dark forest ",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>When creating your Halloween party invitation, don’t forget to layer it with festive stickers to really give it a custom feel. Whether you’re hosting a scary bash or a children’s affair, you can pick from a slew of Halloween stickers to get guests in the mood.  </p>",title:"For Invitations",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/23452960741314098394.png",imageAlt:"you are invited to halloween party invitation template ",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Whether you’re thinking of making a Halloween banner, spooky decals, or candy bags for trick or treating and party favors, you can use Halloween stickers to give them a unique touch. From ghouls and bats to pumpkins and spiders, there are so many options to get creative!</p>",title:"For Decorations",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/20070900978592576349.png",imageAlt:"halloween themed image with 3 girls with scary skull make up on",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Want to show off your costume or Halloween DIY project on social media? We can’t blame you! Don’t forget to add as many Halloween stickers as you can fit on your post to spotlight your festive spirit. Don’t feel like getting dressed this year? Use Halloween stickers for makeup (we’re loving mermaid scales and vampire looks!), spooky eye contacts, cat ears, and fairy or angel wings. You’ll have an instant Halloween costume done in minutes, without a last-minute run to the store!  </p>",title:"For Social Media",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/63253032621603245885.png",imageAlt:"halloween themed image of a girl with a spider web halloween make up",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"6"}}],_l={description:"<p>PicsArt’s Halloween stickers are free, easy to use, and so spookily good.</p>",title:"Halloween Stickers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/54188030114719078412.png",imageAlt:"girl portrait image with halloween stickers",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Try Stickers",gtmValue:"1"}},jl="halloween_stickers",Sl=!0,Cl=function(){return(Cl=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Rl=Tl,Il=Al,Ul=Nl,Ml=Ol,Wl=_l,Dl=jl,Fl=Sl,Ll=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Dl),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Cl({},Wl,{screenName:Dl,isPremium:Fl,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Along with the perfect costume, Halloween also requires figuring out invitations and decorations for the haunted house bash or festive pumpkin carving party. That’s where Halloween stickers come into play. You can use spooky stickers and pumpkin stickers for digital posts or take them into the real world and print them out to create decals. Either way, PicsArt has plenty of premium and free Halloween stickers for you to download. Feeling extra creative? Make your own Halloween stickers with the quick & ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"https://picsart.app.link/nJeWti0Syab",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link"},"easy Sticker Maker")," tool. Once you’ve learned how to use Halloween stickers, incorporate them into your Halloween content and DIY projects!")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Ul,screenName:Dl,isPremium:Fl,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Use Halloween Stickers",data:Il}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Ml,screenName:Dl,isPremium:Fl,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make Your Own Halloween Stickers",data:Rl}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Vl=[{description:"<p>Forget about manually removing backgrounds from your images. This is a time-consuming process that requires you to be overly precise. Let our Artificial Intelligence (AI) do this task for you. Our free Background Remover automatically identifies the background of your image and removes it for you, leaving only the elements that appear in the foreground. Our AI technology has been trained to identify backgrounds even in images that have hundreds of small details and elements. This seemingly difficult task has been simplified by PicsArt. Once the background has been removed from the image, you will be left with a transparent background. You can save this new file in PNG format and use it to create more content. </p>",title:"Our Background Remover is Powered by AI",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/21192249761600424266.png",imageAlt:"girl in sportswear on a juicy and orange background",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Remove Your Background",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>Once AI comes into play, it only takes a single click to have a transparent background behind your image. Creating a transparent background has never been this easy. Now, you have the option to upload your own background, choose from our background templates, set it to a solid color, or create a gradient. PicsArt’s photo Background Remover has various ready-to-use free background templates. You can find many thematic backgrounds, like seasonal, holiday, patterned backgrounds, and much more. <a href="/background-changer" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test=">to-change-your-background-hypertext">To change your background,</a> scroll through to see which one best fits the foreground. If you prefer something more simple, set your background to a solid color that complements your foreground, or create a smooth gradient for a more unique look. </p>',title:"Create Transparent Backgrounds ",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/94210882107903817544.png",imageAlt:"curly hair man on a transparent background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Remove Your Background",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Don’t forget to tone in your background and foreground. You can edit the foreground with <a href="/editing-tools?source=landing_pages" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="our-editing-tools-hypertext">our Editing Tools.</a> Adjust the objects in the foreground by blending them in with your background, or make them stand out even more by increasing the contrast. You have the option to darken, soften, play around with the hue, saturation, color, and the luminosity of your foreground. You can increase or decrease the size of the image, flip it around, and adjust its position on your canvas. The photo Background Remover and its accompanying tools will help you achieve professional-looking content without the hassle of using complicated software.</p>',title:"Background Burner!",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/80291984627480708845.png",imageAlt:"girl sitting on the rock with starts background",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Remove Your Background",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Background Remover comes with an Eraser tool. Use the Eraser tool to make your outlines more precise. In case you want to touch up your edits, you can use this tool to precisely eliminate unwanted lines, shapes, and objects. Erase your background to make your logos and products stand out. As an example, you can use your product images with transparent backgrounds and place them on a banner or other visual content. The same can be done for your company logo. If you want to save certain textures or details from your original background, use the Brush mode to restore certain elements back. Simply select the tool’s Brush mode and go over the area where you want the original background to show again. This tool is instrumental in achieving high-quality content. </a></p>",title:"Background Eraser for Precision",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/70789642193034857934.png",imageAlt:"girl with glasses on a watermelon background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Remove Your Background",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'Remove the background from any of your images and turn them into stickers! You can <a href="/add-stickers-to-photos" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="add-these-stickers-to-any-of-your-images-hypertext">add these stickers to any of your images</a> to give them more personality and uniqueness. You can save these stickers and use them throughout your editing process. A transparent background makes it easy for you to apply them onto other images. Learn more about making stickers <a href="/sticker-maker" class="inline-link" target="_blank">here</a>. If you are a business owner, you can create stickers from your company logo or your products. These are really convenient when you’re creating content for social media channels. You can quickly add them to your banners and images. Your posts will become more identifiable with your consumers - ultimately increasing brand awareness.  </p>',title:"Make a Sticker From Your Picture",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/28342031775915548177.png",imageAlt:"boy sitting photo on a palms background",bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Remove Your Background",gtmValue:"6"}}],zl={description:"<p>Creating transparent backgrounds has never been this simple. Easily remove backgrounds online with this quick tool. </p>",title:"Remove the Background From Images in One Click",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/67123117012773062594.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Remove Your Background",gtmValue:"1"}},ql=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your image or choose from our free-to-edit options."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Let AI detect the background and remove it."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Select the Eraser tool and refine the edges."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Click on the foreground and start editing."}],[{index:5,pointDescription:"Adjust the opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Blend your foreground with your background."},{index:7,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],Bl=!0,Hl="remove_background",Yl=function(){return(Yl=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Gl=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=ql,n=Vl,a=zl,i=Hl,s=Bl;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Yl({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Remove a Background From Your Picture",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Xl=[{description:"<p>Have you ever taken a great picture, but there was just something about the background that you would have liked to erase or change? Luckily, you can easily change the background of your photo online with PicsArt. Once you upload your image,  our AI will detect your background within seconds and suggest multiple replacements. You can choose between textured backgrounds and patterns. Thinking of something more special? PicsArt’s Background Changer offers a huge library of thematic backgrounds, such as special holiday themes, seasonal backgrounds, and even more playful themes, like fruity backgrounds, flowers, hearts, etc. Or, if you want to keep it simple, just apply a plain background. Create new content for your social media channels, and make sure your posts stand out with our unique backgrounds. You will be able to find the perfect background for any type of content you are working with. </p>",title:"Make Your Images More Dynamic With Our Background Photo Editor",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/43452060271053392478.png",imageAlt:"curly hair happy girl with pineapple background",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XT4Tlv7ht8",label:"Change Your Background",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Graphic design is a very competitive field. Visual trends and new techniques emerge on a daily basis. So make sure your content keeps up with the times. Especially on social media, it is important to be able to stand out with your content. Having an eye-catching background is just one of the many ways you can ensure that a person stops scrolling and takes a second look at what you have to offer. This picture Background Changer is especially useful for product promotions. If there is a certain product that you are trying to advertise, your background can serve as the perfect display for it. You can apply a solid color to your background, or create a smooth gradient with colors of your choice. Changing your background color online has never been this simple. If you have your own background in mind that you would like to have, just upload it. To make sure your background and foreground complement each other, use PicsArt’s Editing Tools for some touch-ups. Adjust the hue, saturation, color, and the luminosity of your image in the foreground with our Background Changer online. You even have the option to blend it in with the background or make it stand out even more. Regardless of your marketing objectives, PicsArt gives you all the tools you need in order to succeed.</p>",title:"Change a Background Instantly",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/22504490606453640633.png",imageAlt:"curly black hair girl with night and starts background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XT4Tlv7ht8",label:"Change Your Background",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Make sure your social media posts are sized properly. You want to avoid having a Facebook cover photo that doesn’t fit, or an Instagram post that crops out important aspects of your image. With PicsArt’s Fit tool, you can easily set your canvas to specific social media image sizes. The templates are preset to the optimal size for each specific social media channel. All you have to do is simply click on whichever format you’re going for, and your image will automatically fit to the proportions. With our handy Fit tool, you can take any image and use our photo cropping feature to change its size. Need a square pic? No problem. Want a portrait style? We got you. Once your image is fitted, share it on your social media channels! PicsArt allows you to fit your image for Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest, and YouTube. </p>",title:"Use the Fit Tool for Social Media ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/11159592696118699326.png",imageAlt:"man doing selfie with pinterest,facebook and instagram background",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XT4Tlv7ht8",label:"Change Your Background",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>Our online Background Changer comes with a multi-purpose Eraser tool. Whether you want to refine some elements in your image or achieve a more textured background, this tool will help bring your vision to life. Erase unwanted parts from your image, or make your outlines more precise. In the online photo Background Changer, simply click on the Eraser and start refining your image. This easy-to-use tool will help you achieve professional-looking content, without the need of using professional software. This tool will also work well if you completely <a href="/background-remover" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="remove-the-background-of-your-image-hypertext"> remove the background of your image.</a>  With the brush mode, you can bring back textures and details from your original background. Select the tool and brush over the area where you want your original background to show. Get as creative as possible while editing your background. </p>',title:"Continue Editing Your Photo Background",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/37532553096553072450.png",imageAlt:"happy girl with colorful glasses background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XT4Tlv7ht8",label:"Change Your Background",gtmValue:"5"}}],Ql={description:"<p>Change your plain background with our new Background Editor.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Photo Background Changer",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/71682385003483268837.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XT4Tlv7ht8",label:"Change Your Background",gtmValue:"1"}},Kl=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your image or choose from our free-to-edit images"},{index:2,pointDescription:"AI then detects the background and replaces it with a default texture"},{index:3,pointDescription:"Browse through other options, play around with backgrounds"},{index:4,pointDescription:"Select the Eraser tool and touch-up the edges"}],[{index:5,pointDescription:"Adjust opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Blend your foreground with your background."},{index:7,pointDescription:"Fit your image for social media."},{index:8,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],$l=!0,Jl="change_background",Zl=function(){return(Zl=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},ec=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Kl,n=Xl,a=Ql,i=Jl,s=$l;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Zl({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Change the Background of a Picture",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},tc=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose one of our brochure templates."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a new picture or choose one from our #FreetoEdit images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Swap out the text in the template and adjust the layout of the brochure."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],oc=[{description:"<p>If you’re a travel agent looking to introduce the world to all of your exciting tour packages, PicsArt’s free brochure templates are the way to go. Instead of paying a professional thousands to get the job done, you can do it all by yourself from your home or office. Our travel-related brochure templates are plenty and so easy to use. You don’t need to have any programming or design skills to create something beautiful. Choose the template that works for you, then edit the design details to fit your business needs. Finally, download the final product and start getting the word out. </p>",title:"Travel Brochure Templates to Impress Clients",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/93932162303807752702.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Medical brochures are vital in getting important information out to the public. Equally important as the text is the design as it’s the first thing the reader will see. Each design aspect and imagery should match the copy beautifully. Whether it’s a large healthcare facility or a small practice, PicsArt has a brochure template that suits your needs. Once you choose the one that works for you, just edit the colors and text with our unique fonts until you’re happy with the results. You’ll be proud of what you created with PicsArt’s help.</p>",title:"Medical Brochure Templates to Relay Information",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/20742438487954830561.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>No matter what kind of business you own, there is a product or service you must promote in order to build excitement. Let PicsArt help you out with that. With our free business brochure templates, you’ll never have a shortage of ideas to choose from. No matter your industry and product type, you can personalize any of our templates to fit your business needs. You can change any design aspect like colors, backgrounds, and text using our over 200 stylish fonts. No more paying thousands of dollars to create a brochure when you can do it all on your own with the help of PicsArt.</p>",title:"Business Brochures to Market & Promote",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/15242641984791389374.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>If you’re in the real estate industry, you are no stranger to brochures to get the news out about the properties you’re selling, no matter how big or small. With PicsArt’s free real estate brochure templates, the process is super painless and fast. Just pick a template that fits the theme of the house or condo on the market, then customize the look by switching up the text and colors to match. Once you’re done, you can focus on making that great sell in style.</p>",title:"Real Estate Brochures to Make a Sale",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/08517360877895922817.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>The wedding industry is built on beauty and romance, so it’s especially crucial to present stylized brochures to your clients that convey love in the most stunning way. PicsArt’s wedding brochure templates are soft and sleek, so you can promote your wedding-related product or service in style. Our talented designers make sure to create the most eye-catching templates that any bride or groom will love. From cakes to flowers to event planning to photography, there is a template that’s right for each wedding-related category.</p>",title:"Wedding Brochures to Capture the Romance",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/86460264446710830759.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"6"}}],rc={description:"<p>Use our free brochure templates to get the professional word out and do it in style.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Brochure Templates Are Here for Your Branding Needs",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/07157824356225819588.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},nc="brochure_templates",ac=!0,ic="template",sc=function(){return(sc=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},lc=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=tc,n=oc,a=rc,i=nc,s=ac,c=ic;It(i,c);var u="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,sc({},a,{landingCategory:c,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"With PicsArt’s brochure design templates, you can create beautiful digital brochures that will speak to your business’ unique aesthetic. Do so in a matter of minutes, no headaches or high costs involved. Whether you’re selling services or goods, or announcing a new product or store, a professional brochure is necessary when connecting with your customers. To give your brochure a special touch, you can easily customize your message with stylish fonts and additional design details until you’re satisfied with the end result. Then, all that’s left to do is showcase your eye-catching work. With PicsArt’s free brochure templates, you can rest assured that your sleek brochure will be well admired.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,landingCategory:c,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create Brochures With PicsArt’s Brochure Templates",data:r}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:u,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},isAmp:o,productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,key:t})}))))},cc=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open the Business Card Maker."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Pick a background from the #FreetoEdit image library or upload your own image."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Customize your business card with our editing tools."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your business card."}]],uc=[{description:"<p>Making a business card shouldn’t have to be a complicated process. In fact, at PicsArt, we believe it should be fun! Our Business Card Maker is very easy to use. Within minutes, you can create a professional business card that you’ll be proud to give out at your next networking event. Start by picking the perfect background from one of our millions of #FreetoEdit images or upload one of your own. Next, customize all the details to speak to your aesthetic using our stylish fonts and effects. All our editing tools are intuitive and convenient, so you won’t spend too much of your time making something awesome.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Business Card Maker Is Easy to Use",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/45329033769052874997.png",imageAlt:"architect business card design template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Card",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Every brand has the desire to stand out from the competition. There are so many ways to do so and a professional, sleek business card is definitely one. With PicsArt’s easy-to-use Business Card Maker, you can create a stylish business card that will speak to your brand’s signature voice and style. And you can do so within minutes. If you have a brand logo that you’d like to use on your business card, you can easily add it and play around with its placement until it’s right. From simple to bold, you can make the business card of your brand’s dreams with PicsArt.</p>",title:"Design Professional Business Cards to Make Your Brand Stand Out",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/86365094516574018289.png",imageAlt:"bookshop director business card design template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Card",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Customization is key when it comes to creating your brand’s business card. That’s because you want to make something unique and eye-catching that will capture the attention of your customers. To get away from the generic, PicsArt has tons of editing tools to help you create something that will not only relay your brand’s important contact information but will also impress. You can use one of our millions of #FreetoEdit images or upload your own photo, then pick the right font for your brand’s aesthetic. We have thousands of designer fonts for you to choose from, so you’ll definitely find one that will convey your information in style. </p>",title:"Customize Business Cards in Minutes",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/70872495402244623977.png",imageAlt:"sweets store business card design template",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Card",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>At PicsArt, not only do we have a Business Card Make but we also have tons of business card templates for you to choose from. Templates are a great place to start if you don’t feel like starting from scratch. Peruse our business card templates at your leisure, then pick the one that suits your brand best. Want something subtle? Need something bold? We’ve got it all. Once you do settle on a business card template that matches your style, you can still fully personalize your business card to make it stand out.</p>",title:"Try a Wide Range of Business Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/36333891596232280912.png",imageAlt:"beauty bar business card design template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Card",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Even if you’ve never designed a business card in your life — or anything else for that matter — PicsArt can help you create something sleek and professional within minutes. You can easily incorporate your brand’s logo and signature colors, add beautiful fonts, fun stickers, icons, and any other design attributes you need to make your business card pop. PicsArt’s editing tools make it super easy for you to design a business card without any design experience. All you need is a vision of what you want your brand’s business card to look like. Once you do, we can help you bring it to life.</p>",title:"Design Business Cards With Zero Professional Skills",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/71216640097489821097.png",imageAlt:"museum of modern art business card design template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Card",gtmValue:"6"}}],pc={description:"<p>Create professional business cards with the help of PicsArt and customize with our intuitive, easy-to-use editing tools.</p>",title:" Become a Business Card Maker Pro in Minutes",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/98292802759601176798.png",imageAlt:"photographer business card design template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=marketing",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make a Card",gtmValue:"1"}},dc="business_card_maker",mc=!0,hc=function(){return(hc=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},gc=cc,fc=uc,yc=pc,bc=dc,vc=mc,kc=function(e){var t=e.isAmp;return It(bc),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:t},l.a.createElement(Tn,hc({},yc,{screenName:bc,isPremium:vc,isAmp:t,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:t,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s Business Card Maker is always ready for you when you need a professional business card without spending a fortune or countless hours. Create business cards within minutes using our handy online Business Card Maker, then fully customize the experience to fit your professional needs. Spotlight all the details you want to share on your business card using one of our thousands of stylish fonts. Play around with filters and effects to give your business card the unique touch that will make it stand out in a sea of competitors.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:fc,screenName:bc,isPremium:vc,isAmp:t}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:t,title:"How to Make a Business Card",data:gc}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:t}))},wc=function(){return l.a.createElement(Gt,{bannerProps:ut.photo})},Pc=function(){return l.a.createElement(Gt,{bannerProps:ut.video,editor:"video"})},Ec=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose one of our collage templates."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload multiple pictures or choose one from our #FreetoEdit images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Place your images in the layout."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],xc=[{description:"<p>Picture collages may seem like a complicated design feat to pull off, but with PicsArt’s free collage templates, they’re super easy, fast, and fun. All you need to get started are a handful of beautiful photos that you want to share with the world or keep to yourself. Creating online mood boards is a creative way you can put our collage templates to good use, whether you’re making a mood board to share with friends, or to use as inspiration for a home or work project. You can create fashion-inspired mood boards to keep track of your favorite outfits, a mood board for home decoration purposes, or a mood board to set the theme for an upcoming event. With new filters constantly added, you can give your collages a trendy feel.</p>",title:"Inspire With Mood Board Collages and Fashion Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/29582373803961946532.png",imageAlt:"top 10 international fashion week collage template with a shopping girl on it",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Birthday photos are an exciting way to get in on PicsArt’s collage templates, all while reliving your best memories. Consider that there are a few types of online photo collages to choose from when wanting to create a birthday collage. You can use pre-made collage template grids (we have over 40 to peruse for every kind of look and style), you can try our Collage Maker for a freestyle approach if you’re highly visual, or you can pick from endless free collage templates that are specially designed for birthdays. You can also sift through uniquely designed photo collage ideas, like geometric shapes, glittery frames, colorful collages, bold shapes, and more. In just a few taps, you’ll be ready to share your favorite birthday moments with friends.</p>",title:"Have Fun With Birthday Photo Collage Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/36484129449457336461.png",imageAlt:"happy birthday to my dear friend text on a collage template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>There’s nothing more nostalgic than gathering family photos to celebrate all the special moments you’ve shared together. For special family photos (candids and posed), we have a handful of sweet photo collage templates that can be used to spotlight your loved ones, both by sharing them online or by framing and hanging them on the wall. With PicsArt’s free photo collage templates, you can go the extra mile to personalize your family photo collage by adding in design details that speak to your style. Is there a certain color or image that represents your clan? You can easily incorporate any design detail to your photo collage to create a one-of-a-kind look.</p>",title:"Get Nostalgic With Family Photo Collage Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/76937545337164522931.png",imageAlt:"transformation text on a 10 years challenge image collage template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>One of the most special moments in life involves weddings and all things related to love. For those exciting occasions, we have endless romantic photo collage templates to help you show off your union. Whether it’s an engagement shoot, a bridal shower with friends, or a rustic outdoor wedding, PicsArt’s free photo collage templates are the perfect way to gather your wedding-related moments in one place. You can even create a collage of all the fun selfies you and your partner have taken over the years. Just let your imagination run wild and have fun with it. </p>",title:"Create Romance With Wedding and Love Collage Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/64615210010623410647.png",imageAlt:"can't stop loving you text on a couple's photo collage template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>For holidays like Christmas, Valentine’s Day, and Halloween, our designers create festive photo collage templates that you can use to show off your favorite photos in one spot. Pick the photo template that matches the holiday you want to celebrate, then add as many photos as you’d like to show off to your social circle. With special holiday-inspired photo collage templates, you usually only have to do minimal editing since the theme is set. Choose to add your own text with over 200 stylish fonts that match the holiday. The possibilities are endless, and with PicsArt, the possibilities are painless. </p>",title:"Celebrate With Holiday Collage Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/70789964126335101658.png",imageAlt:"travel time on a travel photo collage template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"6"}}],Tc={description:"<p>Use our free collage templates to bring together your favorite photos, then easily edit the design details to match your style.</p>",title:"Gather Your Memories With PicsArt’s Collage Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/80104351950960027215.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl with a red tshirt and moder glasses photo collage template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},Ac="collage_templates",Nc=!0,Oc="template",_c=function(){return(_c=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},jc=Ec,Sc=xc,Cc=Tc,Rc=Ac,Ic=Nc,Uc=Oc,Mc=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;It(Rc,Uc);var r="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,_c({},Cc,{landingCategory:Uc,screenName:Rc,isPremium:Ic,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Collages are a great way to share a handful of images at once. You’ll find a plethora of easy-to-use photo collage templates on PicsArt that bring your best photos together to create a cohesive, beautiful story. Gather all your favorite moments in one place with an existing photo template or create your own online photo collage from scratch with our ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/collage-maker",className:"inline-link",target:"_blank"},"Collage Maker.")," Then edit the look by playing around with trendy effects, stickers, brushes, fonts, and more. There is no limit to creativity, so personalize it your way for a one-of-a-kind feel.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:Rc,isPremium:Ic,isAmp:o,tag:"tags/collage"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:Uc,productData:Sc,screenName:Rc,isPremium:Ic,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create Photo Collages",data:jc}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:r,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},isAmp:o,productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,key:t})}))))},Wc={picsArt:{title:"Download PicsArt Photo & Video Editor App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38297334288968341477.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"},{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38297334288968341477.png",icon:"google-play-brand",storeName:"Google Play"},{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38297334288968341477.png",icon:"microsoft-brand",storeName:"Microsoft Store"}]},picsArtColor:{title:"Download PicsArt Color Paint App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/18053162215013380227.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"},{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/18053162215013380227.png",icon:"google-play-brand",storeName:"Google Play"}]},pixelArt:{title:"Download PixelArt App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/90742136053287525266.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"},{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/90742136053287525266.png",icon:"google-play-brand",storeName:"Google Play"}]},animator:{title:"Download PicsArt Animator App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/87164372417616239160.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"},{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/87164372417616239160.png",icon:"google-play-brand",storeName:"Google Play"}]},efekt:{title:"Download EFEKT Video Maker App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/46111629124286934244.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"}]},gif:{title:"Download PicsArt GIF & Sticker Maker App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/36141346549104056405.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"}]}},Dc={picsArt:{label:"Get It Now",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TIVYc9ZjNu",qrModal:Wc.picsArt,gtmValue:"3",secondary:!1},picsArtPhotoStudio:{label:"Read More",url:"/apps/picsart-photo-studio",mobileUrl:"/apps/picsart-photo-studio",gtmValue:"4"},picsArtColor:{label:"Get It Now",mobileUrl:"https://paint.app.link",qrModal:Wc.picsArtColor,gtmValue:"5",secondary:!1},pixelArt:{label:"Get It Now",mobileUrl:"https://papixelart.app.link",qrModal:Wc.pixelArt,gtmValue:"6",secondary:!1},efekt:{label:"Get It Now",mobileUrl:"https://efekt.app.link",qrModal:Wc.efekt,gtmValue:"7",secondary:!1},animator:{label:"Get It Now",mobileUrl:"https://animatorpa.app.link",qrModal:Wc.animator,gtmValue:"8",secondary:!1},gif:{label:"Get It Now",mobileUrl:"https://gifpa.app.link",qrModal:Wc.gif,gtmValue:"9",secondary:!1}},Fc={description:"<p>This photo hair editor is a fast and easy way to see how you’ll look with various hair colors before making the permanent jump.</p>",title:"Try PicsArt’s Hair Color Changer for a Virtual Beauty Makeover\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/06008710753166939814.png",imageAlt:"pink hair girl image on a pink background with white clouds and blue butterfly stickers",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TovgGFVpt8",label:"Change Hair Color",gtmValue:"1"}},Lc=[{description:'<p>With PicsArt’s impressive Hair Color Changer, it only takes one tap and a few seconds to switch up your virtual hair color! Always wanted to see how you’ll look with red or pink (or insert another color) hair? Now you can see how you’ll look with any color hair before making the permanent jump. All you have to do is upload a portrait or selfie of yourself to our Hair Color Changer tool in our <a href="/photo-editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="photo-editor-hypertext">Photo Editor,</a> then click on the hair color you’d like to try out. As soon as you do, our AI technology will work its magic to change your hair color in a few seconds. There is no limit to how many hair colors you can try, so keep going until you’re satisfied with the result. For extra pizazz, you can use our <a href="/background-changer" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="background-changer-tool-hypertext">Background Changer tool</a> to add a fun backdrop to your new self(ie).</p>',title:"Try Different Virtual Hair Color Options",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/93933577265296523979.png",imageAlt:"colorful hair girl with glasses",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TovgGFVpt8",label:"Change Hair Color",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>If you’re in the mood to experiment with your hair color but don’t want to make the permanent commitment just yet, just turn to PicsArt’s Hair Color Changer tool to help you out. Our handy tool is great for switching up your hair color in selfies and portraits that you want to post to your social media channels. Want to play a trick on your fans and clients? Just run your photo through our Hair Color Changer to give yourself a makeover that will shock and awe. Hairstylists can access the tool to show clients how they will appear with a certain hair color they’ve been wanting to try out. Beauty bloggers and influencers can use the Hair Color Changer to give themselves a whole new look and ask their fans to vote on their favorite color. Finish by layering on one of our trendy <a href="/photo-effects" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="photo-effects-hypertext">photo effects</a> for added personalization. </p>',title:"Change Your Hair Color Online in Seconds",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/29494432891824860802.png",imageAlt:"red hair girl with closed eyes wearing orange sweeter smiling",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TovgGFVpt8",label:"Change Hair Color",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Hair Color Changer tool is great for a virtual makeover and it completely transforms hair color in just a few seconds, making it extra impressive. The tool is beyond easy to use. All you have to do on your end is upload a selfie or a portrait (we recommend using something pretty close up), tap on the hair color of your choice, then let our AI technology do its thing. We have tons of hair colors to experiment with so you can go through each one until you’re satisfied with your look. You can even play around with the saturation level to go subtle or intense. Who knows, the Hair Color Changer might even inspire you to try a color you never considered before. Want a simple look? We’ve got many basic hair color choices. Want something a bit more funky? Try blue or pink or purple. From neutral to bold, we’ve got it all at your fingertips. Once you’re done, post your new makeover to your social media feed for feedback.</p>",title:"Our Hair Color Editor Will Spark Inspiration",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/99076257599240097173.png",imageAlt:"girl image before and after having purple hair",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TovgGFVpt8",label:"Change Hair Color",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>The best part about PicsArt’s Hair Color Changer is that it gives you a completely natural appearance, so it looks like you actually did change your hair color. That’s an important detail when creating a virtual makeover. With PicsArt, you won’t get an awkward hairline. We made sure to create a smart tool that makes you look effortless and flawless, no matter which hair color you choose to go with. Go as simple or as bold as you wish by changing up the saturation and intensity of the color. Once you run your selfie or portrait through our Hair Color Changer, it’ll look so natural that you’ll soon be convinced it’s your current hair color. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Photo Hair Editor Is Completely Natural",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/62196660432044235255.png",imageAlt:"man in a beard style",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TovgGFVpt8",label:"Change Hair Color",gtmValue:"5"}}],Vc={editingStepsData:[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload a selfie or portrait to the Hair Color Changer tool."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Click on the hair color you like and let the tool apply it to your hair. "}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Download the final product to your computer and share it on social media."}]],landingData:Lc,bannerData:Fc,screenName:"hair_color_changer"},zc=function(){return(zc=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},qc=Vc.editingStepsData,Bc=Vc.landingData,Hc=Vc.bannerData,Yc=Vc.screenName,Gc=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Yc),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,zc({},Hc,{screenName:Yc,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Bc,screenName:Yc,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Change Hair Color",data:qc}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Xc=o(50),Qc=o.n(Xc),Kc=function(e){var t=e.containerClassName,o=e.itemProps,r=e.title;return l.a.createElement(io,{className:Qc.a.testimonialsContainer,containerClassName:t},l.a.createElement("h3",{className:Qc.a.testimonialsTitle},r),l.a.createElement(nn,{className:Qc.a.carousel,settings:{autoplaySpeed:3e3,slidesToShow:1,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},o&&o.map((function(e){return l.a.createElement("span",{className:Qc.a.contentWrapper,key:e.uuid},l.a.createElement("p",{className:Qc.a.userQuote},e.quoteText),l.a.createElement("div",{className:Qc.a.userInfoWrapper},e.profilePic&&l.a.createElement(Ce.a,{className:Qc.a.userImage,alt:"user profile picture",src:e.profilePic}),l.a.createElement(Re,{className:Qc.a.userName,href:"/u/"+e.userName},"@"+e.userName)))}))))},$c=function(e){var t=e.itemProps,o=e.title;return l.a.createElement(io,{isAmp:!0,className:"testimonials__container"},l.a.createElement("h3",{className:"testimonials__title"},o),l.a.createElement(nn,{className:"testimonials__carousel",isAmp:!0,settings:{autoplaySpeed:3e3,slidesToShow:1,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},t&&t.map((function(e){return l.a.createElement("span",{className:"testimonials__contentWrapper"},l.a.createElement("p",{className:"testimonials__userQuote"},e.quoteText),l.a.createElement("div",{className:"testimonials__userInfoWrapper"},l.a.createElement(Ye.AmpImg,{className:"testimonials__image",specName:"default",src:e.profilePic,width:"50",height:"50",layout:"responsive",alt:"User profile picture"}),l.a.createElement(Re,{className:"testimonials__userName",href:"/u/"+e.userName},"@"+e.userName)))}))))},Jc=function(){return(Jc=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Zc=function(e,t){var o={};for(var r in e)Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(e,r)&&t.indexOf(r)<0&&(o[r]=e[r]);if(null!=e&&"function"==typeof Object.getOwnPropertySymbols){var n=0;for(r=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(e);n<r.length;n++)t.indexOf(r[n])<0&&Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable.call(e,r[n])&&(o[r[n]]=e[r[n]])}return o},eu=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Zc(e,["isAmp"]);return o?l.a.createElement($c,Jc({isAmp:o},r)):l.a.createElement(Kc,Jc({},r))},tu={title:"TESTIMONIALS",itemProps:[{uuid:Object(ue.d)(),userName:"whitecloud21",profilePic:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/08020457378465966301.jpg",quoteText:"My favorite part of the Masters Program is the ability to connect more closely with other PicsArtists from all over the world. I like the heterogeneity (both from an artistic and non-artistic point of view) that distinguishes the members of the program. This is an opportunity to learn new things from each other. And although heterogeneity is what distinguishes us within the program, what unites us all is the desire to feed the creative flow!"},{uuid:Object(ue.d)(),userName:"dakotaelle",profilePic:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/52104403273586754344.jpeg",quoteText:"I am infinitely grateful for the opportunity PicsArt has given me to grow as a photographer and artist. The environment of talented artists combined with the supportive community and positive feedback has helped me develop into a more competent and confident creator."},{uuid:Object(ue.d)(),userName:"BlazeBolt",profilePic:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/09526838344788990660.jpg",quoteText:"The exciting part about being in the Masters Program is having a platform where I can showcase all the amazing effects and tools that Picsart has to offer. As a leader in this community, one of my goals is to help and support others in their quest to create their own masterpieces. Inspiring and encouraging new artists helps to ground me as an artist and is a reminder that once I was a new digital artist seeking inspiration from the Masters that I can now call my friends."},{uuid:Object(ue.d)(),userName:"meeori",profilePic:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/94432613978582902259.png",quoteText:"[The PicsArt community is] definitely a big family. A community that loves, respects, supports and inspires each other regardless of language, religion and race. We don't just share pictures; we let people see our souls here. This is a place where you can be yourself, where you can express yourself to millions of people."}]},ou={testimonialsData:tu,promotionData:{title:"I Want to Be a PicsArt Master!",description:"Think you have what it takes to be a PicsArt Master? Submit your portfolio and find out!",buttonProps:{mobileLink:"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdomdVbJ5GYBTbVvPlGvnKp3pRflaNM8GLlTyrCOwXsEoncWw/viewform",link:"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdomdVbJ5GYBTbVvPlGvnKp3pRflaNM8GLlTyrCOwXsEoncWw/viewform",label:"Submit Interest Form",gtmValue:"5"}},benefitsData:{title:"Benefits",checklist:[{description:'<p>Free subscription to <a href="/gold" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="PicsArt-gold-hypertext">PicsArt Gold</a></p>'},{description:"Exclusive Masters badge on your PicsArt profile"},{description:"Private group chat to learn and collaborate with other Masters"},{description:"Direct access to PicsArt’s Community team"},{description:"Dedicated support channel"},{description:"Early access to news and updates"},{description:"Exclusive monthly newsletter to share product updates and recognize all-star PicsArt Masters"},{description:"Opportunities to be featured on PicsArt’s social media, blog, website, and more"}]},landingData:[{description:"<p>Master Storytellers have “mastered” PicsArt. They take any idea in their head and turn it into a digital masterpiece using PicsArt’s photo editing tools. <br/><br/>Most importantly, they love giving back to the community and sharing their knowledge with up-and-coming artists. <br/><br/>Does this sound like you? Submit the interest form linked below to receive an application when the recruitment window is open.</p>",title:"Become a Master Storyteller",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/28456099270143284854.png",imageAlt:"become a master storyteller at picsart masters community",productId:"master-storytellers",buttonProps:{url:"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdomdVbJ5GYBTbVvPlGvnKp3pRflaNM8GLlTyrCOwXsEoncWw/viewform",mobileUrl:"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdomdVbJ5GYBTbVvPlGvnKp3pRflaNM8GLlTyrCOwXsEoncWw/viewform",label:"I’m Interested!",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Master Contributors are artists who share top-notch <a href="https://support.picsart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360002587417-What-is-FreeToEdit-" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="FreeToEdit-hypertext">#FreeToEdit</a> content on PicsArt. Their mission is to create and share high-quality, easy-to-Remix content such as portraits, backgrounds, stickers, stock photos, and more. They love seeing what other artists create with their #FreetoEdit, too. <br/><br/>Does this sound like you? Submit the interest form linked below to receive an application when recruitment is open.</p>',title:"Become a Master Contributor",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/32206508255320049661.png",imageAlt:"become a master contributor at picsart masters community",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",productId:"master-contributors",buttonProps:{url:"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdomdVbJ5GYBTbVvPlGvnKp3pRflaNM8GLlTyrCOwXsEoncWw/viewform",mobileUrl:"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdomdVbJ5GYBTbVvPlGvnKp3pRflaNM8GLlTyrCOwXsEoncWw/viewform",label:"I’m Interested!",gtmValue:"4"}}],bannerData:{description:"<p>Join the PicsArt Masters Program, our exclusive community for top creatives, to be recognized as one of our most active and talented artists.\n</p>",title:"Are You a PicsArt Master?",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/14956792878432808904.png",imageAlt:"join picsart masters community",buttonProps:{extraSpacing:!0,gtmValue:"1",url:"#master-storytellers",label:"Master Storytellers"},additionalButtonProps:{gtmValue:"2",url:"#master-contributors",label:"Master Contributors"}},screenName:"master_community"},ru=o(70),nu=o.n(ru),au=function(e){var t=e.checklistData;return l.a.createElement("div",{className:nu.a.container},l.a.createElement("div",{className:nu.a.sectionWrapper},l.a.createElement("h3",{className:nu.a.title},t.title),l.a.createElement("ul",{className:nu.a.list},t.checklist&&t.checklist.map((function(e){return l.a.createElement("li",{key:e.description,className:nu.a.listItem,dangerouslySetInnerHTML:{__html:e.description}})})))))},iu=new Fo.AmpScripts,su=function(e){var t=e.checklistData;return l.a.createElement(l.a.Fragment,null,l.a.createElement(Fo.AmpScriptsManager,{ampScripts:iu},l.a.createElement("div",{className:"checklist__container"},l.a.createElement("div",{className:"checklist__sectionWrapper"},l.a.createElement("h3",{className:"checklist__title"},t.title),l.a.createElement("ul",{className:"checklist__list"},t.checklist&&t.checklist.map((function(e){return l.a.createElement("li",{key:e.description,className:"checklist__listItem",dangerouslySetInnerHTML:{__html:e.description}})})))))))},lu=function(){return(lu=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},cu=function(e,t){var o={};for(var r in e)Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(e,r)&&t.indexOf(r)<0&&(o[r]=e[r]);if(null!=e&&"function"==typeof Object.getOwnPropertySymbols){var n=0;for(r=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(e);n<r.length;n++)t.indexOf(r[n])<0&&Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable.call(e,r[n])&&(o[r[n]]=e[r[n]])}return o},uu=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=cu(e,["isAmp"]);return o?l.a.createElement(su,lu({isAmp:o},r)):l.a.createElement(au,lu({},r))},pu=function(){return(pu=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},du=ou.testimonialsData,mu=ou.promotionData,hu=ou.benefitsData,gu=ou.landingData,fu=ou.bannerData,yu=ou.screenName,bu=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(yu),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,pu({},fu,{screenName:yu,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:gu,screenName:yu,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(uu,{checklistData:hu,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(eu,pu({isAmp:o},du)),l.a.createElement(Hr,{description:mu.description,title:mu.title,isAmp:o,buttonProps:{mobileLink:mu.buttonProps.mobileLink,gtmValue:mu.buttonProps.gtmValue,label:mu.buttonProps.label,link:mu.buttonProps.link,secondary:!0},borders:!0}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},vu=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload a photo to the Pattern Generator tool."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Let the AI technology create a patterned backdrop for your image."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Use PicsArt’s editing tools to personalize your photo."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your final edit."}]],ku=[{description:"<p>When it comes to making unique backgrounds for your images, turn to PicsArt’s Pattern Generator to help you out. The tool is super easy to use and you don’t need to need any experience to achieve something beautiful. Simply upload your image to the Pattern Generator tool, then let the smart technology pick a fun backdrop for you. Not happy with the result? Keep going until you’re satisfied with the design. There is no limit to how many background styles you can create with PicsArt’s background maker</p>",title:" PicsArt’s Pattern Maker Is Quick and Easy",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/99723626936142097507.png",imageAlt:"cloth bag with flamingos",buttonProps:{productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Pattern Maker tool!",label:"Create Background",gtmValue:"2",subscribeId:45}},{description:'<p>Once you’ve settled on a background that you’re happy with, you can take things a step further by personalizing the experience to create an even more one-of-a-kind look. Customize your edit by adding your own text fonts, stickers, effects, and more using our quick and easy editing tools. You can opt to change the background colors and even background size to fit your needs. You can also choose to remove the background with our <a href="/background-remover" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="automatically-remove-background">Background Remover tool</a>. Then post your completed creation to your website, blog, and social media channels to gain attention.</p>',title:"This Online Pattern Generator Is Fully Customizable",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/19524248449069363964.png",imageAlt:"creative tea coffee thermos",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Pattern Maker tool!",label:"Create Background",gtmValue:"3",subscribeId:45}},{description:'<p>One of the best parts of PicsArt’s Pattern Generator is that it does the creative thinking for you. If you’re running out of ideas and inspiration on how to spruce up your online images, just pull them into the background maker tool and let the smart technology design something special for you. Consider also using our <a href="/background-changer" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="automatically-change-background"> Background Changer tool </a> for more ideas. Then simply download your finished edit to share with your followers and clients. From websites to blogs to social media accounts, PicsArt’s Pattern Generator is the perfect tool to help you take your images to the next level.</p>',title:"PicsArt’s Pre-Generated Pattern Creator Lends Inspiration",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/17238261536603361130.png",imageAlt:"colorful phone case on a green background",buttonProps:{productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Pattern Maker tool!",label:"Create Background",gtmValue:"4",subscribeId:45}}],wu={description:"<p>Create eye-catching patterns for online backdrops using our quick and easy background generator.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Pattern Generator Makes Instantly Cool Backgrounds",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/26255880684190648073.png",buttonProps:{label:"Create Background",gtmValue:"1",subscribeId:45,productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Pattern Maker tool!"}},Pu="pattern_maker",Eu=function(){return(Eu=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},xu=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=vu,n=ku,a=wu,i=Pu;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Eu({},a,{screenName:i,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"},isAmp:o})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s seamless Pattern Generator is always ready to help you create beautiful backgrounds for all your images. Instantly take your photos from simple to stunning by layering a unique pattern behind it. Our online pattern generator is easy-to-use and only takes minutes to achieve. Upload your image into PisArt’s Pattern Generator tool, then personalize it with the ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"automatically-edit-tool"},"photo editing tools")," to create a one-of-a-kind edit that you can share with your social media followers. From loud to subtle, there are no rules when it comes to making the backdrop you envision for your photos.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Create Patterned Backdrops",data:r,isAmp:o}))},Tu=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Select Magic Effects from Editing Tools."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a photo or select one of our stock images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Select the cartoon effect you’d like to apply."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Click Download to finish your work."}]],Au=[{description:"<p>With PicsArt’s online cartoon maker your photos are only a single step away from transforming to a cartoon picture. So if you’re looking to figure out how to make a cartoon picture, then you’re in the right place. With PicsArt’s online cartoonizer you don’t have to worry about actually drawing them yourself, learn how to use complicated programs, you don’t even have to check an online tutorial for this. Going from photo to cartoon with PicsArt is as simple as it could possibly get. You just need to select a photo you’d like to cartoonify and with a single click on the Magic effect of your choice, you’re good to go!</p>",title:"Photo to Cartoon in One Click",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/30964759469636242544.png",imageAlt:"cartoonized photo of a happy girl wearing round hat and modern glasses",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Try Cartoonizer",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Nothing shows that you’re easy-going and creative like a good cartoon picture of yourself. Using PicsArt to turn yourself into a cartoon is the best way to introduce some hilarity and fun into your social media presence. One of the best ways to present yourself as approachable and fun is to poke some fun at yourself, and we think using our online cartoon maker is one of the best ways to easily achieve just that. Grab a photo of yourself that you think best shows your bright personality and use one of our many magic effects to turn your photo to cartoon. If you’re still not sure how to make a cartoon picture, then make sure to scroll all the way down to see exactly how easy it is with PicsArt.</p>",title:"Turn Yourself Into a Cartoon",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/28576480156720969688.png",imageAlt:"cartoonized photo of a laughing girl with curly hair standing near beach",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Try Cartoonizer",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Launching an instagram page dedicated to your lovely pets is super trendy these days. Nowadays even our fluffy little pets have the chance to become major influencers on social media. And if you’re looking to boost your pet’s online presence all the way up, then you need to create some seriously catchy images of your pet. Nothing gets people engaging with your pets’ social posts than funny pictures of them in all sorts of goofy ways. You can achieve this level of engagement in seconds with PicsArt’s online cartoon maker. Simply grab a funny photo of your pet and make a cartoon picture of them with our Magic effects.</p>",title:"Cartoonize Your Pet",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/46379465771908069895.png",imageAlt:"cartoonized image of a cat lying on the bad",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Try Cartoonizer",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>PicsArt’s online cartoon maker is one of the most advanced effects on the market. Most editors require you to upload a profile image of yourself to work. With PicsArt’s state-of-the-art infrastructure and <a href="/photo-editor" target="_blank" class="inline-link">online platform</a> you’re not just limited to your profile pictures. You can use our online cartoon maker to literally transform anything into a cartoon with a single click of a button. You can set up a scene in your house then turn it to a cartoon picture to resemble a scene from one of your childhood animations. With  <a href="/photo-effects" target="_blank" class="inline-link">PicsArt’s magic</a> effects you can turn your or your children’s toys into cartoon characters. Our favorite is taking photos of the view from outside our windows and trying different Magic effects to see how it looks. You can even recreate some hilarious cartoon scenes with your friends and apply the effect on top with PicsArt.</p>',title:"Convert Any Picture Into Cartoon",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/51989259389555030564.png",imageAlt:"cartoonized image of a city streets with cars and buildings",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Try Cartoonizer",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>Any one of PicsArt’s Magic effects can be your go-to way to creating art with a single click. You don’t need fancy skills or a degree in art to make full use of PicsArt. Designed ground-up to be incredibly easy-to-use, you can <a href="/photo-effects/photo-into-art" class="inline-link" target="_blank">easily create artworks</a> with no previous experience and post them on your socials. This online cartoonizer is perfect for you to kickstart your journey into photo editing. Start making art with PicsArt’s Magic effects and create the best looking cartoon pictures.</p>',title:"Apply Magic Effects and Make Art",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/61672172021315556389.png",imageAlt:"cartoonized image of a meal on the table ",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Start Making Magic",gtmValue:"6"}}],Nu={description:"<p>Use PicsArt’s online cartoonizer to instantly turn photos into cartoons.</p>",title:"Go From Photo to Cartoon with PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/22166081449592849934.png",imageAlt:"cartoonized image of a man wearing round hat and glasses",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Try Cartoonizer",gtmValue:"1"}},Ou="photos_to_cartoon",_u=!0,ju=function(){return(ju=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Su=Tu,Cu=Au,Ru=Nu,Iu=Ou,Uu=_u,Mu=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Iu),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,ju({},Ru,{screenName:Iu,isPremium:Uu,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Nothing lights up the mood like a good cartoon picture. With PicsArt’s online cartoonizer your photos can go from photo to cartoon in seconds. There’s not a single person out there who hasn’t grown up on cartoons or doesn’t find them hilarious, the second you turn yourself into cartoon using one of PicsArt’s many Magic effects you’re guaranteed to become the talk of your socials. By turning your photo to cartoon online with PicsArt, you’ll be spoiled by all the different available effects. Whether you’re looking to turn your photo to cartoon in classic american pop art style, sketched with a pencil, a touch of surrealism, and more, your choices are endless.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Cu,screenName:Iu,isPremium:Uu,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Go From Photo to Cartoon",data:Su}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Wu=!0,Du="add_audio_to_video",Fu={description:"<p>Select the perfect track and easily add audio to your videos online.</p>",title:"Add Music to Your Videos With PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/62435202164925922806.jpg",imageAlt:"dj night party",bgImage:!0,lightText:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=audio",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Audio to Video",gtmValue:"1"}},Lu=[{description:"<p>Music has the power to enhance your videos and make them more marketable. Transform your social media posts by adding music to your videos. The perfect song will make the video more memorable for your audience, whether it’s on Instagram, Facebook, or your website. Overall, videos with a music track perform better on social media channels and are more engaging than those with no audio. For advertisements or promotional videos, you can use dramatic music that will help evoke emotions in your audience. For more descriptive videos, you can use subtle sounds that will complement the product/service you are showcasing. Our library of stock music and audio tracks offers a wide range of categories you can choose from. Browse through to find the perfect background music for your video. </p>",title:"Add Music to Videos for Social Media ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/85155974037477957820.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=audio",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Music to Video",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Music also fits perfectly in tutorial and explainer videos. Just because there’s speech in your video, doesn’t mean you shouldn’t add music to it as well. In fact, the right background music enhances the spoken voice and engages your listeners on a higher level. This online music video editor is perfect for those who make videos for Youtube, Vimeo, Instagram and even platforms for online courses like Udemy and Coursera. Our large music library has numerous audio tracks that are perfect for these videos.</p>",title:"Background Music for Videos",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/96095573425919467502.jpg",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?tool=audio",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Add Audio to Video",gtmValue:"3"}}],Vu=[{description:"Add audio to your videos directly in your browser. PicsArt’s intuitive and easy-to-use Video Editor allows you to create professional-looking content very quickly. ",title:"Fast Editing"},{description:"Choose an audio track from our large library of free stock music. You’ll find music for any and every occasion, mood, and purpose. Add music to videos online in just a few steps.",title:"Free Stock Music "},{description:"If you have your own track or audio file that you would like to include in your video, simply upload it to PicsArt’s Video Editor and continue editing.",title:"Upload Your Own Track "}],zu=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your audio track or choose one from our free stock music library."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Select the duration of the track and adjust its length."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Save your video and export it to your desktop."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Start sharing!"}]],qu=o(110),Bu=o.n(qu),Hu=function(){return(Hu=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Yu=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=zu,n=Vu,a=Lu,i=Fu,s=Du,c=Wu;return It(s),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Hu({screenName:s,isPremium:c},i,{isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Music is arguably one of the best ways to convey an emotion, set a tone, and create a unique atmosphere. This holds especially true for videos and motion graphics. Without a doubt, music has long played a huge part in visual storytelling. By adding music to videos you can create impactful content that directly resonates with your audience. PicsArt offers a large library of stock music, the option to upload your own track, and handy editing tools that will assist you in achieving the perfect video. From our library, you can choose background music for videos that fit any theme. From up-beat tempos to subtle tunes, we guarantee you’ll find the perfect audio for your video.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{className:Bu.a.productsContainer,productData:a,screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Benefits",dataTests:{title:"promotiontitle",description:"erwarwesertgerfd"}}),l.a.createElement(Ya,{isAmp:o,featuresData:n}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Add Music to a Video",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Gu=[{description:"<p>You’ve booked the date for your special event, now it’s time to create an equally beautiful invitation to go along with it. To get the word out in style (and free), turn to PicsArt’s designer invitation templates. From weddings to birthdays to graduations to anniversaries to engagement parties and more, we’ve got all the details covered. Just pick the template that matches your mood, then customize it to your liking.  </p>",title:"Invitation Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/36718304991590710003.png",imageAlt:"save the date text on a bride and groom wedding invitation template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>To help you get in on the hugely popular meme-making game, PicsArt has created hilarious meme templates to get your ideas trending. Once you’ve got your idea down and are ready to shout it from the rooftops, just use one of our meme templates to bring it to life. Then share it with the social world. Our meme templates are super easy to use and completely customizable.</p>",title:"Meme Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/52931166969987152312.png",imageAlt:"when my friend talks about his girlfriend text on a template with a bored man photo on it",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>When you want to combine a few photos into a single collage, you can use PicsArt’s collage templates. Bring your best memories together with ease by choosing one of our collage templates, then swap the images to make it completely yours. Edit the design until it matches your taste. From exciting birthday party shots to romantic wedding snaps, you can relive all your moments in one place.</p>",title:"Collage Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/80377533996492506238.png",imageAlt:"happy family collage template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:"<p>To get the word out on anything from a sale to a meeting to a company party, turn to PicsArt’s easy-to-use online flyer templates. They’re perfect for more professional events. Make all announcements in style and showcase your brand’s signature aesthetic by personalizing the design aspects to fit your needs. It’ll look like you spent hours on designing, when you just spent minutes!</p>",title:"Flyers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/04057132620102710625.png",imageAlt:"denim sale text on a flyer template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"9"}},{description:"<p>Brochures get the word out about a product or service, so for maximum effectiveness, it’s important for the message and design to look on point. With PicsArt’s brochures templates, you can create something sleek and professional that speaks to your company’s aesthetic. Then use one of our over 200 designer fonts to type out your messaging in style. It’ll get the point across and look good while doing it.</p>",title:"Brochures",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/03057283447378416857.png",imageAlt:"shop now text on a brochure template with a make up goods",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"10"}},{description:"<p>YouTube banner art is the first thing users see when they enter your page, so to make sure it stands out, use PicsArt’s YouTube banner templates to pick a style that pops. Add your own logo or photo, or use one from our extensive image gallery, then edit the design details until you’re happy with the final result. Go back and edit when your signature style needs a new look.</p>",title:"YouTube Banners",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/46744619778131968187.png",imageAlt:"easy and fast diy toy ideas for your kids youtube banner with a sleeping baby on it",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"11"}}],Xu=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Browse through categories and choose a template."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a new picture or choose one from our #FreetoEdit images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Edit text and imagery."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],Qu=[{description:"<p>PicsArt’s design templates are a joy to work with because they’re easy to navigate and completely customizable to your aesthetic. If any part of the template doesn’t speak to you, all you have to do is edit it with new design details until it fits with your event’s theme and look. You can layer on new photos, stickers, shapes, overlays, and text to personalize it your way.  </p>",title:"Templates Are Customizable",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/14050124772326955500.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl with bathing suits swimming in pool",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>What’s better than a designer template? A designer template that’s completely free! With PicsArt’s beautiful templates, you don’t have to pay a dime to get the invitation, collage, flyer, or business brochure you desire. No matter which style you go with for your special event or big announcement, all the gorgeous little details will definitely impress your guests and customers.</p>",title:"They’re Also Free!",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/47295229645129682353.png",imageAlt:"style in a way to say who you are text on a template photo with a man in suite",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>When it comes to personalizing your template, it’s important for the process to be seamless and enjoyable. The goal is for you to be creative while making something stunning. With PicsArt’s easy-to-use templates, you can simply drag and drop your images into the editor with ease. It’s those simple features that make your experience pleasurable.</p>",title:"Try Easy-to-Use Drag-and-Drop Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/46903538960809134632.png",imageAlt:"baby bobby text on a template with a baby boy on it",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>We are proud to have a talented team of designers who are regularly updating templates just for your important life and business events. They make sure to take every single tool and design detail into consideration when creating the perfect template for weddings, anniversaries, birthdays, bridal showers, baby showers, business events, and more. Whether you need invitations, cards, flyers, business brochures, or collages, PicsArt has you fully covered.</p>",title:"Professionally Designed for You",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/63556662220399023715.png",imageAlt:"fashion month text on template with a fashion girl wearing modern glasses and orange make up",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}}],Ku={description:"<p>PicsArt’s free templates are easy to use and fitting for any special occasion.</p>",title:"Anything-But-Basic Design Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/46322149886354257770.png",imageAlt:"blond hair fashion girl photo on trendy template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},$u="design_templates",Ju=!0,Zu="template",ep=function(){return(ep=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},tp=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Xu,n=Gu,a=Qu,i=Ku,s=$u,c=Ju,u=Zu;It(s,u);var p="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,ep({},i,{landingCategory:u,screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Design templates are such a unique — and painless — way to get the word out about your upcoming events, be it a wedding, engagement, birthday, anniversary, or graduation. And PicsArt’s free templates, made specially by our talented in-house designers, don’t disappoint. So the next time you have to send out an invitation or make a brochure, flyer, or photo collage, create something beautiful with one of our easy-to-use graphic design templates.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o,tag:"trending"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:u,productData:a,screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Templates for Any Occasion"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:u,productData:n,screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Edit PicsArt’s Design Templates",data:r}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:p,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,isAmp:o,key:t})}))))},op=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open the Invitation Maker."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Choose a background for your invitation. You can also upload an image of your own."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Personalize the invitation with fonts, stickers, effects, and more."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your finished invitation."}]],rp=[{description:"<p>Custom invitations are essential in getting the word out about upcoming special events, be it for personal or professional reasons. With PicsArt’s Invitation Maker — all completely customizable — you’ll actually have fun designing an invite that speaks to your style and impresses your guests. What’s more, designing invitations online is thankfully super fast, painless — and even highly creative! PicsArt’s Invitation Maker may sound complicated and expensive, but on the contrary, it’s super easy to use and doesn’t cost a penny. All the editing tools and features are ready for you to play around with, even if you have zero designing experience. From fonts to stickers to backgrounds, it’s all at your fingertips 2/47. Get started and before you know it, you’ll be creating something to be proud of. The result is a beautiful custom invitation to invite your guests to any special events in your life. From birthdays to graduations to professional affairs and everything in between, there is no limit to how many invitations you can create with PicsArt.</p>",title:"Design Invitations That Are Easy to Use",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/72925016276207790470.png",imageAlt:"happy girl on a birthday party invitation template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Invitation",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Designing a digital invitation is the perfect way to get your design juices flowing. PicsArt’s Invitation Maker is made for all of the following occasions and more: birthday party invitations, wedding invitations, engagement invitations, bridal shower invitations, baby shower invitations, graduation invitations, anniversary invitations, and baptism invitations. Once you’re ready to embark on your journey of creating an invitation from home, PicsArt’s Invitation Maker will give you the opportunity to customize the design, text, and colors of your invitations to make sure it stands out and speaks to your unique style. Use our handy tools in our Template Editor will assist you in making something one-of-a-kind and special that reflects all the little details of your event. We have over 200 unique fonts to choose from and millions of free stickers that will take your custom invitation to the next level. You can also search within our endless #FreetoEdit image library for inspiring ideas.</p>",title:"Invitation Maker Is Fully Customizable",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/91930938414720567467.png",imageAlt:"bridal shower invitation template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Invitation",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Take a second and imagine the difference between getting a basic invitation and receiving a fully personalized invitation. The difference is huge and it doesn’t take much time to create a customized invitation that will set you apart. Your custom invitation may feature a photo of you, design details that are unique to your taste, and text that you can custom create to convey your message in style. PicsArt’s Invitation Maker is available to use for everyone and for any occasion. Whether it’s a birthday party, anniversary dinner, business retreat, large or intimate wedding, baby or bridal shower, graduation bash, or anything about in between, you can create the most eye-catching custom invitation that will announce your affair in major style. From subtle to bold, you can make a beautifully designed invitation that will go with the aesthetic of your event.</p>",title:"Customize Invitations for Any Occasion",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/11365272065653499577.png",imageAlt:"invitation template with save the date text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Invitation",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Making your own invitations doesn’t have to be complicated, and with PicsArt’s invitation templates, it’s even easier. If you’d rather get some help in the design department, our ready-to-use invitation templates are a great option for you. First, start by searching for the invitation template that fits your affair’s desired aesthetic, then personalize the invitation to suit your style. We have templates for all kinds of occasions, plus colors and designs that will match the mood of your party or special event. The customizing process for the design-your-own invitation is super user-friendly. All the tools you need are available in the toolbar, so that’s a good place to start. You can change the background (pick a new color or an image), text (we have over 200+ impressive fonts to choose from), add stickers (of just about anything you can imagine!), and layer on a new photo. You can also search for online invitations according to social media size standards.</p>",title:"Try a Wide Array of Invitation Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/33412082485420111325.png",imageAlt:"techno party invitation template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Invitation",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Invitation Maker houses endless easy-to-use editing tools that you can play around with to create something special with zero professional skills. From newbies to even experienced editors, you will enjoy the painless process from start to finish. From designer fonts to fun stickers to useful icons, a variety of colors, and many other design features, there is no limit to what you can create with PicArt’s Invitation Maker. What’s more, our extensive #FreetoEdit image library allows you to incorporate any image in our network. Or you can upload an image from your own library. With PicsArt, you have unlimited options. Play around with all the design tools available at your fingertips until you’re happy with the result. Once you’re all done, your custom invitation is ready to be sent out and admired.</p>",title:"Create Invitations With No Professional Skills",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/10669368009543715241.png",imageAlt:"pajama party invitation template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Invitation",gtmValue:"6"}}],np={description:"<p>Create invitations for all the special occasions in your life with our easy-to-use custom invitations.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Online Invitation Maker Is Fast & Easy for Everyone",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/77858939591197813110.png",imageAlt:"birthday party invitation template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=invitation",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Invitation",gtmValue:"1"}},ap="invitation_maker",ip=!0,sp=function(){return(sp=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},lp=op,cp=rp,up=np,pp=ap,dp=ip,mp=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(pp),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,sp({},up,{screenName:pp,isPremium:dp,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"With PicsArt’s Invitation Maker, you’ll never create a dull custom invitation ever. With our easy-to-use tools and features all at your fingertips, you are fully equipped to design something extra special and stylish to impress your guests. Create invitations online without having to spend a fortune. Do it all for without paying a dime with the help of our handy Invitation Maker. From birthdays to anniversaries to weddings to baby showers and all of the special moments that are worthy of celebrating, PicsArt will help you make something you’ll be proud to send out and show off.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:cp,screenName:pp,isPremium:dp,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make Invitations",data:lp}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},hp=[{description:"<p>Event posters are a great way to put your message out there in style. Whether it’s an upcoming conference, festival, birthday party, graduation dinner, or a festive holiday affair, PicsArt’s poster templates are the perfect way to get the word out. Our talented team has created a collection of stunning poster templates that you and your audience will be impressed with. Personalization is the name of the game with PicsArt, so once you choose the template you like, you can completely alter it to suit your preferences. Add stickers, effects, text, colors, and backgrounds that match the mood of the event or occasion. Our editing tools are super easy to navigate, so you don’t need to be a pro to create your own poster with PicsArt.</p>",title:"Announce Special Events With Stylish Poster Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/11573329150245966343.png",imageAlt:"music fest design poster template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Inspirational posters with meaningful quotes or statements are super popular on social media. Anytime you have a motivational message to put out there, be it for personal or business purposes, you can do so with the help of PicsArt’s poster templates. It’ll only take a few minutes but the impact will be everlasting. We’ve designed a handful of motivational poster templates to guide you in creating something truly special for your audiences. Pick the template that speaks to you, then customize it by adding your message or quote using one of our stylish fonts. From simple to bold, there is a font design that will match your message. Once you’re done, post your new motivational poster to your social feed to get the conversation started.</p>",title:"Make Motivational Posters With the Help of PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/89330551792742171841.png",imageAlt:"it's never too late to focus on your dream poster template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Campaign posters can convey your stance on issues and spread awareness out into the world. PicsArt’s thoughtful poster templates help you with putting out the good word by taking on the design aspect for you. To that end, advertising posters are also a great way to get your message out about a new product or service. Pick a template that’s suited to your signature style, then customize it with our easy-to-use editing tools. Make an impactful poster by adding text with beautiful fonts and stylish effects. No matter the topic or issue, PicsArt can help you create something meaningful in minutes.</p>",title:"Create Impactful Campaign Posters for Professional Settings",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/59875464082089921902.png",imageAlt:"hang in there better days are coming poster template design",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Music posters are here to help you announce any kind of musical or concert event in style. With music concerts being jovial affairs, PicsArt has created a collection of stylish, sleek, and bold poster templates that will definitely stand out from the crowd. From jazz to rock to pop and festivals to concerts to more intimate outdoor events, there is the perfect poster template that will match your event’s musical mood. Go through the collection to pick your favorite template, then personalize its details to announce your upcoming show with pizazz. Add stickers, effects, fonts, and colors to create an even more one-of-a-kind invite.</p>",title:"Make Music With Bold and Sleek Concert Posters",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/04563338837091718607.png",imageAlt:"jazz orchestra festival poster template design",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s beautiful movie posters are the ultimate way to promote your short film. They’re fully customizable to match your movie’s unique theme. Find the perfect font to convey the message of your movie title and any other details you will include on your movie poster. Use our editing tools to create a one-of-a-kind poster using fonts, stickers, effects, icons, and backgrounds. Share on social media or print your high-quality movie poster for show off in real life. Not a filmmaker? Not to worry. You can also use our movie poster templates to create personalized posters for your favorite flicks to share on social media. </p>",title:"Larger-Than-Life Movie Posters to Match Your Favorite Flicks",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/24784250550090952601.png",imageAlt:"old film night poster template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"6"}}],gp={description:"<p>Choose from a collection of high-quality poster design templates and customize your picks for any occasion.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Poster Templates Are Always Ready for You",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/09780342497984850119.png",imageAlt:"summer art exhibition poster template design",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"1"}},fp="poster_templates",yp=!0,bp="template",vp=function(){return(vp=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},kp=hp,wp=gp,Pp=fp,Ep=yp,xp=bp,Tp=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;It(Pp,xp);var r="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,vp({},wp,{landingCategory:xp,screenName:Pp,isPremium:Ep,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt has created a beautiful collection of poster templates that are ready to use anytime and for any event. From simple to eye-catching, there is a stunning poster template that’s suited for your business or brand. Choose the template that speaks to your specific needs, then fully customize it to match the aesthetic you’re going for. Use PicsArt’s handy editing tools to add text, stickers, effects, colors, and more for a one-of-a-kind finish. Then post your new creation to your social media channels, blog, and website.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:Pp,isPremium:Ep,isAmp:o,tag:"tags/poster"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:xp,productData:kp,screenName:Pp,isPremium:Ep,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:r,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},isAmp:o,productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,key:t})}))))},Ap=[{description:'<p>Why buy a basic holiday greeting card that everyone has when you can make your own unique one with PicsArt? To kick off this advent calendar, it’s time for you to make your very own holiday greeting card(s)! Whether you celebrate Christmas, Hanukkah, or Kwanzaa, or prefer to make a winter wonderland card, you can customize your card with seasonal <a href="/sticker-maker" target="_blank" class="inline-link">stickers,</a> effects, shapes, <a href="/text-editor" target="_blank" class="inline-link">fonts,</a> and more quick & easy editing tools. You can even make a different one customized for every recipient!</p>',title:"Day 1: Make a Holiday Greeting Card",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/09825602095087728615.png",imageAlt:"wish you joy this holiday - a holiday greeting card ",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Make a Holiday Card",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Anyone up for a challenge? Great, because Day 2 is all about this fun Snow Globe Replay Challenge. ☃️  Because it’s a Replay, it’s quick and easy to make the most amazing snow globe featuring YOU (or anyone you love)! Every snowflake is different, so don’t forget that you can manually edit anything in a Replay to make the edit custom for you. Shake it up with as many cute and cozy details as you like— and we’ll be over here crossing our fingers for you to win! 🤞🏾</p>",title:"Day 2: Snow Globe Replay Challenge",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/79025462306384725849.png",imageAlt:"boy wearing glasses and round hat is posing inside a christmas themed globe with snowman and presents",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/i/345208214002203?edit_history=1",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/bg7QDBlLTbb ",label:"Start Snow Globe Challenge",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Haven’t written a letter to Santa in ages? Well, now’s your chance! Use holiday templates, stickers, and fonts to spill your heart out to 🎅 (or conveniently print it out for your significant other to find, 😉) using our <a href="/editing-tools" target="_blank" class="inline-link">quick & easy photo editing tools.</a> Use our unique holiday fonts to type out your list or message, then finish with some festive stickers to really capture Santa’s heart. 💓 We’ll make sure it gets delivered to him on time. 😉</p>',title:"Day 3: Write a Letter to Santa",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/96889436034702491453.png",imageAlt:"write a letter to santa template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/bCazYYtr6bb",label:"Start My Letter Now",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>2020 might have thrown off your chances to win the annual ugly holiday sweater competition at work or school 😠 but it will not cancel this: our online ugly holiday sweater challenge! Layer as many crazy stickers, effects, and fonts as you can possibly imagine. Wrap it in ribbons or top it with bows and bells. The uglier the better! 🤪</p>",title:"Day 4: Ugly Holiday Sweater Challenge",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/71313756877914314963.png",imageAlt:"man in an ugly holiday sweater posing",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:{title:"Download PicsArt Photo & Video Editor App For Free",stores:[{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38297334288968341477.png",icon:"apple-mono-gen",storeName:"App Store"},{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38297334288968341477.png",icon:"google-play-brand",storeName:"Google Play"},{qr:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38297334288968341477.png",icon:"microsoft-brand",storeName:"Microsoft Store"}]},mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/tbXINNqLTbb ",label:"Make My Ugly Sweater",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>We’re all about that DIY life! If you’re spending hours crafting the perfect gift for that special someone, then don’t skimp on the gift tag. They should know who it’s from! With PicsArt’s <a href="/editing-tools" target="_blank" class="inline-link">photo editing tools</a> at your fingertips, Day 5 is all about using stickers, effects, shapes, fonts, and more to create custom gift tags. They can reflect the gift, the giver, or the recipient. Just print off your gift tags and tie them onto all of your presents as you spread yuletide cheer. </p>',title:"Day 5: Make Your Own Gift Tags",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/94809360323969052517.png",imageAlt:"christmas holiday red gift tag with a christmas tree ",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/search/stickers?q=gift%20tag",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Make Custom Gift Tag",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>With holiday celebrations going virtual this year, why not celebrate Hanukkah both at home and online? Menorahs have eight holders for oil or candles, plus an additional holder. For this project, use candle stickers, lights brushes, and cozy filters to bring light and warmth into your home. Light a virtual menorah and have a Happy Hanukkah (December 10-18 this year)! 🕎</p>",title:"Day 6: Bright Lights",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/41523560029509660589.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl in a red holiday sweater sitting around bright lights",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9 ",label:"Create Hanukkah Edit",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>Level up all those selfies taken at home this year by transforming yourself into an elf! Just upload a photo of yourself (or a friend), then add our elf ear stickers to take your selfie from simple to spirited in no time. You can add cool effects, text, or change the background to transport yourself to Santa’s workshop. Go all-out wild with your elf-ie. 🧝‍♂️🤳🏼</p>",title:"Day 7: Elf Yourself",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/69643202105400593962.png",imageAlt:"happy girl with elf ears",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/hashtag/elf%20ears/most-edited-stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/t77uVWIr6bb",label:"Make Me an Elf",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:'<p>It’s time to express gratitude for someone special in your life. After all, the holidays are all about spreading joy and being thankful for everyone from grandparents and roommates to essential workers. 🥰 Since we can’t travel to see our loved ones this year, we can still send them something thoughtfully sweet and guaranteed to arrive in time! 😔 Use our <a href="/video-editor" target="_blank" class="inline-link">Video Editor</a> to create a heartfelt video message in-app or online. Dress it up with stickers, text, music, and effects you think they’ll appreciate. </p>',title:"Day 8: Make a Thank You Video",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/73037140918208375080.png",imageAlt:"man creating a thank you video with a phone",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/cWCgZQfpSbb ",label:"Send Thanks Now",gtmValue:"9"}},{description:"<p>So long, 2020! 👋🏼 It’s time to send this year off! Not going out this year? Our New Year’s Sparkler Challenge will bring the party to you. 🎉 Instantly light up any photo and create a spotlight-worthy edit in seconds with the addition of sparkler stickers, brushes, masks, and filters. Make your New Year’s social posts sizzle with a stunning selfie, made even more radiant in time for the new year! ✨</p>",title:"Day 9: New Year’s Sparkler Challenge",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/53168298070684140454.png",imageAlt:"happy curly hair girl smiling and holding sparkling fireworks in her hands",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=overlay",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Tjri3HxLTbb",label:"Start Sparkler Challenge",gtmValue:"10"}}],Np={landingData:Ap,bannerData:{description:"<p>Create joy with awesome edits inspired by PicsArt’s 2020 Advent Calendar, using our popular web tools and in-app features.</p>",title:"Create Joy With PicsArt’s Advent Calendar",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/39918526818194705752.png",imageAlt:"happy blond hair girl posing in the snow holding christmas tree stickers",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9 ",label:"Start Editing",gtmValue:"1"}},screenName:"advent_calendar",isPremium:!0},Op=function(){return(Op=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},_p=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Np.landingData,n=Np.bannerData,a=Np.screenName,i=Np.isPremium;return It(a),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Op({},n,{screenName:a,isPremium:i,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"The holidays are the perfect time to wrap gifts, bake gingerbread cookies, bundle up in warm knits, and sip a delicious peppermint hot cocoa by the fireplace. To help spread yuletide cheer, we went to Santa’s editing workshop and cobbled together a nine-day advent calendar chock full of seasonal activities. Except, it’s 2020. So instead of making you unlock one activity per day, we’re giving them all to you at once to kickstart your editing! From making your own holiday greeting cards and gift tags to participating in jolly editing challenges like adding snowy stickers to your selfies, you’re guaranteed to have a blast both on PicsArt web and in-app. We hope these creative holiday projects will make your time at home a little more festive and fun this year!")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:r,screenName:a,isPremium:i,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},jp=[[{index:1,pointDescription:'In a Slack message, enter “/picsart thanksgiving." You can also enter "Christmas," "Kwanzaa," "Hanukkah," or "2020." If you enter any other words, content related to these phrases will appear.'},{index:2,pointDescription:"Click “Shuffle” to see options to send"}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Click “Send” to share the greeting card"},{index:4,pointDescription:"Clicking “Cancel” will cancel the process"}]],Sp=[{description:"<p>PicsArt is the world’s #1 creative platform and social editing app leading the visual storytelling revolution with more than 150 million monthly active creators. To dress up your Slack messages, we’re bringing virtual greeting cards that are wickedly funny and awesome for the 2020 holiday season! Send them to your favorite friends & colleagues for fun! </p>",title:"",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/65959113610013451837.png",imageAlt:"Card template with a man wrapped up in a toilet paper and a halloween text on it",buttonProps:{url:"https://slack.com/oauth/v2/authorize?client_id=2777428522.1476597796416&scope=commands&user_scope=",mobileUrl:"https://slack.com/oauth/v2/authorize?client_id=2777428522.1476597796416&scope=commands&user_scope=",label:"Add to Slack",gtmValue:"2"}}],Cp={description:"<p>Send and receive a variety of fun greeting cards in your messages to your colleagues. Try PicsArt!</p>",title:"PicsArt Keyboard for Slack",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/15708239083610189445.png",imageAlt:"Halloween card template with pink witch brooms and text on it ",buttonProps:{url:"https://slack.com/oauth/v2/authorize?client_id=2777428522.1476597796416&scope=commands&user_scope=",mobileUrl:"https://slack.com/oauth/v2/authorize?client_id=2777428522.1476597796416&scope=commands&user_scope=",label:"Add to Slack",gtmValue:"1"}},Rp="PicsArt_Slack",Ip="apps",Up=function(){return(Up=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Mp=jp,Wp=Sp,Dp=Cp,Fp=Rp,Lp=Ip,Vp=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Fp),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Up({},Dp,{landingCategory:Lp,screenName:Fp,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:Lp,productData:Wp,screenName:Fp,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Use PicsArt on Slack",data:Mp}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},zp=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload a photo (or choose from our free-to-edit options), preferably a portrait of a person against a fairly neutral background to create the perfect Double Exposure effect"},{index:2,pointDescription:"Select “Add Photo” to add a second image. To avoid too many contrasting colors, it’s preferable to choose a black-and-white picture"},{index:3,pointDescription:"Adjust the size of your second image to fit it over your portrait. Reduce the opacity to make it semi-transparent"}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Experiment with different overlay modes to blend them in different ways and create the double exposure photography style"},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download your work"}]],qp={description:"<p>Double exposure portraits give plain selfies and close-ups completely new dimensions. As an example, with the Double Exposure effect, you can choose to add a photo of a skyline or a busy street over your portrait to give it a slick city vibe. There are no rules when it comes to double exposure photography, so experiment with your work. This form of photography has been around for quite some time, and has definitely gained traction among creative industries. You’ve most likely seen double exposure used on album covers, movie posters, and magazines. Start creating your own designs by following the tutorial down below.  </p>",title:"Double Exposure Photography Made Easy ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/11090474176999179093.png",imageAlt:"girl with tattoos and glasses with double exposure effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-exposure",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/d6DaOiijt8",label:"Try Double Exposure!",gtmValue:"2"}},Bp=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload a photo or choose one from our free-to-edit images."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Select a color scheme and apply it to your image."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Edit the opacity, brightness, saturation, and contrast of the second layer."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Adjust the positioning of the second layer."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],Hp={description:"<p> If you want the Double Exposure effect with only one image, try PicsArt’s Color Exposure quick tool. Simply upload an image and let PicsArt do the magic. Once the Color Exposure effect is applied, you can choose from numerous color schemes that will liven up your image. You can adjust the opacity, brightness, saturation, and contrast of your image to reach your desired outcome. </p>",title:"You Can Also Try Color Exposure ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/50415282919159639605.png",imageAlt:"closed eyes girl face with double exposure effect",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-exposure",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/d6DaOiijt8",label:"Try Color Exposure!",gtmValue:"3"}},Yp={description:"<p>The Double Exposure effect of combining two images into one can create captivating works of art.</p>",title:"Dabble in Double Exposure",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/88579681064552249841.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-exposure",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/d6DaOiijt8",label:"Try Double Exposure Now!",gtmValue:"1"}},Gp="double_exposure",Xp=!0,Qp=function(){return(Qp=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Kp=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=qp,n=Bp,a=zp,i=Hp,s=Yp,c=Gp,u=Xp;return It(c),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Qp({},s,{screenName:c,isPremium:u,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"You may be wondering what double exposure is exactly. Double exposure is the act of combining two photos into a single image, creating something even more impressive and artistic than the original version. It sounds complicated, but the process — also called multiple exposure — is actually pretty simple. Just add a photo, layer on another image, and play around with"," ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages",className:"inline-link",target:"_blank"},"PicsArt’s handy tools")," to make magic.")}),l.a.createElement("div",null,l.a.createElement(pr,Qp({description:r.description,buttonProps:r.buttonProps,imageUrl:r.imageUrl,title:r.title,screenName:c,isPremium:u,isAmp:o},r))),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Do Double Exposure",data:a}),l.a.createElement("div",null,l.a.createElement(pr,Qp({description:i.description,buttonProps:i.buttonProps,imageUrl:i.imageUrl,title:i.title,screenName:c,isPremium:u,isAmp:o},i))),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Do Color Exposure",data:n}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},$p=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your video."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Click on the “Text” button."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Select a font and input your content."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download the output video and share!"}]],Jp=[{description:"PicsArt’s Video Editor has a large library of custom text fonts. You will surely find the perfect font that fits your video. \n",title:"Library of Fonts"},{description:"Upload your videos in MOV, MP4, AVI, WEBM, FLV, and more. Our Video Editor supports the most popular video formats. \n",title:"Multiple Video Formats Supported\n"},{description:"PicsArt’s Video Editor is very easy to use. Our intuitive layout allows you to quickly navigate from one tool to another. \n",title:"Easy-to-Use Interface"}],Zp=[{description:"<p>Level up your social media content by adding text to your videos. Whether you’re an influencer, business, or a vlogger, you can easily create impressive content for your followers. Adding text to videos will enforce the message you are trying to send and make it stick with your audience. With PicsArt, you can easily prep your videos for social media channels like Facebook, Instagram, and YouTube. Quickly add text to your videos - select the font, color, styling, and placement of your words and start spreading your message! </p>",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/80667499157378797214.jpg",title:"Add Text to Videos for Social Media",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=text_to_video&tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Add Text to Video",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Adding subtitles to your videos has numerous benefits. First, people are consistently flooded with content on their timelines, regardless of the social media platform they use, a great way to capture their attention is by using subtitles. Since it’s not always convenient for people to turn on their audio while scrolling through their phones, subtitles are a great way to keep your audience engaged and informed. As an example, numerous studies have shown people watch 85% of Facebook videos on mute. You can see why having subtitles can be beneficial for your marketing efforts. Second, a great reason to add subtitles to your videos is that you won’t exclude the fraction of your audience that may have hearing impairments. </p>",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/76918941968363329794.jpg",title:"Easily Add Subtitles to Your Videos\n",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=text_to_video&tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Add Text to Video",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Adding words to your videos can truly drive visual storytelling to another level. You can easily emphasize key aspects of your message by simply adding text to your videos. You can enlarge key words and phrases, apply a unique color to them, increase their size, and strategically place them throughout your video. To optimize your video for marketing, make sure to <a href="/trim-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="trim-your-video-hypertext">trim your video.</a> You can even <a href="/add-music-to-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="add-audio-hypertext">add audio</a> to make it more engaging. Once you’re done editing, start promoting your business content on your blog, website, or any social media channel. \n</p>',imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/92312430846628986559.jpg",title:"Create Promotional Videos",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=text_to_video&tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Add Text to Video",gtmValue:"4"}}],ed="text_to_video",td={description:"<p>Easily add text to videos online to achieve stunning edits. </p>",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/18456439128095280857.jpg",title:"Add Text to Your Videos With PicsArt",imageAlt:"boy in a greenery",lightText:!0,bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=text_to_video&tool=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Add Text to Video",gtmValue:"1"}},od=!0,rd=function(){return(rd=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},nd=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=$p,n=Jp,a=Zp,i=td,s=ed,c=od;return It(s),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,rd({},i,{screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{dataTests:{title:"promotiontitle",description:"description data test"},isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Adding text to a video can give it a whole new dimension. PicsArt offers a large library of premium fonts that will visually elevate any text and paragraph. Use this quick tool to add subtitles to your videos, insert explanations, add titles, descriptions, and call to action buttons in your videos.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:a,screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Benefits",dataTests:{title:"title data test",description:"description data test"}}),l.a.createElement(Ya,{isAmp:o,featuresData:n}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Add Text to a Video",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},ad=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Select one of our flyer templates."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload your images or choose from our #FreetoEdit options."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Swap out the text in the template and adjust the layout."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Once you finish, download your work."}]],id=[{description:"<p>Throwing a party is fun, but creating a one-of-a-kind party flyer with PicsArt’s flyer templates keeps the fun going. You should first take into account every single detail of your affair (color scheme, theme, props, etc.) and then convey it in style with your personalized flyer. Start by searching for the perfect template that fits the day’s theme (we have tons and tons to choose from), then edit any design detail you need to in order to create the perfect look that you and your guest list will be satisfied with. Whether you’re hosting a nighttime dance party, a cozy and quaint dinner party, a daytime bridal shower, or a black-tie affair, you’ll find a flyer template that will suit your taste.</p>",title:"Have a Blast With Party Flyer Templates\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/65091101084039884445.png",imageAlt:"your beach club is hrere summer flyer template with happy girls on it",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>When it comes to picking flyer templates, there’s time for fun, then there’s a time to be more professional. For business-related events, we have a plethora of sleek and subtle flyer templates to get the word out to your clients and customers. Be it a business lunch meeting, a charity banquet, an employee baby shower, or a friendly tennis tournament, PicsArt has event flyer templates that will appeal to your work audience. Whether it’s a large, medium or small event, the template you choose — and then personalize your way — will definitely draw a crowd. You can choose to pull in your brand logo or any other images to complete the look.</p>",title:"Spread the Word With Event Flyer Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/40846409789350377000.png",imageAlt:"happy galentines day flyer template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>When it comes time to promote a product or service, you want your flyer to make a major impact. In that case, you can turn to PicsArt’s flyer templates to help you get the word out with ease and style, no matter how grand or subtle your marketing plan. Whether you want to make a big announcement about a new store opening, shout out a new chef at your eatery, or let the public know about a hot new book release, you can do so by picking the perfect flyer template. Then just edit the design details to match the look of your brand or company and share across all your social media channels. Once you go this painless and free route, you’ll be back to promote your next product with PicsArt.</p>",title:"Promote Your Product With Marketing Flyer Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/62175558126883917785.png",imageAlt:"online handmade shop flyer template",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Real estate flyers can be just as exciting as party flyers — and just as fun and quick to create. All you need to do is turn to PicsArt’s easy-to-use flyer templates to help you design the look and feel you’re going for your next sale. Pull in as many photos of the property you’ll be promoting, then personalize the design details to match the house by changing up the color scheme, adding a background, and layering on text with all the important details with over 200 stylish fonts. The creative possibilities are endless. Once you get the process down, it’ll be your new favorite way to feature your future sales.</p>",title:"Sell in Style With Real Estate Flyer Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/58282100336941153597.png",imageAlt:"city center houses, real estate flyer template design",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"5"}}],sd="flyer_template",ld={description:"<p>With our customizable flyer templates, you can create online content to get the news out about everything from events to sales to updates. \n</p>",title:"Get the Word out With PicsArt’s Flyer Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/50090881696580128476.png",imageAlt:"furniture house dinale sale text on a flyer template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},cd=!0,ud="template",pd=function(){return(pd=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},dd=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=ad,n=id,a=ld,i=sd,s=cd,c=ud;It(i,c);var u="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,pd({},a,{landingCategory:c,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"At PicsArt, you can find flyers for any occasion. We can help you create everything from event flyers, professional flyers with our business flyer templates, or fun flyers with our party flyer templates. Our talented designers don’t overlook any detail and are constantly adding new templates just for you. So the next time you need to get the word out about an exciting sale or store opening, turn to PicsArt’s flyer templates to help you do it with style and ease.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,tag:"tags/flyer"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:c,productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create Flyers With PicsArt’s Flyer Templates",data:r}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:u,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,isAmp:o,key:t})}))))},md=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your images and videos."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Trim your footage as necessary."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Start organizing your content in your preferred order."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Once you finish sequencing, apply transitions or add music to your slideshow."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download the output video and start sharing! "}]],hd=[{description:"<p>Easily create slideshows for your internal presentations, promotions, and marketing activities! Slideshows are the perfect way to group material, format thoughts, and even  introduce your business to a new audience. Showcase your products and services through unique slideshows, or recap events you’ve participated in. You can easily design beautiful video slideshows and use them on your website, in your email marketing campaigns, or for internal communication within your business.</p>",title:"Business Slideshows",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/51535190926171639169.png",imageAlt:"skin care tender hands and feet photo collage",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Gather  remarkable moments from the most important events of your life and create a video slideshow with PicsArt! Whether it’s a wedding, graduation, a birthday celebration, or any other milestone you’ve achieved - all are deserving of a beautifully designed slideshow. Our online slideshow maker will help you eternalize your memories. Easily create photo slideshows to share with your friends and family members. You can also incorporate video footage from events to make your slideshows more lively. PicsArt’s slideshow maker will help make all of your memories even more special.</p>",title:"Celebrations of Life - Wedding, Graduation, Birthday Slideshows and More",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/17309132619655514742.png",imageAlt:"happy girls in festive dresses laughing",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>Slideshows are the perfect addition to your social media content catalogue. Engaging, fun, and memorable - transform your simple posts and stories into well-thought-out and formatted content. Whether you’re creating slideshows for your personal social media account or for promoting your business, PicsArt’s slideshow maker allows you to optimize the size and contents of your posts. Instead of posting multiple pictures and videos, you can easily group your content into short slideshows - which are far more engaging to your audience. You can easily <a href="/resize-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="resize-your-videos-hypertext">resize your videos</a> for social media channels like Instagram, YouTube, and Facebook. </p>',title:"Social Media Slideshows",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/70395485721010494683.png",imageAlt:"Palm purple hair happy girl and dog photo collage",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"7"}}],gd=[{description:'<p>Whether you have images you’d like to incorporate in your slideshow, or videos you’ve taken, PicsArt’s slideshow maker allows you to seamlessly combine both to achieve stunning results. Our <a href="/video-editor" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="video-ditor-hypertext">Video Editor</a> provides all the necessary editing tools for you to achieve the perfect slideshow. Easily trim your footage, apply transitions, and add text to your video to drive your message home. Our slideshow maker is perfect for creating content that celebrates any and every important milestone or event.</p>',title:"Easily Combine Images and Videos With Our Online Slideshow Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/79414931209268286790.png",imageAlt:"happy summer girls photo collage with cool girls text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Editing can truly become a time consuming task if the tools you’re using are not easy to work with . With the wrong software, editing a simple slideshow could turn into a day's work. Luckily, PicsArt’s Video Editor has an intuitive interface and many tools that will make the editing process easy and fun. You won’t have to spend hours trying to figure out how to edit your content. </p>",title:"Save Your Time With Our Slideshow Creator",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/61477910679295106817.png",imageAlt:"short hair girl with different styles photo collage",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>The best way to elevate your slideshows is - of course, by <a href="/add-music-to-video" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="adding-music-hypertext">adding music.</a> The right audio track can have a lasting impact on your audience and make the slideshow even more memorable. PicsArt offers you a large library of stock music tracks. Choose from a number of genres and beats to add to your slideshow. You can instantly liven up a basic photo slideshow with the correct choice of music.</p>',title:"Put Our Slideshow Maker With Music to Use",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/83141348150760055359.png",imageAlt:"dj style photo collage with disco lights",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"4"}}],fd={description:"<p>Our easy-to-use slideshow creator will help you make memorable video and photo slideshows.</p>",title:"Create Beautiful Stories With PicsArt’s Online Slideshow Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/59637063983059399183.jpg",imageAlt:"modern black hair girl with glasses and hat posing",bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/uMgPdWxnt8",label:"Create Slideshow",gtmValue:"1"}},yd="slideshow_maker",bd=!0,vd=function(){return(vd=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},kd=md,wd=gd,Pd=hd,Ed=fd,xd=yd,Td=bd,Ad=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(xd),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,vd({},Ed,{screenName:xd,isPremium:Td,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s free slideshow maker provides you with all the necessary tools to create professional-looking slideshows. You can opt for creating a simple photo slideshow by uploading images and sequencing them, or you can mix photo and video footage to diversify your content. Our video slideshow maker allows you to easily create slideshows within minutes. Whether you’re creating a slideshow of your family memories, footage from important events, or for your business, slideshow videos are, without a doubt, a great way to share experiences in a unique format.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:wd,screenName:xd,isPremium:Td,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Check Out the Most Popular Slideshow Categories"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Pd,screenName:xd,isPremium:Td,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a Slideshow ",data:kd}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Nd=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open PicsArt’s Wallpaper Maker. "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a photo or use one of our #FreetoEdit images. "}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Add a personal touch using PicsArt’s photo editing tools. "},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your wallpaper and upload it to your devices."}]],Od=[{description:'<p>PicsArt’s Wallpaper Maker makes it easy to create the wallpaper of your dreams — and the best part is that it’s completely free. Whether you’re looking to update your desktop or phone background, we can help you design something that will stand out among a sea of standard wallpapers. Looking for something simple and soothing? Want something bold and colorful? Need something trendy and timely? No matter your desired aesthetic, PicsArt’s wallpaper creator lets you create it in minutes. You can use an image from our extensive #FreetoEdit collection or upload your own photo to customize with <a href="/editing-tools" class="inline-link" target="_blank">PicsArt’s quick & easy photo editing tools.</a></p>',title:"Design Amazing & Free Wallpapers in No Time",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/12208770124462001152.png",imageAlt:"phones with creative colorful wallpaper",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Wallpaper",gtmValue:"2",subscribeId:47,productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Wallpaper Maker Tool!"}},{description:"<p>Is it time to change up the background of your phone and/or desktop? PicsArt’s Wallpaper Maker is a great and fast way to update the background of your preferred devices. That means you can switch up your wallpaper as many times as you want without wasting any time. With the constant use of phones and computers these days, isn’t it better to stare at a beautiful backdrop instead of a basic one? Let PicsArt help you create a wallpaper design that you won’t want to take your eyes off of. Try one of our striking wallpaper templates or make your own wallpaper design that speaks to your one-of-a-kind style or current mood. Have a favorite photo that would look amazing as a phone or desktop backdrop? Just upload it to PicsArt and within minutes you can turn it into the perfect wallpaper. </p>",title:"Wallpaper Ideas for Your Phone & Desktop",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/45042306024656066217.png",imageAlt:"phone and laptop with creative colorful flamingo wallpaper",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{label:"Make a Wallpaper",gtmValue:"3",subscribeId:47,productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Wallpaper Maker Tool!"}},{description:"<p>Want to change up your phone or desktop’s wallpaper but short on time? Just choose from one of PicsArt’s extensive wallpaper templates to switch things up in minutes. From simple desktop wallpapers to pretty floral desktop wallpapers to Christmas desktop wallpapers, you can find a beautiful desktop wallpaper that will work for your signature style, desired theme, and mood. Keep the template design as is or customize any of the details using PicsArt’s quick & easy photo editing tools. Add cool effects, fun stickers, stylish text to speak your mind, and so much more to make create something that is truly one-of-a-kind. </p>",title:"Try Tons of Wallpaper Templates to Save Time",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/08200938587001223413.png",imageAlt:"phones with winter christmas and seasonal wallpaper templates",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"See Wallpaper Templates",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>Not sure what background to go with? That’s where PicsArt’s <a href="/pattern-generator" class="inline-link" target="_blank">Pattern Generator tool</a> comes in and saves the day — and you! Just upload a photo that you would like to use for your desktop or phone’s backdrop, then let smart technology work its magic and deliver a fun new background. If you’re not feeling it, no problem, just keep utilizing this impressive tool to get new options until you find the background that works for you. Once you do, you can save the creation or customize it using <a href="/editing-tools" class="inline-link" target="_blank">PicsArt’s quick & easy editing tools.</a></p>',title:"Let PicsArt’s Pattern Generator Do the Work",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/71843547895949914532.png",imageAlt:"christmas pattern templates of christmas trees, acorns and snowflakes",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{label:"Create Wallpaper",gtmValue:"5",subscribeId:47,productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Wallpaper Maker Tool!"}},{description:"<p>Got something on your mind? Easily spotlight your thoughts on your computer or phone by adding text to your personalized wallpaper with PicsArt. Start by searching for the perfect font that will help you speak your mind in style — there are 200+ unique options to peruse. Whether your message is short or long, PicsArt’s creative collection of fonts will make sure that your words shine. Once you pick the perfect font for you, then you can choose to change its color, blend it, play with its opacity, add shadows, and do so much more in the PicsArt photo editor.</p>",title:"Easily Layers Text on Any Wallpaper",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/88003532526984927327.png",imageAlt:"girl hands holding the phone and showing the phone wallpaper template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Add Text to Wallpaper",gtmValue:"6"}}],_d={description:"<p>PicsArt’s Wallpaper creator helps you create unique wallpaper designs for your desktop and phone that speak to your style and mood. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Wallpaper Maker for Anything-But-Basic Backgrounds",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/45386692293209546648.png",imageAlt:"white working desk with plants, calendar and apple computer screen with creative wallpaper on it",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Wallpaper",gtmValue:"1",subscribeId:47,productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Wallpaper Maker Tool!"}},jd="wallpaper_maker",Sd=!0,Cd=function(){return(Cd=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Rd=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Nd,n=Od,a=_d,i=jd,s=Sd;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Cd({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Anytime you need a backdrop refresher on your phone or your desktop, turn to PicsArt’s Wallpaper Maker online to help you create something that will match your unique aesthetic and ever-changing moods. Want to change up your wallpaper every week or every month? It’ll only take a few minutes to go from a basic background to something special and stunning. You can choose from one of our beautiful premade wallpaper templates and personalize it to your liking. Want to know how to make your own wallpaper? You can make your own customized design with our wallpaper creator. Whether you’re craving something simple or striking, let PicsArt help you turn your desktop or phone background into something you won’t get tired of staring at.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create Your Own Wallpaper",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Id=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose one of our meme templates."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload a new picture or choose one from our #FreeToEdit images."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Swap out the text in the template. "},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your meme."}]],Ud=[{description:"<p>With PicsArt’s meme templates, it’s so fun and painless to create funny and trending memes. Come ready with your own design ideas or let our easy-to-use templates give you inspiration. Interacting with funny memes is such a nice way to de-stress after a long day. One hilarious meme photo that speaks to your humor or current mood can put a smile on your face, or even better, make you crack up for minutes and completely alter your state of mind. And with a long list of meme templates available, there are so many topics to explore. It’s one thing to laugh at others’ memes, but it’s another world when you start creating trending memes for yourself. It takes your creativity to a whole new level and results in social media gaining some pretty hilarious new memes. </p>",title:"Funny & Trending Meme Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/24788992080261446396.png",imageAlt:"funny dog face collage meme with facebook linkedin tinder instagram texts",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>If you’ve been thinking about getting in on the game of creating the most popular memes online (that can potentially go viral), you’ve come to the right place. With PicsArt’s popular meme templates, it doesn’t take much time or effort to make a comical meme that will make your friends and fans laugh out loud. With the ready-to-use meme templates, you can replace the original text or photo — or both — to make the meme completely your own. With each new hot current event that occurs, we design a new meme template for you to easily get in on trending conversation.  </p>",title:"Popular Meme Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/40617898402754465149.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Another way to get in the meme-making game is to create your own meme from scratch with PicsArt’s Meme Maker online. It’s still a quick and simple way to show off your personality and joyful side. You can create memes from scratch for many purposes. You can use memes to inject some lightheartedness to your business or brand. This will express to your customers, clients, and fans that your company has an amusing personality and isn’t afraid to show it off. Especially when it comes to your social channels, it’ll garner all the “Likes.” You can also use blank meme templates to make personal memes to prank your friends, create fun birthday messages, or to just show off your funny bone. </p>",title:"Blank Meme Templates\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/79772617697622595288.png",imageAlt:" grandmother with hat image meme with me waiting for my boyfriend text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"4"}}],Md={description:"<p>Our customizable meme templates are the easiest way to get in on the trending and popular memes craze. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Meme Templates Are Hilarious",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/07601734065544725350.png",imageAlt:"dog with glasses image meme with my happy friday face text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Try Templates",gtmValue:"1"}},Wd="meme_template",Dd=!0,Fd="template",Ld=function(){return(Ld=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Vd=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Id,n=Ud,a=Md,i=Wd,s=Dd,c=Fd;It(i,c);var u="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Ld({},a,{landingCategory:c,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Memes are all the rage on social media. From celebrity to politics to pets to television and movies, memes are the perfect way of expressing your jokes on any relevant current event. And with PicsArt’s customizable meme templates, it’s so easy to get in on the game. To start, just click on the #memes hashtag from the Templates page, choose the right template, and begin customizing. Or you can create your own memes from scratch with our easy-to-use ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/meme-generator",className:"inline-link",target:"_blank"},"Meme Maker.")," So the next time you come up with a funny parody that you want to share with the world, turn to PicsArt’s meme templates and start meme-ing away.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,tag:"tags/meme"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:c,productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Play With PicsArt’s Meme Templates ",data:r}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:u,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,isAmp:o,key:t})}))))},zd=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your image or choose one from our free-to-edit library."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Select a mask to apply to your photo."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Adjust the opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],qd=[{description:"<p>Light flares, out-of-focus lighting elements, and light leaks have been growing in popularity all over social media. Bokeh photography may require an expensive camera, and special skills to operate it, but luckily for you, PicsArt’s new photo overlays simplify the entire process to a few clicks. Bokeh masks will elevate your images and make them stand out even more. Simply upload your image and start browsing our free image overlay library. You will find light flares of different sizes, shapes, positionings, and colors. Select your overlay and continue editing your image. PicsArt’s Image Overlays tool allows you to edit the lighting elements, so they fit better with your image. Apply these masks to images and enjoy the magic!</p>",title:"Light Overlays and Detailed Elements ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/15402919786075753014.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=overlays",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JQLh3p7jt8",label:"Add Image Overlays",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Image overlay effects are a great way to add texture and dimension to your images. You will find cute overlays like festive lighting, hearts, and light painting photography designs. If you’re going for a more grungy aesthetic, PicsArt’s overlay library has multiple textures you can choose from. Textures are edgier and add uniqueness to your image. Simply apply one and start adjusting it to your needs. </p>",title:"Add Photo Overlays for a Dramatic Effect",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/83254149539950549213.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=overlays",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JQLh3p7jt8",label:"Add Image Overlays",gtmValue:"3"}}],Bd="image_overlay",Hd={description:"<p>Add photo overlays to images online.</p>",title:"Light Up Your Photos With Image Overlays",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/68525063003270970464.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=overlays",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JQLh3p7jt8",label:"Add Image Overlays",gtmValue:"1"}},Yd=!0,Gd=function(){return(Gd=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Xd=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=zd,n=qd,a=Hd,i=Bd,s=Yd;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Gd({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Add Image Overlays to Your Image",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Qd=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Pick a meme template from “Templates”."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Swap out the image and/or write your text."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Hit download and share."}]],Kd=[{description:"<p>Memes have established their undisputed place in the social media landscape. Today making memes can be considered a valid career path. It seems as though every time you log onto social media, there is a new meme making rounds. Even businesses are joining in on the meme culture.  PicsArt’s new Meme Generator is the tool you need to create your own memes and join in on the conversation. Our online Meme Generator simplifies the meme-creating process, allowing you to quickly produce content. The timing of memes is very important. Because conversations shift very quickly, you don’t want to join in on one too late. As long as you listen to your audience, create memes that are relatable, and stay true to your brand, memes could potentially be a great marketing tool for you. </p>",title:"Why Make Memes?",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/86222075443244257367.png",imageAlt:"my happy friday face meme of a man on a pink background",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Start Making Memes!",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>Why are memes so popular? Memes have become the ultimate source of entertaining remarks, motivating phrases, and even political satire - essentially a staple in pop culture. Anything and everything can become a trending meme. To make your own meme, you just have to<a href="/images" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="pick-an-image-hypertext"> pick an image</a> and give it a new meaning with a witty phrase or joke. Memes are popular across all major social media channels - Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Tumblr, and Pinterest. People genuinely love sharing memes. This could potentially be a great way for you to increase your number of followers and number of interactions with your content. Simply follow the steps below to create your own meme. </p>',title:"Memes Are All the Rage",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/90095561120642651724.png",imageAlt:"my happy friday face meme of a smiling dog with white background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Start Making Memes!",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>With PicsArt’s free Meme Generator, you can completely push the boundaries of humor. Our awesome meme templates make it easy to get your ideas into meme format. The minute you have funny commentary about an event, a news story, or a celebrity, open <a href="/" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="PicsArt-hypertext">PicsArt</a> and start making your own meme. You can also make memes relating to your business and brand. Listen to what customers are saying about you. The more relatable your memes are, the easier your audience will consume them. Using memes as a marketing tactic has been gaining more and more attention. Some of the biggest companies in the world are sharing memes on their social media channels - opting to be more light-hearted and funny, as opposed to a more serious tone of voice.  </p>',title:"Memes Are the New Source of Entertainment ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/20357019939438056112.png",imageAlt:"omg text on a cat meme with blue background",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Start Making Memes!",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Memes are super sociable - arguably the most shared format of content on the Internet. You should be able to quickly generate memes, make them consumable and relatable to your audience and most importantly - make them funny. You can use your own company and products to make a meme, or check what’s trending on social media and add your commentary to it.  </p>",title:"Memes Are Social",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/48577001388361955312.png",imageAlt:"cows meme with there is always that on friend text",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Start Making Memes!",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Can’t wait to make your own meme? First, look through the templates. You will find numerous pre-made meme designs that you can directly apply to the image of your choice. Scroll to search for funny meme pictures or upload your own. Then, swap out the text with your own phrases. Save it and don’t forget to share on your social media channels! </p>",title:"Get Started With Our Free Meme Generator!",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/41997537979116450441.png",imageAlt:"dog meme with my face when my best friend makes plans without me text",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Start Making Memes!",gtmValue:"6"}}],$d={description:"<p>Create viral social media content in seconds with our free meme maker.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Meme Generator ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/22113791397079590879.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateCategory=memes",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Create a Meme Now!",gtmValue:"1"}},Jd="meme_generator",Zd=!0,em=function(){return(em=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},tm=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Qd,n=Kd,a=$d,i=Jd,s=Zd;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,em({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make Your Own Meme",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},om=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your picture or choose one from our #FreeToEdit images."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Define the area you want to be eliminated from your image."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Apply changes and let AI remove unwanted elements from your picture."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],rm=[{description:'<p>Driven by users\' need to quickly remove objects from photos, we created a quick tool that will save you hours. Just define the area you want to delete and the object will disappear in mere seconds. The best part is that you don’t need to be a professional editor, or even have a lot of spare time, to pull it off. Once you’re done, continue editing with our <a target="_blank" class="inline-link" href="/photo-editor" data-test="photo-editor-hypertext">Photo Editor.</a></p>',title:"Why the Need for the Remove Tool?\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/41928852830084551979.png",imageAlt:"summer vacation at the sunny beach with gold sand",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Images speak volumes when it comes to creating a blossoming brand that is here to stay. So it’s highly important to create and present flawless imagery that will resonate with your target audience. With the Remove tool, it’s possible to delete any unwanted text, logo, timestamp, or any other element that’s in the way. The best part is that it’s free, fast, and you don’t need any editing expertise to get it done.  </p>",title:"Remove Unwanted Text and Imagery",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/44485464004135326388.png",imageAlt:"calm girl face image with effects",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Then there’s the matter of photos with a messy background. The last thing you want is for the world to see a disheveled backdrop in an otherwise stunning shot. That’s when the Remove tool comes into play and saves the day. Easily remove objects, like bottles, and dirty dishes and power lines and buildings, that could tarnish a squeaky clean image.</p>",title:"Remove Clutter From Photos",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/90533840058408471397.png",imageAlt:"girl looking through the pages of book",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>When creating product or promotion shots, it’s not uncommon to end up with unwanted shadows, folds, and creases. That’s when PicsArt’s Remove tool can take care of business and give you a more flawless end result. You can also use it to get rid of wrinkles, folds, and stains from clothing on model shots. If you want to completely change the dynamic of your background to make your product shots stand out, use our <a target="_blank" class="inline-link" href="/background-changer" data-test="background-changer-hypertext">Background Changer</a> to replace your background or our <a target="_blank" class="inline-link" href="/background-remover" data-test="background-remover-hypertext">Background Remover</a> to make it transparent. </p>',title:"Remove Shadows and Creases",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/79885010839693258755.png",imageAlt:"image of 2 people and their shadows",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>There are also times when you need to remove an ex boyfriend or girlfriend (or just anyone who you don’t want in your shot) from your photos. If you still want to preserve those pictures, that’s when the Remove tool becomes your go-to. Removing people from photos is an option should you need it. </p>",title:"Remove People From Your Past",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/97427015698438414784.png",imageAlt:"happy girl is running in the field",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>Sometimes strangers standing in the background of your photo can really ruin the aesthetic. That’s a justified reason to remove people from photos. Photobombing is yet another reason to use the Remove tool to your advantage. Both instances are out of your control, but with this tool at your fingertips, you can get rid of them in a snap — and a few taps. At the end, apply our <a target="_blank" class="inline-link" href="/photo-effects" data-test="online-photo-effects-hypertext">online photo effects</a> to your image for a final touch-up.</p>',title:"Remove Photo Bombers and Strangers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/92769287096344785973.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl posing in the beach",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"7"}}],nm={description:"<p>With PicsArt’s Remove Objects tool, you can delete unwanted text and imagery in just a few taps. </p>",title:"A Quick and Painless Way to Remove Objects From Photos",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/12781994285036718636.png",imageAlt:"building with the usa flag on top ",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?patchOpened=true",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rIhqGQjlt8",label:"Remove Objects",gtmValue:"1"}},am="remove_objects",im=!0,sm=function(){return(sm=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},lm=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=om,n=rm,a=nm,i=am,s=im;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,sm({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Even the most perfect shot has imperfections in it. Whether it’s background clutter, unwanted text, or a logo, there are instances when you need to polish up an image — and fast. Removing objects from photos online is super easy with PicsArt’s Remove tool. In just a few taps, you can get rid of anything or anyone getting in the way of your beautiful image.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Remove an Object From a Photo",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},cm=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"To start, select a #FreetoEdit image or upload one of your own."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Next, choose another image from the left-hand toolbar whose design will transfer onto your original image. Or upload your own photo to transfer its design."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Adjust the fade, intensity, contrast, brightness, and saturation if need be."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your final image."}]],um=[{description:'<p>Neural style transfer allows you to take the look (colors and lighting) from your favorite images and transfer them to a whole other photo  — all in a single tap. When performing a style transfer on a photo, all you have to do is click once and Artificial Intelligence works its magic behind the scenes to turn your photo into a masterpiece that will set it apart from a sea of social media posts. You can choose to transfer the look of any image already available in <a href="/images" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="our-FreetoEdit-image-library-hypertext">our #FreetoEdit image library</a> or you can transfer the look of any photo that you upload onto another image. When wanting to make your social feed pop, neural style transfer is the perfect — not to mention the easiest and quickest — way to go. </p>',title:"Neural Style Transfer Is Social Media Feed Gold",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/77912891080658180509.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl with scarf image collage with sunflower color effect",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-transfer",mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Try Style Transfer",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>When it comes to promoting yourself or your business online, you constantly need to find new and innovative ways to cut through all the virtual noise. With PicsArt’s Style Transfer tool, creating eye-catching images that are spotlight-worthy is super fast, easy, and painless. Turn your photos into art in mere seconds by clicking on one of the images in our extensive library to transfer the design of that photo to the one you’re working with. Or, if you love the design of a photo you’ve taken or discovered on your own, you can also use it to transfer its look to another photo you’re working with. Once you do the neural style transfer from one image to another, you can personalize it further by adjusting the fade levels, contrast, brightness, and saturation to create an even more dream image. </p>",title:"Create Artistic Images in a Single Tap",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/29097244076763054469.png",imageAlt:"girl with a backpack and a hat standing in the field image collage with special effects",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-transfer",mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Try Style Transfer",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>For Instagram influencers looking to make their feed pop, while simultaneously lending an artistic flair, PicsArt’s Style Transfer tool is the quickest and best way to go. And it’s completely free! You can take any simple image and give it the look of a beautiful painting in seconds. There are no limits or rules when it comes to the neural style transfer technique, so just have fun with it. If you love the look and colors of an image (any image) and want to transfer its design to another picture you’re promoting, it can be done in a few taps. Then, play around with the brightness, saturation, and contrast levels. Personalize it even further by pulling the final product into our <a href="/photo-editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="photo-editor-hypertext">Photo Editor</a> and changing its background design with our <a href="/background-changer" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="background-changer-tool-hypertext">Background Changer tool.</a> </p>',title:"Style Transfer Is Ideal for Instagram Influencers\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/44020908594996493710.png",imageAlt:"bride and groom standing happily image collage with before after white color effetcs",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-transfer",mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Try Style Transfer",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>One of the fastest ways to capture attention on your blog or website is to run your images through our free Style Transfer tool. In a matter of seconds, your simple photo will turn into a masterpiece that will impress your audience. Design blogs and websites will especially appreciate PicsArt’s neural style transfer technique since it can turn any photo into a famous painting. What took great artists like Picasso and Warhol to days and months to create can be mimicked on any of your photos in seconds! All you have to do is click on the image you want transferred to your photo and Artificial Intelligence will do its magic behind the scenes. You can then use our <a href="/image-upscale" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="image-upscale-hypertext">Image Upscale</a> tool to enlarge your images without losing its resolution. </p>',title:"Style Transfer Makes Blog Images Pop",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/75609198145447790911.png",imageAlt:"girl practising yoga in the nature with before after image effects",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-transfer",mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Try Style Transfer",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>For businesses that have a product or service to promote online, our Style Transfer tool is a great way to make your marketing images pop. Instead of presenting a simple photo, why not turn it up a notch and capture attention with something more artistic? If it makes sense for the product you’re promoting, you can use PicsArt’s neural style transfer technique to give your images the push they need to stand out. Just run your promotion photos through our Style Transfer tool and they’ll be sure to make heads turn. You can make them as bold or as subtle as you need by adjusting the design settings, depending on the message you’re trying to send. As a final touch, you can also layer on one of our <a href="/photo-effects" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="trendy-photo-effects-hypertext">trendy photo effects</a> for added flair. </p>',title:"Style Transfer Helps Marketing Promotions",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/22561401564700981479.png",imageAlt:"black hair boy before after image with mountains and fields effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-transfer",mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Try Style Transfer",gtmValue:"6"}}],pm={description:"<p>Turn simple photos into artistic images in a single tap.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Style Transfer Tool Transforms Images to Masterpieces",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/50241965545504317833.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl in denim image collage with club lights effects",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-transfer",mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Try Style Transfer",gtmValue:"1"}},dm="style_transfer",mm=!0,hm=function(){return(hm=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},gm=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=cm,n=um,a=pm,i=dm,s=mm;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,hm({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"The Style Transfer tool uses a photo technique that takes simple shots and turns them into masterpieces in seconds. Also referred to as neural style transfer, the impressive Artificial Intelligence-powered tool completely alters the look of any image in seconds. How it works is, it takes the colors and lighting from one image, and in just one tap, transfers them to another photo. The amazing transformation happens right before your eyes! And though it may sound like a complicated process, all you have to do is click a button and let the magic happen.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Use Style Transfer Tool",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},fm=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Find a background in the photo chooser."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Add a rectangular sticker (or several) to define the three sections of the brochure."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Use the text tool to add text. "},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download the finished brochure. "}]],ym=[{description:"<p>One of the biggest reasons to turn to PicsArt’s Brochure Maker is that it won’t cost you a penny — or an arm or a leg. That means you can save thousands of dollars and get it done all by yourself from your home or office. We make it easy for you to create the perfect, professional brochure without worrying about draining your wallet. Our Brochure Maker is also beyond easy to navigate, so don’t wait for another minute, get your message out with the help of PicsArt.</p>",title:"Brochure Maker Is Completely Free",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/65858396711973248908.png",imageAlt:"vegetables, products brocure template",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Brochure",gtmValue:"2",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Brochure Maker!",subscribeId:28}},{description:"<p>With PicsArt’s Brochure Maker, you don’t need to have any programming or design skills to create something beautiful. All you need is a desire to be creative and have fun with it. In just a few clicks and minutes, you can finish a professional-looking brochure that will speak to your brand’s one-of-a-kind aesthetic. You can choose a background design from our extensive #FreetoEdit image library, then personalize things further with our unique PicsArt-exclusive tools. Before showcasing it to the world, jazz up your brochure with designer fonts, fun stickers, and trendy effects.</p>",title:"Brochure Design Doesn’t Require Any Skills",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/28961999486033767660.png",imageAlt:"it's not about brand it's about style text on a brochure template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{label:"Make a Brochure",gtmValue:"3",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Brochure Maker!",subscribeId:28}},{description:"<p>To give your professional brochure a one-of-kind feel to make it stand out from the competition, you can easily customize it in PicsArt’s Brochure Maker. Start by choosing a background that fits your needs. You might look for a backdrop for a big announcement or special project, or you may seek a subtle background to set a serious tone. No matter your purpose or theme, we have the right tools to help you create the brochure that’s right for you. Once you make your selection, it’s time to edit it as you see fit. Swap in your own images or logo, and modify the text using our over 200 designer fonts. Add fun stickers and effects to give your brochure design a unique look. </p>",title:"Customize Brochures to Your Liking\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/92465332470938057765.png",imageAlt:"health center design brochure template",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Brochure",gtmValue:"4",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Brochure Maker!",subscribeId:28}},{description:"<p>Whether you’re a professional photographer who wants to create a romantic brochure for your wedding services, a travel agent who’s looking to convey seasonal deals, a real estate agent wanting to show off high-end properties, or a restaurant entrepreneur who wants to get the word out on any aspect of your business, look no further than PicsArt’s Brochure Maker. It doesn’t matter what your message is or which industry you’re a part of, we’ve got you covered with tons of tools and effects that will help you create your perfect brochure. All it takes is a few minutes of your time. In addition, we have more easy-to-use template designs (invitation templates, meme templates, and more) for other marketing needs. \n</p>",title:"Make Professional Brochures for Any Occasion\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/82541075606608020131.png",imageAlt:"green house restaurant brochure template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Brochure",gtmValue:"5",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Brochure Maker!",subscribeId:28}},{description:"<p>Along with our handy Brochure Maker, we also have an array of brochure templates for you to work with. From bold to understated and everything in between, there is a brochure design template that will stand out for all of your business needs. PicsArt features endless brochure templates for you to sift through and pick the one that’s right for your branding message. Need something bright and cheery for a big restaurant opening party? Want a subdued brochure to announce more serious developments? We’ve got you covered. If you don’t love the color scheme or imagery, you can always swap it for new photos or colors. You can easily edit any of the design details on any of our templates to give it a signature touch that will speak to your customers.</p>",title:"Choose From a Wide Selection of Brochure Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/48501780370236540352.png",imageAlt:"the best furniture for your home text on a brochure template",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Brochure",gtmValue:"6",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Brochure Maker!",subscribeId:28}}],bm={description:"<p>We’ve made it super easy for anyone to create a brochure design that’s sleek and stylish. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Brochure Maker Is Professional — No Experience Needed",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/57949230988708590385.png",imageAlt:"your colorful new home text on a brochure template",buttonProps:{label:"Make a Brochure",gtmValue:"1",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Brochure Maker!",subscribeId:28}},vm="brochure_maker",km=function(){return(km=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},wm=fm,Pm=ym,Em=bm,xm=vm,Tm=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(xm),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,km({},Em,{screenName:xm,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s online Brochure Maker is your go-to when you need to put out a professional brochure that will impress your clients. No matter the kind of business or industry you’re involved in, we can help you come up with a brochure design that will get the word out about your projects in no time. How do you create a brochure with PicsArt right from home? Start by choosing the perfect backdrop that you can find in our extensive #FreetEdit image library, then customize it by adding text, effects, stickers, and more.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Pm,screenName:xm,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a Brochure",data:wm}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Am={description:"<p>Fix red eyes in everything from selfies to portraits to group shots quicker than you can count 1, 2, 3!</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Red Eye Remover Is Your Go-To for Perfect Portraits",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/65114972051132710729.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl with a hat in profile image",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/n3oYyfOpt8",label:"Remove Red Eyes",gtmValue:"1"}},Nm=[{description:'<p>PicsArt’s Red Eye Remover is your go-to for all things red-eye related. Red eyes that appear in photos are something you can’t control and they have the potential to ruin the perfect shot, so when that happens, you can run your images through our handy Red Eye Remover. The tool, housed in our <a href="/photo-editor" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="photo-editor-hypertext">Photo Editor</a> along with a ton of other impressive editing tools, is designed to help you fix red eyes in all types of photos with just one single click. From selfies to portraits to group photos, our Red Eye Remover will take care of your problem in seconds. Our AI technology handles most of the work so you can just upload and click, then sit back and relax because the tool locates all the red eyes in each shot for you. Watch your eyeballs go from red to white in seconds with PicsArt’s Red Eye Remover tool.</p>',title:"Remove Red Eyes in One Single Tap",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/54964550287710715013.png",imageAlt:"happy black hair girl before after image",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/n3oYyfOpt8",label:"Remove Red Eyes",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>What happens when you run your images through PicsArt’s Red Eye Remover? Flawless shot after flawless shot. No one wants to post photos with red eyes, so whenever you come across this problem, fret not, just turn to the Red Eye Remover tool to solve it in just one tap and a few seconds. With PicsArt’s Red Eye Remover at your fingertips, you’ll never deal with annoying red eyes ever again. There is no limit to how many images and how many red eyes our Red Eye Remover can handle, so you can keep going until you’re done. Once you’re finished clearing all the red eyes, your images will be ready to be spotlighted on all your social media channels. Don’t forget to add a fun backdrop to your photo with our <a href="/background-changer" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="background-changer-tool-hypertext">Background Changer tool</a> to really step up your editing game before sharing with the world.</p>',title:"Fix Red Eyes to Get Flawless Shots",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/16814288451195410172.png",imageAlt:"happy boy in hoodie profile image",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/n3oYyfOpt8",label:"Remove Red Eyes",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>While PicsArt’s Red Eye Remover tool is highly impressive and sophisticated, it’s super easy to use. All you have to do is upload the images in which red eyes exist, click on the tool, and let the AI technology go to work. It starts by locating all the red eyes in each shot — there is no limit to how many red eyes it can remove in one photo. If you’re not happy with the positioning of the automated circles around the red eyes, you can choose to drag and position the circles yourself. This only takes a few more seconds to pull off. Once the circles are in position around the eyes, all you have to do is click the checkmark to confirm and let the magic happen. Now your perfect selfie or portrait is ready to be touted to the social world. If need be, change the image size with our <a href="/crop-image" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="crop-tool-hypertext">Crop tool</a> and remove any clutter with our <a href="/background-remover" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="background-remover-hypertext">Background Remover.</a> </p>',title:"Fixing Red-Eye Pictures Is Insanely Easy",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/91443790414859242662.png",imageAlt:"freckles girl before after Image",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/n3oYyfOpt8",label:"Remove Red Eyes",gtmValue:"4"}}],Om={editingStepsData:[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload the image you want to be corrected. "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Click the Red Eye Remover tool and let AI locate the red eyes."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Tap the checkmark to confirm."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your photo."}]],landingData:Nm,bannerData:Am,screenName:"red_eye_remover"},_m=function(){return(_m=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},jm=Om.editingStepsData,Sm=Om.landingData,Cm=Om.bannerData,Rm=Om.screenName,Im=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Rm),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,_m({},Cm,{screenName:Rm,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Sm,screenName:Rm,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Remove Red Eyes",data:jm}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Um=[{description:"<p>Birthday cards are a memorable way to express your love and appreciation for your loved ones on their special day. With PicsArt’s birthday card templates, your heartfelt message will speak volumes and won’t take long to make. Pick the birthday card template that suits your recipient’s style, then customize it with our beautiful fonts, stickers, effects, and colors to get a one-of-a-kind creation that they’ll appreciate. Share your high-quality birthday card online or have it printed to hand out in person.</p>",title:"Beautiful Birthday Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/88184306768542398435.png",imageAlt:"birthday invitation card template design",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>For your big day, save tons of money and let PicsArt’s gorgeous wedding invitation templates help you create something truly special. Send out save-the-dates and wedding reception invites using our stunning collection of wedding invitation templates, then customize your pick using our fast and easy editing tools to create a unique finish. Add your own images to your wedding invitation template or pull stock photos from our extensive #FreeToEdit image library. Personalize things even further by adding text with beautiful fonts, stickers, effects, and more. Send out your high-quality wedding invite online, post it to your wedding website, or have it printed to send out in the mail.</p>",title:"Romantic Wedding Invitation Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/87826528870118861557.png",imageAlt:"wedding invitation card template design",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Going to a baby shower celebration? Create a sweet card for the family using our collection of adorable baby shower card templates. We’ve got a variety of colors and designs to choose from, whether the baby is a girl or a boy. Keep things gender-neutral with our more earthy baby shower card templates. Our ready-to-use templates will only take a few minutes to customize to reflect your message. Add fun stickers, trendy effects, bold backgrounds, and text using our stylish fonts.</p>",title:"Adorable Baby Shower Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/72992265758833210655.png",imageAlt:"baby shower invitation card design template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Any time you need to thank someone for something, whether it’s for personal or business reasons, turn to PicsArt’s sweet thank you card templates to give you tons of ideas. Choose the thank you card template that speaks to you and your recipient, then customize it to add your own text using our stylish fonts, stickers, effects, and more. It’ll only take a few minutes but the impact will last forever. Send your thank you card online or have it printed to hand out in person. All our card templates are high-resolution so you don’t have to worry about quality.</p>",title:"Sweet Thank You Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/01499979572101053419.png",imageAlt:"thank you card design template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>When it’s time for the holiday season, PicsArt can help you send out cards with our easy-to-use holiday card templates. There is no limit to how many holiday cards you can make, so choose as many templates as you need. Our holiday card templates are absolutely festive, so you’ll find a design that matches your mood. We even have stylish card templates for other special holidays such as Mother’s Day and Valentine’s Day. Personalize each card template you pick with our quick and easy editing tools. Add it text with our stylish fonts, festive stickers, effects, and more.</p>",title:"Festive Holiday Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/96013609097330630731.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>When it comes to conducting business, PicsArt can help you create professional and sleek business cards using our handy business card templates. Our business card templates are very versatile and only take minutes to customize. Pick the business card template that matches your style, then personalize it with your unique details with our easy-to-use editing tools. Add in your own logo and signature colors to make something one-of-a-kind.</p>",title:"Professional Business Card Templates",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/38317241800970773166.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"7"}}],Mm={description:"<p>Choose from a collection of stylish card templates and customize your card design template for any event.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Card Templates Are Ready to Use for Any Occasion",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/63459828258985105631.png",imageAlt:"thank you for being you card template idea for a friend",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=card",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create a Card",gtmValue:"1"}},Wm="card_templates",Dm=!0,Fm="template",Lm=function(){return(Lm=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Vm=Um,zm=Mm,qm=Wm,Bm=Dm,Hm=Fm,Ym=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;It(qm,Hm);var r="desktop"===ue.c?6:"phone"===ue.c?2:4;return l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Lm({},zm,{landingCategory:Hm,screenName:qm,isPremium:Bm,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"At PicsArt, we’ve designed design card templates to help you celebrate any occasion in your life with class and ease. Whether you need to create a special card for a birthday, anniversary, wedding, baby shower, or any holiday like Mother’s Day, our ready-to-use card templates take mere minutes to customize. From simple to bold, there is a stunning card template that will help you express yourself in style. Choose the card template that matches your event, then personalize it as much or as little as you wish. Use our fast and easy editing tools to add text with beautiful fonts, fun stickers, trending effects, bold colors, and more for a one-of-a-kind finish.")}),l.a.createElement(Po,{screenName:qm,isPremium:Bm,isAmp:o,tag:"tags/card"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{landingCategory:Hm,productData:Vm,screenName:qm,isPremium:Bm,isAmp:o,darkBg:!0}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Other Templates"}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o,settings:{autoplaySpeed:2e3,slidesToShow:r,autoplay:!0,infinite:!1}},Mr&&Mr.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement(_r,{dataTests:{button:"carousel item "+t},isAmp:o,productMetaTitle:e.productMetaTitle,templateLabel:e.templateLabel,thumbnailUrl:e.thumbnailUrl,subscribeId:e.subscribeId,bgColor:e.bgColor,imgUrl:e.imgUrl,key:t})}))))},Gm=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open Magic effects tool."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload your picture."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Click on your desired Magic effects."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Adjust details as needed. "},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download your final edit."}]],Xm=[{description:"<p>Want artsy pictures but don’t want to do any heavy photo editing? PicsArt’s quick & easy Magic effects are the way to go. All in a matter of seconds and just one click, you’ll go from simple to spotlight-worthy images that look like they belong in a museum. Turn your photos into art with no effort at all. Just tap the effect that speaks to your aesthetic and mood and let the smart technology work its magic on your images. With effect names like Flora, Galaxy, Moonlight, Midnight, Feast, White Ice, and so many more, you know the result will be nothing short of amazing. Make any of your photos look like a painting with a stunning collection of Magic effects, all ready and waiting to turn basic photos into art. </p>",title:"Quickly & Easily Turn Photos Into Art",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/96375246967849738905.png",imageAlt:"smiling girl photo with special art effects applied",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Turn Photo into Art",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>The amazing thing about PicsArt’s Magic effects — besides that it can be achieved in one single tap — is that it works on any type of image. That means you can turn just about any photo into art. From selfies to portraits to city shots to nature scenes to food photos, you can transform any simple photo in your camera roll or on your desktop into something truly special. Achieve artsy pictures in mere seconds with a collection of unique effects that will stun your friends and followers. What looks like it took hours and complicated editing tools to create can be done in one fast and easy click! That’s the magic of PicsArt’s Magic effects.</p>",title:"Turn Any Picture into a Painting — Yes, Any",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/20399504041446092663.png",imageAlt:"smiling girl photo turned into a painting",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Start Making Art",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Online cartoonizers are aplenty but PicsArt’s Magic effects stand out from the rest thanks to a collection of stunning and truly one-of-a-kind designs like Moonlight, Rainbow, Pow, Neo Pop, Rose Quartz, Animation and so many more. Instantly turn any photo into a cartoon with our easy-to-use online caritoonizer. From artistic cartoon effects to multicolored effects for a bolder look, you can take your pick depending on your aesthetic and mood. Want to achieve a pop art painting? Looking for a touch of surrealism? Interested in a sketch-like look? You can find these and many more styles with <a href="/photo-effects/photo-to-cartoon" target="_blank" class="inline-link">PicsArt’s online cartoonizer.</a> Try out every effect in a single tap and choose the one(s) that work for your photo needs. Get stunning results every time — turn photos into paintings in seconds with PicsArt. Click away and watch the magic that transpires right before your eyes. End up with artsy pictures that are nothing short of head-turning. </p>',title:"PicsArt’s Online Cartoonizer Is Extraordinary ",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/75252479989114191075.png",imageAlt:"yellow taxi in megapolis with special photo art effects applied",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Try Cartoonizer",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>Tired of plain selfies? <a href="/canvas-effect" target="_blank" class="inline-link">Try PicsArt’s Canvas effects</a> to turn your simple selfies and portraits into works of art. Achieve artsy pictures in just one click with four unique Canvas effects. So how does it all work? The smart tool takes parts of famous paintings and sculptures — there are thousands of beautiful options in our collection — and places them on sections of your face. From your eyes to your mouth, get a whole new artistic look, and become your own masterpiece. If you don’t like the look, just shuffle for a brand-new result and keep going until you’re satisfied. Customize your masterpiece using PicsArt’s quick & easy photo editing tools for an even more one-of-a-kind finish. Next time you want to turn your selfie into art, just look to PicsArt’s Canvas effects to do it for you. Another fun way to achieve artsy pictures is to try the highly trendy <a href="/drip-effect" target="_blank" class="inline-link">Drip Art effect.</a></p>',title:"Become Your Own Masterpiece With PicsArt’s Canvas Effects",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/26041873902746093896.png",imageAlt:"photo of a girl with canvas effect & frame sticker on it",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=canvas-effectt",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/OHjBWzAlt8",label:"Try Canvas Effects",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>Love the hand-drawn look but can’t draw? <a href="/photo-effects/sketch" target="_blank" class="inline-link">PicsArt’s Sketch effects</a> are the perfect solution for you. It’s a quick & easy feature that transforms photos into art in seconds. Take basic selfies and portraits and turn them into artsy pictures in just one tap. Upload the portrait of your choice and choose from six Sketch effects that all give your photo a hand-drawn sketch. Each Sketch effect is slightly different and features unique details so you can pick the one that matches your aesthetic. To customize your experience, you can play around with the placement, color, and width of the sketch lines. You can also use PicsArt’s photo editing tools to create something even more outstanding and eye-catching. </p>',title:"Give Selfies a Hand-Drawn Look With Sketch Effects ",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/40557089233179340024.png",imageAlt:"smiling boy photo with sketch effects",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/editor?category=sketch-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Sketch Yourself",gtmValue:"6"}}],Qm={description:"<p>Turn any photo into a painting and watch your images morph into photo art before your very eyes.  </p>",title:"Turn Any Photo Into Art in Just One Click",imageUrl:"https://easycdn.picsart.com/06885960716366648977.png",imageAlt:"photo art effects on a shoot of a pretty girl with red beret and trench",buttonProps:{url:"https://picsart.com/create/chooser?redirect=editor&category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/4pv7HdD7S9",label:"Start Editing",gtmValue:"1"}},Km="photos_into_art",$m=!0,Jm=function(){return(Jm=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Zm=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Gm,n=Xm,a=Qm,i=Km,s=$m;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Jm({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s Magic effects make it possible to turn photos into art — all in a matter of one click. Turn any of your photos into paintings and end up with artsy pictures worthy of the spotlight. Choose from a collection of eye-catching effects that will transform photos like magic. Tired of basic pictures but don’t want to do heavy editing? Anytime you want to turn up the dial on your simple photos, you can make any photo look like a painting in a matter of seconds with PicsArt. From selfies to portraits to landscapes, Magic effects work on any kind of photo in your camera roll. Once you go Magic effects, you’ll never go back!")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Make a Cartoon Picture",data:r,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},eh=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your image."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Let AI improve the quality of your image automatically."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Download your image."}]],th=[{description:"<p>Enlarging a photo can take a toll on the image’s overall quality. Even slight adjustments to the size of an image can lower its resolution. PicsArt’s Image Upscale uses AI technology to visibly enhance and increase the resolution of your image. Images are a great way to promote your business, regardless of your industry. They grab your attention, are highly engaging, and help you build your brand. High resolution images that have low file size are your best option, both for your website and social media. Scaling down the size of your image doesn’t affect the quality as much as enlarging it. Don’t risk losing the quality of your content. With Image Upscale, you will be able to restore your photos in an instant. Confidently resize images without losing quality.  </p>",title:"Resize Images Without Losing Quality ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/48834146029283915172.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Improve Your Image!",gtmValue:"2",url:"/create/chooser?redirect=upscale"}},{description:"<p>Phone cameras are not always able to capture a quality image in the same way professional lenses do. By using Image Upscale, you can drastically increase the resolution and quality of your selfies, group photos, landscape images, product photos, and anything you choose to capture. PicsArt’s Image Upscale is fully powered by AI. This technology identifies areas within the image that need enhancement and improvement - ultimately refining it. This tool can be beneficial for both professional and personal use. You can expect improved tones and colors, as well as clearer details within the image. </p>",title:"Increase the Resolution of Low Quality Images",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/97928380008015684618.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Upscale Your Image!",gtmValue:"3",url:"/create/chooser?redirect=upscale"}},{description:"<p>In practice, not all the images you work with will be shot on a professional camera with pronounced lighting and attention to detail. This is especially true if your business relies on a lot of user generated content. Content created by your users is one of the best ways to tap into your customer base and get to know what they like and dislike about your products/services. In most cases, the images taken by users are shot on phone cameras. With Image Upscale, you can easily enlarge images and increase their resolution so you can repurpose them later on for your marketing efforts. </p>",title:"Enhance Pictures Which Are User Generated",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/32829116766904802402.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Improve Your Image!",gtmValue:"4",url:"/create/chooser?redirect=upscale"}}],oh={description:"<p>Instantly increase the resolution of your image online With our AI powered tool.</p>",title:"Increase the Resolution of Your Images With PicsArt’s Image Upscale ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/06674205473358547944.png",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"/create/editor",label:"Upscale Your Image!",gtmValue:"1",url:"/create/chooser?redirect=upscale"}},rh="image_upscale",nh=!0,ah=function(){return(ah=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},ih=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=eh,n=th,a=oh,i=rh,s=nh;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,ah({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Increase the Resolution of Your Image With Image Upscale",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},sh=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your image or choose one from our free-to-edit images."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Let the AI remove the background for you."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Adjust the opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast of your new sticker."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Smooth out the edges or restore elements with the Eraser/Brush tool."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Flip it around or rotate it around its axis."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Download your sticker and start sharing."}]],lh=[{description:'<p>Stickers are a great form of cost-effective advertising. These are very useful for increasing your brand awareness and getting the word out about your company. Just think of how many brands effectively advertise through stickers. Seemingly small, they leave quite the impression and are seen by almost everyone. Start creating stickers with PicsArt’s Sticker Maker. This tool allows you to easily create custom stickers and share them with your customers. You can share them online, via social media, or even print tangible copies and distribute them in person. You want to make sure that they are eye-catching and easily recognizable. Design your own stickers and make them unique to your brand. You can even turn your company logo or slogan into a sticker. If you have a company mascot, make it into a sticker as well. Anything that can be associated with your brand/company can be turned into a sticker. Print them out and share them with the world, you can even save them and <a href="/add-stickers-to-photos" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="add-your-stickers-to-images-hypertext"> add your stickers to images.</a></p>',title:"Make Your Own Stickers for Promotions",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/73947036075323472930.png",imageAlt:"girl with a hat on with flamingo stickers ",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Start Making Stickers",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>Making personalized stickers from your own images has never been this easy. Upload your image and our AI technology will <a href="/background-remover" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="automatically-remove-the-background-hypertext"> automatically remove the background</a> for you, leaving you with the main foreground component. Your sticker will have a transparent background. You can either save it as it is, or continue editing. You have the option to adjust the opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast of your sticker. You can adjust the size and even play around with its positioning by rotating it around its axis. If you want to eliminate certain elements from your sticker, simply use the Eraser tool, or, if you want to bring back some elements from your original photo, use the Brush mode to restore them. Creating stickers online is a fun and easy process. PicsArt gives you <a href="/editing-tools?source=landing_pages" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="all-the-necessary-tools-hypertext">all the necessary tools</a> to achieve your desired results. You can find the section on how to make your own stickers below.  </p>',title:"Custom Stickers That You Can Edit ",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/78111177312388892523.png",imageAlt:"colored hair girl with flamingos and colorful tapes on a blue background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Start Making Stickers",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Creating your own stickers with PicsArt is a personalized experience. You no longer have to delegate to a fellow designer. This tool is very simple and does not require any professional knowledge of design software. Without a doubt, stickers are a great form of advertising. They have multiple uses and are truly unique to your business. <a href="/stickers" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="stickers-hypertext">Stickers</a> can be used on various surfaces, and in numerous different ways. They are very versatile and you can use this to your advantage. Having your company sticker on someone’s laptop can expose you to new customers. It may seem small, but you never know whose eye it might catch. You can easily create custom stickers online for a specific target market or a customer base. These are great - from product promotions to marketing activities. Don’t underestimate the power of a Sticker Maker. You’ll thank us later. </p>',title:"Why Create Stickers?",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/82958147114745098892.png",imageAlt:"man photo with crown, water drops, thunder and rainbow stickers",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Start Making Stickers",gtmValue:"4"}}],ch={description:"<p>Create your own stickers and share them with the world.</p>",title:"Get Creative with PicsArt’s Sticker Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/50644216720434683243.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/remove-background",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TgjdhuAit8",label:"Start Making Stickers",gtmValue:"1"}},uh="make_sticker",ph=!0,dh=function(){return(dh=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},mh=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=sh,n=lh,a=ch,i=uh,s=ph;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,dh({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make Stickers",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},hh=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload an image or use one of our free-to-edit options."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Try the four different types of Sketch Effects."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Apply one to your image."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Play around with the line size, line color, and positioning."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],gh=[{description:"<p>If you’re an artist, you know that drawing a sketch can take time, but with PicsArt’s Sketch Effects, it only takes a second! The longest part of the process is finding the perfect image to use. Once you have it, all you have to do is upload it and you’ll see your final result.</p>",title:" Create a Sketch Drawing in Seconds",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/78114135002805369534.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl face with sketch effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=sketch-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Sketch Yourself!",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>Finalize your edit <a href="/background-changer" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="by-changing-the-background-hypertext"> by changing the background</a> of your image and by switching up the line color of the sketch to a scheme that fits your style. Go simple with a white or black line or choose a more vibrant color, like neon yellow or bright pink. The possibilities are endless, so just play around and see what looks best on your photos.  </p>',title:"Choose Any Color Line or Background",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/62707043128025691311.png",imageAlt:"man with a hat on with sketch effect on a blue background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=sketch-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Sketch Yourself!",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Four different Sketch Effects are available for you to experiment with. You can create a classic look with Simple Sketch; go with a more dramatic feel with Total Sketch; get a double dose of you with Double Sketch, and create a cool dynamic effect with Reverse Sketch. </p>",title:"Pick From Four Amazing Sketch Effects",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/26985256555787589092.png",imageAlt:"girl face with sketch effect and rainbow effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=sketch-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Sketch Yourself!",gtmValue:"4"}}],fh={description:"<p>Turn a photo into a sketch online with PicsArt’s four Sketch Effects! </p>",title:"Photo to Sketch in One Tap",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/54898889434921926227.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=sketch-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Start Sketching Now!",gtmValue:"1"}},yh="sketch_effect",bh=!0,vh=function(){return(vh=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},kh=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=hh,n=gh,a=fh,i=yh,s=bh;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,vh({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"One of the most prominent new trends in"," ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/photo-editor",className:"inline-link",target:"_blank"},"photo editing")," is sketch. You can take any photo of yourself — or anyone — and create a sketch for an artistic effect. How does it work? The Sketch Effect automatically detects the outlines of your portrait and instantly transforms your photo, saving you a lot of drawing time. Try it on your selfies or with friends and family for a fun, trendy, and modern edit. Take any portrait image and turn it into a masterpiece in just one tap.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Turn Your Photo to Sketch ",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},wh=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose from thousands of designer-made templates or start one from scratch."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Instantly upload your own images or choose from millions of free-to-edit images."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Simply drag-and-drop your images into your chosen template."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Customize the colors, fonts, and images until you’re happy with your design."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Save your image and share on social media."}]],Ph=[{description:"<p>You can easily design fun photo collages using one of PicsArt’s bank of free professional templates and layouts. It’s the best way to show off your artistic skills, too! You can choose to make a virtual mood board, which is basically a mish-mash of all the things you love, and doesn’t have to have a particular theme or color scheme. If you love it, add it to your online mood board. You can have tons of mood boards for all your different moods and aesthetics. If you love Polaroids (do they ever go out of style? We think not), you can create a cute retro collage using one of our many fabulous backgrounds. This would also make the most adorable virtual birthday card for your bestie. Basically, as you can see, you can do a lot with our Collage Maker — so start gathering your pics and do it! </p>",title:"Check Out These Cool Collage Ideas!",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/320332661524201.png",imageAlt:"girls photo collage with butterfly stickers out of cup",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s photo Collage Maker lets you decide what  kind of collage you want to make. You can use grids, frames, or go freestyle if you’re feeling more experimental. There are no rules or mistakes when it comes to making collages, so go with where your creativity takes you. Pick one of our grids for an easy start or go with a frame with various themes like birthdays, love, geometric, colorful, and more. For the freestyle option, you can choose up to 10 images and play around with their placements. Move them up, move them down, twist them, turn them — do what looks good to your unique eye. </p>",title:"Photo Collages With Grids, Frames or Freestyle — Take Your Pick!",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/320332661181201.png",imageAlt:"boy and curly hair girl photo collage with green leaf sticker and clouds",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Family reunions, weddings, birthdays, or a Summer party, PicsArt’s photo collage editor has templates for every occasion and can help you tell your story effortlessly. Every time you have a special occasion, pop into PicsArt to find the perfect template to show off your good times. Going back to school? We have tons of fitting frames. Getting married? Check out our romantic Save the Date templates. When you’re done creating your fabulous collage online, share it with the world on Instagram, Facebook, or Twitter to  get all the “Likes.”  </p>",title:"Relive Memories and Share With Others!",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/320332661485201.png",imageAlt:"girl walking in desert in summer photo collage with butterfly stickers",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>To spice up your designs, you have access to <a href="/search" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="awesome-free-to-edit-stickers-and-images-hypertext">PicsArt’s awesome free-to-edit stickers and images.</a> Don’t let them just sit there, use them on your photos to make them look even cooler and cuter! Thanks to the ever-growing library of over a 100 million picks, you can find just about anything you’re looking for, from your favorite celebrity, hobby, or embellishment. Just type a keyword in the search bar and you’ll be sure to find the sticker you’re looking for. Should you not find what you’re after, you can even create custom stickers by cutting them out from pictures already in your phone. That means you can even <a class="inline-link" href="/sticker-maker" target="_blank" data-test="create-a-sticker-of-yourself-hypertext">create a sticker of yourself.</a> How cool is that?</p>',title:"Access Millions of Free Images and Stickers",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/320332661337201.png",imageAlt:"girls photo collage with butterfly stickers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>The best part about our Collage Maker is that it doesn\'t take professional design skills to dress up your images. It’s so easy that a two-year-old can even work it? Ok, maybe not, but you know what we mean! With our <a class="inline-link" href="/photo-editor" target="_blank" data-test="free-photo-editor-hypertext">free Photo Editor</a>, you can add photos, stickers, and text to any shot to make it even better. Or use ready made picture frames and a variety of photo grids to come up with the perfect design and instantly wow your friends. </p>',title:"Free Editing Tools to Impress",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/320332660537201.png",imageAlt:"green eye makeup photo collage with text and sticker",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>With PicsArt's collage frames and templates, anyone can create a stunning mashup in seconds.  Forget complex editing softwares, our collage creator is made for everyone from selfie fanatics to artists to bloggers to business owners. It’s so easy to work with, you can even play around during your coffee break.</p>",title:"Fast and Easy for Everyone",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/320332661229201.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl photo collage with star stickers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>No matter the memory, our free collage editor has you covered. Need to create a birthday card or a wedding invite? No problem! Want to show off your best selfie or create a product ad for your small biz? We have that too. Browse all our pic collage templates below: Birthday, Family, Love, Christmas, Wedding, Baby, Travel, Sport, Fashion and many more! </p>",title:"Perfect for Any Occasion",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/320332661408201.png",imageAlt:"vacation sea photo collage of a girl",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Cool Collage",gtmValue:"8"}}],Eh="collage_maker",xh={description:"<p>Easily create the coolest collages using your favorite photos and our free Collage Maker.  </p>",title:"Collage Maker: Tons of Templates and Photo Frames ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/75170397259906550454.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=collages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage Now!",gtmValue:"1"}},Th=!0,Ah=function(){return(Ah=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Nh=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=wh,n=Ph,a=xh,i=Eh,s=Th;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Ah({screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}},a)),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s online Collage Maker is here to help you bring your A-game to photo editing. Photo collages are so much fun to make because they bring together all your favorite things — all in one place. Whenever you’re feeling sad or down, you can just look back at your snazzy collage creation of your best friends or your celebrity crushes and get an instant smile.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a Picture Collage",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Oh=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open PicsArt’s Editing Tools."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Select which tool you’d like to use."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Upload your image or choose from our free-to-edit options."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Select a filter and apply it to your image."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Adjust and blend your image until your desired result is achieved."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],_h=[{description:'<p>Sketch Effects is one of our most popular online photo effects that has been making rounds all over social media. Quickly <a href="/photo-effects/sketch" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="turn-your-photo-into-a-sketch-hypertext">turn your photo into a sketch</a> by simply uploading it - we’ll take care of the rest. With PicsArt’s Editing Tools, you can adjust the thickness of the sketch line, change its color, and placement. This cool photo effect will visually elevate any image, so start sketching! </p>',title:"Outline Your Photo With Sketch Effects",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/32113863971958232591.png",imageAlt:"girl face with glasses with sketch effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=sketch-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Apply Sketch Effect!",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>A simple filter for your picture can make a significant difference in your final result.   PicsArt’s Light Effects tool offers a wide range of filters and photo effects that will completely transform your images. From soft grunge aesthetic all the way to more vivid and bold color filters, browse through them all and apply them to your photos! You can later adjust the level of fade, brightness, saturation, and contrast of the selected filter to create a more captivating image. </p>",title:"Add Cool Photo Effects With PicsArt’s Light Effects",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/68753773780999138573.png",imageAlt:"white flower in the field",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=lut-filters",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/PWIXiZ7it8",label:"Apply Light Effects!",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Color Toning is one of those steps that people tend to gloss over, but if you want your photos to have a uniformed and stylistic look, then it’s super important that you include it in your photo editing process. Do you want your image to be more vibrant or a little more on the pale side? With PicsArt’s Color Toning tool, you can choose between warm pink/orange color filters to liven up your image or choose cool blue/green tones to create a more mellow aesthetic. PicsArt produces your selected tone by mixing your color with different levels of grey. It reduces the colorfulness but the hue of the image remains the same. </p>",title:"Color Toning: An Essential Step in Your Photo Editing",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/32658936069112369720.png",imageAlt:"",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-toning-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/PWIXiZ7it8",label:"Start Color Toning!",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>PicsArt has simplified the art of <a href="/photo-effects/double-exposure" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="double-exposure-photography-hypertext">double exposure photography!</a> Combine two photos into a single image to create a remarkable composition. Choose two photos you’d like to combine and simply upload them. This cool photo effect will effortlessly combine your images. You can use our Editing Tools to adjust and blend the two images. Also, make sure you apply free photo filters as well.</p>',title:"Two Is Better Than One: Introducing Double Exposure",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/34098214976685855406.png",imageAlt:"black and white photo of a boy with double exposure effects",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-exposure",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/d6DaOiijt8",label:"Try Double Exposure!",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Want the double exposure picture effect but with a single image? You can easily achieve this with our Color Exposure tool. PicsArt will automatically superimpose a second layer of your original image. All you have to do is apply a filter for your picture and start editing! Choose from the various color filters to apply to your image. The contrasting effects will create a stand-out image, full of dynamic elements.</p>",title:"Get Creative With Color Exposure ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/73507871707033999490.png",imageAlt:"girl with hat on with double exposure effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=color-exposure",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/d6DaOiijt8",label:"Try Color Exposure!",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>PicsArt’s Pixel Stretch Effect allows you to stretch out your pixels to create a rainbow-like effect in your images. This tool works great with images full of vibrant and striking colors. After uploading your image, you are presented with the option to stretch out the colors either horizontally or vertically. Choose to which side and at what angle you want your colors to be stretched at. As soon as you’re happy with the result, continue editing your image with <a href="/editing-tools?source=landing_pages" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="our-editing-tools-hypertext">our Editing Tools.</a> You can further blend your original image and the stretched layer to achieve a more cohesive look. Or, increase the contrast so the stretched layer becomes more prominent. This unique online photo effect is perfect for your social media visuals!</p>',title:"Pixel Stretch Effect ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/58727342445929056943.png",imageAlt:"short hair girl with pixel stretch effect",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=runout",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/7J3EAshkt8",label:"Apply Stretch Effect!",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>The quickest way to turn your photos into art is with our Magic Effects. With over 30 unique styles to choose from, you’d be surprised at how many stunning colors and design possibilities there are. Crushed Marble, Rose Quartz, Dystopia, Moonlight, Stay Gold, and Neo Pop are just the tip of the iceberg. Give your pictures the magic touch they deserve with our online photo effects. </p>",title:"You’ll Believe in Magic When You See Our Magic Effects",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/35748987167187812396.png",imageAlt:"curly hair girl face with magic effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=magic-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/tRtW2ntjt8",label:"Start Making Magic!",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:"<p>Like the name suggests, Duotone is  the simultaneous use of two contrasting colors. Duotone photography increases the tonal range of a grayscale image and produces something with a slight tint, adding to the dynamic range of the duotone image. For dramatic online photo effects, it’s best to use two contrasting colors; for something more subtle, you can play around with two subdued hues. </p>",title:"Double Tones With Duotone",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/17408466149015101477.png",imageAlt:"happy short hair girl photo with duotone effect before after",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=duotone",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/ywXEz7Gjt8",label:"Try Duotone!",gtmValue:"9"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Rainbow Filters are a unique blend of all the colors of the rainbow. These vibrant online photo filters will add color to your favorite images. You can choose a specific hue, or one of our more ombré-like effects that incorporate many colors in one filter. With over 40 rainbow filters in our color Photo Editor, you will surely find the perfect blend for your image. </p>",title:"Color Your Images With Rainbow Filters",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/85846784440429051801.png",imageAlt:"girl looking right photo with rainbow effect before after",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=rainbow-effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/NbJgCRVjt8",label:"Apply Rainbow Filters!",gtmValue:"10"}},{description:'<p><a href="/image-overlays" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="photo-overlays-hypertext">Photo Overlays</a> are a great way to add dimension to your images. You can choose from various light flares, bokeh effects, and different textures to apply to your pictures. These online photo effects are very popular on social media, so be sure to try them out! You can further adjust the overlays by changing the opacity, color, and positioning of the new elements added to your image. </p>',title:"Add Beautiful Masks To Your Images With Photo Overlays ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/32410847613448275555.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl face with photo overlays",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=overlays",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JQLh3p7jt8",label:"Apply Photo Overlays!",gtmValue:"11"}}],jh={description:"<p>With PicsArt’s unique photo effects and filters, there is no limit to what you can do to achieve vibrant and striking images.</p>",title:"PicsArt’s Online Photo Effects Will Liven Up Your Dullest Pics",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/75284329050819376208.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/wVWLgnvxn8",label:"Start Editing!",gtmValue:"1"}},Sh="photo_effects",Ch=!0,Rh=function(){return(Rh=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Ih=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Oh,n=_h,a=jh,i=Sh,s=Ch;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Rh({isPremium:s},a,{screenName:i,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Photo effects and filters are the perfect way to elevate the visual elements and the overall aesthetic of your images. Vibrant colors, subtle shadows, enhanced details - you can achieve all of this with our online filters. If you’re looking for something a little more dramatic, our online photo effects will do the magic for you. PicsArt offers all the necessary tools for you to express your imagination and vision, and apply it onto a digital canvas.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How To Add Photo Effects",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Uh=[[{index:1,pointLabel:"Upload your video",pointDescription:"Drag and drop your video or simply click the upload button to start editing."},{index:2,pointLabel:"Trim your video to the duration you want",pointDescription:"Move the sliding arrows around the segment you want to save and click Apply."}],[{index:3,pointLabel:"Download output video",pointDescription:"The output video will be the same format as the original upload."}]],Mh=[{description:"<p>Quickly shorten your videos with just a few clicks. Our video trimmer delivers fast results - shortening your overall editing time. You can trim a video online in less than 2 minutes.</p>",title:"Fast Video Cutting",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/47925247281186294074.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_trimmer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Trim a video",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Go no further than your browser to make video edits. Cut videos online for a fast and productive outcome. You don’t have to download or install any additional software.</p>",title:"Directly in your Browser ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/15192110269218114915.jpg",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_trimmer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Trim a video",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Our free video cutter supports the most popular video formats. Upload videos in MOV, MP4, AVI, WEBM, FLV, and other formats. </p>",title:"Multiple Video Formats",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/94859121003263972271.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_trimmer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Trim a video",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p> Our video cutter is very easy to use. You don’t need to have any prior editing experience. With the Video Editor’s intuitive interface, you can easily navigate through the various tools and settings. </p>",title:"Easy-to-Use Interface",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/43409111346428474277.jpg",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_trimmer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Trim a video",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Trim videos online completely free of charge. Professional video editing software can be very expensive. Save your money for other important investments.</p>",title:"Completely Free ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/69981593789118885101.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_trimmer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Trim a video",gtmValue:"6"}}],Wh={description:"<p>Easily trim and cut videos directly in your browser</p>",title:"Optimize Videos With Our Online Video Trimmer ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/25966908924846190502.jpg",imageAlt:"boy snowboarding",bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_trimmer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Trim Your Video",gtmValue:"1"}},Dh=!0,Fh="video_trimmer",Lh=function(){return(Lh=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Vh=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Mh,n=Wh,a=Fh,i=Dh,s=Uh;return It(a),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Lh({screenName:a,isPremium:i},n,{isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s online video cutter allows you to segment your videos and keep the necessary footage. Quickly trim videos online in your browser without the hassle of relying on expensive and complicated software. Upload your video to our"," ",l.a.createElement(Re,{target:"_blank",href:"/video-editor",className:"inline-link","data-test":"online-video-editor-hypertext"},"online Video Editor")," and cut the unnecessary parts out. PicsArt supports numerous video formats, including MOV, MP4, AVI, WEBM, and FLV. The user-friendly interface allows you to easily navigate through the various tools. Select video trimmer and adjust the sliders around the section of the video you would like to keep. Once you’ve reached the desired video length, simply click Apply. Your video will be ready in seconds! Download the output and start sharing across your channels.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:r,screenName:a,isPremium:i,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Video Trimmer - The Perfect Tool for Online Business",description:l.a.createElement("p",null,"Whether you’re a freelancer, run a small online business, or manage social media accounts, working with videos is an inevitable part of today’s online landscape. Videos convert more people, have higher engagement rates, and people share them more via social media channels. Although creating videos seems like an intimidating and complicated task, it doesn’t necessarily have to be that way. PicsArt’s Video Editor is packed with features. With easy-to-use tools like our online video cutter, you get to define the scope of your video projects yourself, then trim and optimize them. A short video with a smaller file size would be perfect for your website, blog, and your social media channels like Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, and YouTube.")}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Trim a Video Online",data:s}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},zh={editingStepsData:[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload the image you want to retouch. "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Open the Photo Retouch tool to get started."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Click on the specific tool you would like to use on your image. Tap as many tools as needed. "}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Let AI edit your image and customize by adjusting the settings. "},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download your final image."}]],landingData:[{description:"<p>The handy Blemish Remover tool takes care of erasing small marks and flaws in your selfies and portraits. Whether it’s a scar, mole, pimple, or anything else you’d like to make vanish, all you have to do is tap on the blemishes to let our AI technology work its magic. There is no limit to how many blemishes you can erase in our beauty editor, so keep tapping until you’re finished. The result will surely impress and create a more flawless image. </p>",title:"Blemish Remover",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/95659228177815832543.png",imageAlt:"girl image before and after having blemishes",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/n7SUyrNot8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Our Wrinkle Remover does the job of locating the wrinkles on your face and automatically gets rid of them. Whether smile lines or forehead wrinkles, the AI-powered tool gets to work in seconds. If you’re not happy with its work, you can get even more wrinkles removed by scaling up the fade option. Scale down for a more subtle job. Once you’re done with this selfie editor feature, your photos will be ready to be spotlighted on social media.</p>",title:"Wrinkle Remover",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/56701776004840932595.png",imageAlt:"happy girls image with special effects",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/EwN8XGGpt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Should you experience annoying red eyes in your photos, fret not because PicsArt’s Photo Retouch tool has a quick and painless way to get rid of your problem in seconds. Our Red Eye Remover locates all the red eyes in your photos and gets to work to fix them. All you have to do is confirm that the small circles are around your red eyes and tap once. You can even choose to do the work of dragging the small circles around your red eyes yourself. Once the job is done, there won’t be a red eye in sight. </p>",title:"Red Eyes Remover",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/17350419056802830366.png",imageAlt:"boy image before and after having red eyes",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/n3oYyfOpt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Want to change your hair color without making the permanent commitment? That’s where PicsArt’s Hair Color Changer comes in. Just run your photo through our smart tool to give yourself a quick and easy virtual makeover. From red to black to blonde to silver to green and many more colors, you can go as simple or as bold as you wish. The best part about PicsArt’s Hair Color Changer is that it gives you a completely natural appearance, so you won’t get an awkward hairline. Once you’re done, post your new makeover to your social media feed for feedback.</p>",title:"Hair Color Changer",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/83394517250314365243.png",imageAlt:"purple hair girl image",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TovgGFVpt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>Always wanted blue or green eyes? Now with PicsArt’s Eye Color Changer in our Photo Retouch tool, you can get it in seconds! The tool does the job of locating your irises, then allows you to play around for as long as you want. Try out an endless variety of colors available, and adjust the opacity, saturation, and hue for even more personalization. Go as subtle or as bold as you wish and don’t stop until you achieve the result you’re looking for. With PicsArt’s Eye Color Changer, you can achieve a new eye color without ever having to deal with annoying colored lenses again.</p>",title:"Eye Color Changer",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/82947909635320057916.png",imageAlt:"blond hair green eyed girl smiling",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/xXOH8z4pt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Teeth Whitening tool is super easy to use and saves you lots of money on teeth whitening kits. Just upload a photo in which you’re showing your not-so-pearly whites and let the AI-powered technology instantly get to work to whiten your teeth. If you’re not happy with the intensity of the color, you can choose to tone it up or down for a more natural approach. This tool is so fun and addictive, you’ll soon be (virtually) whitening all the teeth in your selfies.</p>",title:"Teeth Whitening",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/64773062521485820323.png",imageAlt:"happy boy with white teeth",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/v6PAPWcqt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Photo Retouch tool features a fancy Face Editor from which you can alter the shape of your face, nose, lips, eyes, and eyebrows. It’s up to you how subtle or dramatic you want to go. Dial things up or down depending on your preferences. Get a slimmer or wider face, a longer or shorter chin, a smaller or more prominent nose, fuller or thinner lips, thicker or thinner eyebrows, bigger or smaller eyes, and more. Within the Face Editor, you can even access the Eye Bag Remover tool. It automatically does it for you or to get an even more flawless fix edit it yourself. Play around for as long as you want and post your final masterpiece to social media. </p>",title:"Face Editor",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/36347974498625004699.png",imageAlt:"summer girl holding a flower and smiling",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/rbhELikqt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:"<p>As part of PicsArt’s Photo Retouch toolkit, the Reshaping tool allows you to change the proportions of any feature on your face to get a completely transformed makeover. You can refine, reduce, enlarge, or restore any part of your face in seconds. Play around for the perfect look and go as subtle or as dramatic as you wish.</p>",title:"Reshaping",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/91040698626298007717.png",imageAlt:"short hair green eyed girl image",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/ZRiEqYpqt8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"9"}}],bannerData:{description:"<p>Photo retouching doesn’t have to be complicated — PicsArt’s Photo Retouch tool does the work for you!\n</p>",title:"Retouch Photos With PicsArt for Flawless Shots Every Time",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/64956390716962112948.png",imageAlt:"red hair happy girl image with special effects",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/dyl0hMhot8",label:"Retouch Photo",gtmValue:"1"}},screenName:"retouch"},qh=function(){return(qh=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Bh=zh.editingStepsData,Hh=zh.landingData,Yh=zh.bannerData,Gh=zh.screenName,Xh=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Gh),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,qh({},Yh,{screenName:Gh,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s photo retouch game is strong and painless. Our easy-to-use Photo Retouch tool will help you enhance portraits and selfies before posting on social media. The smart AI-powered tool features a blemish and wrinkle remover, hair and eye color changer, teeth whitening, face reshaping, and more unique attributes. The face editor allows you to smoothen skin; alter face shape, nose, eyes, lips, and eyebrows; and even remove pesky eye bags. Any time you need a flawless shot, retouch your photos online with PicsArt in a few minutes. Then try more impressive ",l.a.createElement(Re,{className:"inline-link",target:"_blank",href:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages","data-test":"editing-tools-hypertext"},"editing tools")," in our ",l.a.createElement(Re,{className:"inline-link",target:"_blank",href:"/photo-editor","data-test":"photo-editor-hypertext"},"Photo Editor")," to personalize your edits.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Hh,screenName:Gh,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Retouch Photos",data:Bh}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Qh=function(){return(Qh=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Kh=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your images and videos."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Organize your content and sequence it."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Trim, resize, and add music to your video."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Don’t forget to add text throughout your video."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download the output video and start sharing!"}]],$h=[{description:"Promo videos are a great way to grow your business and increase your online presence."},{description:"Easily increase your brand awareness and reach new audiences with promo videos."},{description:"Promote your products, services, and events you’re organizing with the help of promotional videos."},{description:"Engage more customers by targeting your audience online."},{description:"Use promo videos on your website, app preview, social media channels, ads, emails, and more."},{description:"Customers can share your videos on social media channels."}],Jh=[{description:"<p>To effectively promote your business, you will need to pinpoint the audience you intend to reach and define the message you want to deliver. A well-thought-out video concept coupled with the necessary tools to execute your vision will ensure great results for your business. Promo videos will help increase your sales, drive engagement, and act as a tool to help you convert new customers. PicsArt’s tools are easy to use and make the overall editing process much easier and quicker.</p>",title:"Define the Purpose and Target Audience of Your Promo Video",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/01754021285755868693.png",imageAlt:"adding milk in caffe latte",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Create Promo Video ",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>You want to showcase what you have on offer in the best possible way. Whether you’re promoting a new product, a service, an event you’re organizing, or increasing awareness for a certain cause, the content of your video should be compelling enough to evoke action in your viewer. Promo videos are the perfect format for grouping your images and video footage into cohesive and entertaining content. Make your promo videos easily stand out from your competitors by making them unique and colorful.</p>",title:"Come Up With a Unique and Compelling Script",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/72214098379131924198.png",imageAlt:"breads and bakery store - man is adding final ingredients on a bread",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Create Promo Video ",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>The length of your video plays a large role in keeping the attention of your viewer. You don’t want your video to be too long, where the viewer gets bored, and you don’t want it to be too short either. With our video trimmer, you can easily trim your video to its perfect length. Depending on your goals, you can make longer videos for your website, and shorter videos for your social media channels. You can even resize your videos for specific social media channels, like Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, Twitter, Snapchat, and others. This way, your content will fit perfectly in your posts without cropping the sides.</p>",title:"Determine the Right Length and Size of Your Promo Video",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/68693850002035442973.png",imageAlt:"happy girl with headphones is recording a song and playing guitar",bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Create Promo Video ",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>Music is a great accompanier to promotional videos. Luckily, PicsArt offers a large library of stock music. Browse through our library to find the perfect track that suits your video. You will find music of different genres, various tunes and beats to add to your promo video. <a href="/add-music-to-videor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="adding-music">Adding music to your videos </a> will help them become more memorable to your audience. The right song will evoke all of the necessary emotions in your viewer and motivate them to take action on your website, social media channel, email, ad, or wherever you choose to incorporate your videos.</p>',title:"Add Music to Your Promo Video",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/12720521537641078809.png",imageAlt:"ballet teacher is showing dancing moves to little ballet dancers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Create Promo Video ",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>Easily <a href="/add-text-to-video" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="adding-text-to-video">add text</a> to your promo videos with PicsArt’s video editing tools. Adding text throughout your video visually amplifies the message you are trying to convey. You can add important keywords to your video, subtitles, short explainers, and call to action phrases throughout your content. People are visual learners, and process information better when visual cues are present. Tactically placing text throughout your video will help your audience follow your message and take away the important information you are providing.</p>',title:"Place Text and CTA’s Throughout Your Promo Video",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/60931539619712855403.png",imageAlt:"man with a hat on is doing selfie while feeding a monkey on his shoulder",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Create Promo Video ",gtmValue:"6"}}],Zh={description:"<p>PicsArt’s promo video maker will help you create standout content for all your marketing efforts.</p>",title:"Create Captivating Promo Videos for Your Business",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/04509532808404671258.jpg",bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Create Promo Video ",gtmValue:"1"}},eg="promo_video",tg=!0,og=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(eg),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Qh({screenName:eg,isPremium:tg},Zh,{isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"If your business intends to promote its products and services to a larger audience, then promo videos are a great way to start! Promotional videos are an excellent way to engage your audience, introduce them to your numerous offerings, and get them to convert right on the spot. You can use promo videos directly on your website, in your email marketing campaigns, video ads, as well as social media channels. PicsArt’s",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/video-editor",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"automatically-video-editing"}," Video Editor "),"provides you with all the necessary tools to create dynamic and eye-catching content.")}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{title:"Make Promo Videos That Sell",isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Jh,screenName:eg,isPremium:tg,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{title:"Why You Need to Start Making Promo Videos",isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Ya,{featuresData:$h,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{title:"How to Make a Promo Video",data:Kh,isAmp:o}))},rg=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your picture or choose one from our #FreeToEdit images."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Choose the Resizer tool from the Tools page."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Type in your desired width or height to resize your image."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],ng=[{description:"<p>The better question would be, “Why not use PicsArt’s picture resizer?” Whenever you need to change an image size, just turn to our online photo resizer. It’s completely free and only takes a few seconds to get your image to the size you need. Once you know your desired width and height, type it into the Resize Image pop-up that will appear and the tool will do the rest for you. All that’s left to do next is approve the resizing, then save it to your profile or upload it privately to your phone. </p>",title:"Benefits of Using a Photo Resizer",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/28827760645649206624.png",imageAlt:"short hair girl with glasses and red coat is posing",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>If you decide to change the size of your images without a photo resizer, you run the risk of the final result being poor quality. With PicsArt’s online photo resizer, you’re guaranteed to get high resolution images that are ready to be spotlighted on your social media channels and website. When it comes to showcasing imagery that’s nothing short of stunning, changing your image size with PicsArt’s resizer — and simultaneously keeping the quality as high as possible — is a no-brainer. You can even utilize our handy <a href="/image-upscale" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="image-upscaler-hypertext">Image Upscaler</a>, which allows you to enlarge your image without sacrificing its quality. </p>',title:"Always Get High-Quality Images",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/18490673487295966449.png",imageAlt:"boy with summer hat on standing in the port",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>Did you know that resizing photos can ensure that your web pages load faster? The last thing you want is for customers or clients to become frustrated with your website speed. To prevent slow performance, use PicsArt’s photo resizer to make sure that all your images are the correct size. Your website will remain relevant and user-friendly, just the way it should be. To achieve different sized images for various pages of your website, you can use our <a href="/crop-image" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="crop-tool-hypertext">Crop tool</a> to size your photos down in just seconds. </p>',title:"Resizing Makes Web Pages Load Faster",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/63338884424097897946.png",imageAlt:"blond hair gril with round hat on and in black sweater with stripes is standing back beside the lack",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>One of the most popular uses of our free photo resizer is for social media profiles. Whether it’s for Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, or YouTube, PicsArt can accommodate your specific needs. And there is no limit to how many images you can resize with PicsArt’s online photo resizer. So if you’re promoting a single image across all your social media channels, just change the size with our photo resizer in a few taps. Make your YouTube banner photo pop, resize any photo for Instagram “Likes,” and give your Facebook cover photo an instant upgrade. After working with PisArt, your image will definitely stand out among a sea of competitors. </p>",title:"Use Image Resizer to Spruce up Your Social Media",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/53183867712971613389.png",imageAlt:"two twin red and white roads spliting",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>To go along with your blog posts, you’ll need beautiful, high-resolution imagery that captures the essence of your copy. The two go hand in hand, so use PicsArt’s free online photo resizer to ensure that the look and quality of your blog posts will be top notch. Your readers will take notice. For cluttered backdrops, you can use our <a href="/background-remover" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="background-remover-hypertext">Background Remover</a> tool to create a more appealing aesthetic. Then, when it comes time to promote the blog posts on your social feeds, you can easily change the size of your images in our picture resizer. </p>',title:"Make Better Blogs",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/07522992889480260755.png",imageAlt:"healthy breakfast plate with strawberries, blueberris and banana",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>Your best memories deserve the best treatment. For those extra special images that require printing and hanging on the wall, you can easily use our free photo resizer to get the correct size you need without sacrificing its resolution. Whether it’s a romantic anniversary photo, an epic birthday shot, or an adorable pet portrait, fine tune the look with our picture resizer before sending it to the printer. </p>",title:"Prep For Printing ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/24635148899055793772.png",imageAlt:"long hair skater boy jumping on a skate beside a pink and green background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"7"}}],ag={description:"<p>PicsArt’s photo resizer can quickly change the size of any picture in a few clicks.</p>",title:"Resize Images Easily and Quickly With PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/76401650806129843422.png",imageAlt:"girl with glasses and in denim posing beside a colorful wall",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=photos",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/aqe6SX5lt8",label:"Resize Image",gtmValue:"1"}},ig="resize_image",sg=!0,lg=function(){return(lg=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},cg=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=rg,n=ng,a=ag,i=ig,s=sg;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,lg({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"With PicsArt’s online photo resizer, you have the ability to resize images easily and quickly within our",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/photo-editor",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"all-in-one-photo-editor-hypertext"}," all-in-one Photo Editor.")," There is no photo that we can’t resize. All you have to do is choose the image you want to resize and change its dimensions within our Resize tool. Type in your desired width or height, and the Resize tool will make the right adjustment for you without ever sacrificing the resolution quality. It’s that simple.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Resize Your Image With PicsArt’s Resizer Tool",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},ug=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your video."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Click on the “Format” button."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Select which social media format you’d like your video to fit into."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Apply formatting."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Download the output video and start sharing!"}]],pg=[{description:'<p>Quickly resize videos directly in your browser. You don’t have to learn how to use complex <a class="inline-link" target="_blank" href="/video-editor" data-test="video-editing-software-hypertext">video editing software</a> to achieve professional-looking content for your social media channels. </p>',title:"Fast Video Resizing",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/13210973334373628463.jpg",imageAlt:""},{description:"<p>Our online video resizer supports the most popular formats. Upload videos in MOV, MP4, AVI, WEBM, FLV, and more. We don’t limit you to just one format. </p>",title:"Multiple Video Formats Supported",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/97496516415030213401.jpg",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:""},{description:"<p>Our online video resizer is very easy to use. Create custom videos for each social media platform, without spending hours on editing. You’ll have your content ready in no time!</p>",title:"Easy-to-Use Interface",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/66235342018860345323.jpg",imageAlt:"",bgPosition:"bgToLeft"}],dg=[{description:"<p>What works for one social media channel may not necessarily work for another. Platforms like Instagram, YouTube, and Facebook have different requirements when it comes to optimal video dimensions. To avoid having your video cropped and reduced at the edges, we present to you our video resizer that can easily change the dimensions of your videos without cropping out any of your material. PicsArt offers optimal sizing for Instagram stories and posts, Facebook stories and posts, as well as YouTube videos. You can easily resize your video online by simply selecting the format of your choice. You can optimize the same video for all social media formats. This way, when you’re ready to go live with your video, you can share each optimized video to its respective social media channel. The best part is that our online video resizer can resize videos both horizontally and vertically. Your Facebook and Instagram stories have never looked so fit.</p>",title:"Resize Videos for Social Media ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/28433458737789537458.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Resize Video",gtmValue:"2",url:"/create/video/?referrer=resize_video&tool=fit"}},{description:'<p>You can resize a video within minutes. With just a few clicks, your videos can look perfect for all social media channels. You can even use these videos in your blog or website. Easily resize to 1:1 (square), 16:9 (horizontal),  9:16, and 4:5 (vertical). It is true that tampering with dimensions could potentially affect your overall video quality, but, the best part about our online video resizer is - you don’t! Additionally, our easy-to-use Video Editor provides an intuitive layout for you to edit your videos without any difficulty. Upload your video in MOV, MP4, AVI, WEBM, FLV, or other formats and get straight to editing. You can <a class="inline-link" target="_blank" href="/trim-video" data-test="trim-your-video-hypertext">trim your video</a> to your desired length and easily fit it to the dimensions you want with our video resizer. This tool is perfect for small business owners, bloggers, social media managers, and freelancers who create promotional content, tutorials, and quick how-tos. Producing social media content is not an easy task. PicsArt offers the necessary tools for you to succeed in your promotional efforts and make the whole process more fun!</p>',title:"Simplify Your Editing Process With Our Video Resizer ",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/36859796455276761041.jpg",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Resize Video",gtmValue:"3",url:"/create/video/?referrer=resize_video&tool=fit"}}],mg={description:"<p>Instantly resize videos and change dimensions with this quick tool. </p>",title:"Adjust the Size of Your Videos Using PicsArt’s Online Video Resizer ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/61429107066560758315.jpg",imageAlt:"girl holding a flower",bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Resize Video",gtmValue:"1",url:"/create/video/?referrer=resize_video&tool=fit"}},hg="resize_video",gg=!0,fg=function(){return(fg=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},yg=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=ug,n=pg,a=dg,i=mg,s=hg,c=gg;return It(s),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,fg({},i,{screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:a,screenName:s,isPremium:c,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Benefits"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{isAmp:o,productData:n}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Resize a Video",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},bg=[{description:"<p>Easily create promotional videos for your business. Boost your conversion rates, increase engagement, and build credibility with your customers. Our Video Editor is perfect for coffee shops, cafés, beauty salons, showrooms, and other small businesses. </p>",title:"Small Businesses",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/08578490788080964092.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Edit Your Video",url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_editor",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Create content for your social media marketing efforts. PicsArt’s online Video Editor allows you to quickly resize and fit your videos for various social media channels. Create content specifically tailored for Instagram, YouTube, and Facebook. </p>",title:"Social Media Managers",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/12237488261897213320.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Edit Your Video",url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_editor",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>You don’t need a large budget to promote your work. Create professional-looking videos from home with PicsArt’s online video maker. This tool perfectly suits freelancers like photographers, real estate agents, private trainers, bloggers, yoga instructors, foreign language tutors, and others. </p>",title:"Freelancers ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/70017717821527298925.jpg",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Edit Your Video",url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_editor",gtmValue:"5"}}],vg=[[{index:1,pointLabel:"Upload your video",pointDescription:"Drag and drop your video or simply click the upload button to start editing."},{index:2,pointLabel:"Edit and add effects ",pointDescription:"Experiment with various tools and effects. This Video Editor is simple and full of versatile editing tools."}],[{index:3,pointLabel:"Download output video ",pointDescription:"Once you’ve finished editing, export your video and save it to your computer."},{index:4,pointLabel:"Share your video ",pointDescription:"Upload your video to various social media channels, website or blog, and start sharing!"}]],kg=[{description:"<p>This free Video Editor requires no prior editing experience. Make videos directly in your browser with PicsArt’s intuitive and flexible video editing tools. </p>",title:"Easy-To-Use ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/24737727328906555554.jpg",imageAlt:""},{description:"<p>Cut your editing time short and produce content at a faster rate with PicsArt’s online Video Editor. You can make a creative and impressive video in as little as 3 minutes. </p>",title:"Fast Results",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/55159225666965097886.jpg",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:""}],wg=[{description:"Add titles, subtitles, and descriptions to your videos with the help of our text tool. Choose from many special fonts and text styles to apply to your videos. ",title:"Add text to videos"},{description:"Choose the perfect song from our library of licensed stock music, or simply upload one from your computer. ",title:"Add music to videos"},{description:"Insert animated transitions to gradually move from one scene to another. Experiment with our large selection of Video editor effects. ",title:"Animated transitions"},{description:"Easily resize your content for Instagram posts and stories, YouTube, and Facebook. Simply click on the format you would like to work with and continue applying our Video editor effects until you’re satisfied with the final result. ",title:"Resize video"},{description:"Cut and trim your footage to achieve the perfect video. You can effortlessly adjust the duration and order of your video tracks to achieve the sequence you’re looking for. ",title:"Trim video"},{description:"Browse through our endless catalog of free-to-edit images that you can use in your videos. ",title:"Free-to-edit Images "}],Pg=[{description:"<p>Videos are a great way to promote your brand, products and services. In fact, having videos on your website significantly reduces bounce rates. Visitors stay on your website longer, which could potentially lead to higher conversion rates for you. With PicsArt’s Video Editor, you can create short and informative videos that will represent your brand better than words ever could. Create stunning product visuals with the help of our video editing tools. </p>",title:"Promote Your Business",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/20604997917699539307.jpg",imageAlt:""},{description:"<p>Grow your social media presence with unique and consumer-oriented visuals. Using videos for social media channels results in increased interaction with content. Videos are also a great way to present important information in a concise manner. Because the social media landscape moves very quickly, you and your team will have to be able to produce content at a fast pace. This could mean posting 3+ videos a week to keep up with competition. With PicsArt’s free Video Editor, you can easily make videos, edit them, and fit them to specific social media channels. You will save yourself and your creative team hours of editing time. </p>",title:"Increase Your Social Media Presence",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/01013816170187408652.jpg",imageAlt:""},{description:"<p>Do you need to create videos for personal projects or freelance work? If the answer is yes, then our free Video Editor is the perfect tool for you. Whether you are working on a school project, running a blog, or teaching courses, you will find that this simple Video Editor will cover all of your creative needs. Layer your visuals with text and don’t forget to add music. The Video Editor’s intuitive interface makes it very easy-to-use. You don’t need to have any prior knowledge of professional editing software. Simply upload your video, and start editing!</p>",title:"Personal Projects ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/44517611434575732872.jpg",imageAlt:""}],Eg={description:"<p>A simple Video Editor equipped with professional-grade editing tools.</p>",title:"Create and Edit Videos With PicsArt's Online Video Editor",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/99821917752222169791.jpg",bgImage:!0,lightText:!0,buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",url:"/create/video/?referrer=video_editor",gtmValue:"1"}},xg="video_editor",Tg=!0,Ag=o(79),Ng=o.n(Ag),Og=function(){return(Og=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},_g=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=bg,n=vg,a=Pg,i=kg,s=wg,c=Eg,u=xg,p=Tg;return It(u),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Og({},c,{screenName:u,isPremium:p,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Benefits"}),l.a.createElement(kr,{className:Ng.a.productsContainer,productData:i,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,buttonProps:{label:"Try Quick Tools",mobileLink:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",link:"/create/video/?referrer=video_editor",gtmValue:"2",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Web Video Editor!",subscribeId:19,className:"promotionAction",secondary:!0,screenName:u,isPremium:p}}),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,titleClassName:Ng.a.promotionTitle,title:"PicsArt’s Video Editor Perfect For"}),l.a.createElement("div",{className:Ng.a.perfectForCarousel},l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o},r&&r.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement("div",{key:t},l.a.createElement(pr,Og({screenName:u,isPremium:p,isAmp:o},e,{creativeBg:!0})))})))),l.a.createElement(Ya,{isAmp:o,featuresData:s}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Edit a Video",data:n}),l.a.createElement("div",{className:Ng.a.perfectForCarousel},l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o},a&&a.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement("div",{key:t},l.a.createElement(pr,Og({isAmp:o,creativeBg:!0},e)))})))),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},jg=[[{index:1,pointLabel:"Pick",pointDescription:"You’ve already chosen the best online Photo Editor, now choose the photo you want to edit."},{index:2,pointLabel:"Upload",pointDescription:"Bring your image over to our editor and click automatic sizing for posts or stories."}],[{index:3,pointLabel:"Edit",pointDescription:"Apply the perfect filter, like Rainbow Filters for that instant glow, Double Exposure to make it pop, or Magic Effects for a surreal vibe."},{index:4,pointLabel:"Share",pointDescription:"Every feature is fully customizable, so adjust the levels until it's perfect!"}]],Sg=[{description:'<p>Can’t find the right image to create the edit you have in mind? Just take a look through our endless <a href="/search" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="image-and-sticker-library-hypertext">image and sticker library.</a> You never know what you might find that will give you that spark of inspiration you’ve been needing. You’ll even surprise yourself with what you’re able to pull off with a lot of handy tools and a little creativity!</p>',title:"A World of Content and Inspiration",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/07021166135608562862.jpg",imageAlt:"blond hair girl sketch effect",buttonProps:{url:"/create",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",label:"Try Photo Editor",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>If editing is your favorite activity, then PicsArt is your creative playground. All you need to make amazing things happen is our awesome photo editing toolkit! We’ve taken complicated photo editing tools and simplified them, so all kinds of <a href="/editing-tools?source=landing_pages" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="fancy-editing-tools-hypertext">fancy editing tools</a> are accessible to anyone looking to tap into their creative side. Adding masks, layers, filters and magic effects to your photos is now just as easy as applying a filter.</p>',title:"A Full Set of Tools",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/35387279048172835137.jpg",imageAlt:"happy girl with modern yellow background",buttonProps:{url:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",label:"Try Photo Editor",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Into photography? Take your pictures and use our impressive editor to make them look even more stunning. Love all things vintage? Use our beautiful vintage backgrounds, filters, stickers, and templates. Want to explore the galaxy? Scroll through the images and stickers in our outer space community. Or make images your own by adding personalized text, fonts, stickers, and photos!</p>",title:"Customize Anything",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/58011396729498114716.jpg",imageAlt:"girls with butterfly wings photo effect",buttonProps:{url:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",label:"Try Photo Editor",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>More tools do NOT mean more complications! With PicsArt’s Photo Editor, you can edit pictures like a pro, without any hassle. Our high-end features are designed to leave your photos looking smoothly retouched — no professional experience needed. Drag and drop in a flash, switch through projects effortlessly, and make images your own in just one click!</p>",title:"A Simple Process With a Professional Outcome",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/78188758273834129942.jpg",imageAlt:"girl in fields with duotone effect",buttonProps:{url:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",label:"Try Photo Editor",gtmValue:"5"}}],Cg=[{description:"Use your all-in-one editor for free – no strings attached!",title:"Free forever"},{description:"Create professional-looking photos in minutes",title:"Advanced tools"},{description:"Millions of photos, stickers, templates and other content",title:"100+ million images"}],Rg=[{description:'<p>Add a layer of awesome to your photos. With our <a href="/photo-effects" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="online-photo-effects-hypertext">online photo effects</a>, you can take your pictures to a whole new level and feel like a professional photo editor! Whether you’re looking for a soft vintage vibe, a bold feel, or want to dabble with our Distortion tool, PicsArt has made it super easy for you to start. Just click on the filter that best fits your mood and you’re all set!</p>',title:"Photo Effects & Filters",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/318500952269201.png",imageAlt:"bronze filter of a man before after",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=effects",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",label:"Try Effects",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:'<p>If you’ve added the perfect filter and you still need more, just search through our endless library of stickers! From emojis to your favorite food and celebrities, we have it all. Find the clipart you need, select the one you want, and then layer it on. Or take it to the next level by <a href="/sticker-maker" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="creating-your-own-custom-stickers-hypertext">creating your own custom stickers.</a></p>',title:"Sticker Maker",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/318500952429201.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"colored hair happy girl with flamingo and colorful stickers",buttonProps:{url:"/create/background-remover",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9?component=cutout",label:"Make Stickers",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:'<p>At PicsArt, we give you a vast library of <a href="/images" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="free-to-edit-images-hypertext">free-to-edit images</a> so you have everything you need to make the best edits. With our content library that we constantly keep adding to, you’ll never have a shortage of images.</p>',title:"Free-To-Edit Content",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/318500952383201.png",imageAlt:"girl with green leaf and colorful star stickers ",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/images",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9?chooser=photo&directory=fte",label:"Get Inspired",gtmValue:"9"}},{description:'<p>With our <a href="/collage-maker" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="collage-maker-hypertext">Collage Maker</a>, you can pick your best shots to create awesome, shareable memories in a flash. Choose from one of our preset collage formats or create your own design. If you want even more design inspiration, try out one of our hundreds of templates — perfect for any occasion. We’ve done the hard work for you; all you have to do is add your favorite photos!</p>',title:"Collage Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/318500952359201.png",imageAlt:"sharp mask image of girls with neon stickers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/collage-maker",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/jXpDGQ7kt8",label:"Create a Collage",gtmValue:"10"}},{description:'<p>Use PicsArt’s online image editor to show people what you have to say. <a href="/text-editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="customize-your-text-hypertext">Customize your text</a> with our massive font library. Our Text Editor helps you choose and even animate the font that best suits your photo, aesthetic, and mood.</p>',title:"Fonts for Days",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/318500953003201.png",imageAlt:"strong sticker on a colored hair girl image",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9?component=text",label:"Have Fun With Fonts",gtmValue:"11"}},{description:"<p>Retouch your selfies with our advanced Beautify tool. Our special technology detects your facial features in a flash, so you can easily find your way around the image editor. Add to your beauty, enhance your best features, try out new hair colors, and turn your face into a canvas!</p>",title:"Beautify",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/318500953002201.png",imageAlt:"pink hair girl face edited with beautify effect",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9?component=beautify",label:"Enhance Yourself",gtmValue:"12",productMetaTitle:"Get Early Access to PicsArt Beautify!",subscribeId:7}},{description:'<p>This is for all those times you’ve had a funny meme idea but didn’t know <a href="/meme-generator" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="how-to-make-memes-hypertext">how to make memes.</a> With PicsArt, making memes is a piece of cake. Don’t just laugh at other people’s memes, become a content creator, too!</p>',title:"Meme Generator",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/318500951223201.png",imageAlt:"cat meme with omg text and background",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/meme-generator",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/2McSBhOkt8",label:"Make a Meme",gtmValue:"13"}}],Ig={description:"<p>Our Photo Editor is insanely good — and it’s at your fingertips!</p>",title:"Online Photo Editing Has Never Been so Easy",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/75221377491263861300.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",label:"Try Photo Editor",gtmValue:"1"}},Ug="photo_editor",Mg=function(){return(Mg=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Wg=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Sg,n=Rg,a=Ig,i=jg,s=Cg,c=Ug;return It(c),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Mg({},a,{screenName:c,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Ya,{isAmp:o,featuresData:s}),l.a.createElement(nn,{isAmp:o},r&&r.map((function(e,t){return l.a.createElement("div",{key:t},l.a.createElement(pr,Mg({imageToRight:e.imageToRight,buttonProps:e.buttonProps,description:e.description,imageUrl:e.imageUrl,imageAlt:e.imageAlt,screenName:c,title:e.title,isAmp:o,creativeBg:!0},e)))}))),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,title:"Tools You Need to Win the Editing Game",description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Whatever it is that you need in your online editing toolkit, we have you covered. Don’t like the colors in your photo? Choose one of our Color Effects like Duotone, Double Exposure, Color Toning, or Rainbow Filters to amp it up. Want a more dramatic look? Try an out-of-this-world Magic Effect. You can even use our Background Remover or Changer to set your picture in any scene you want: nature, a big city, the beach, Mars, you name it. Try our easy sizing options to crop your image for any of your other social accounts. With our free online Photo Editor, you get instant edits in seconds."),buttonProps:{mobileLink:"https://picsart.app.link/5NE80Z4gs9",gtmValue:"6",label:"Try Quick Tools",link:"/editing-tools?source=landing_pages",secondary:!0,screenName:c}}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:c,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Edit the Perfect Photo Online",data:i}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Dg=function(){return(Dg=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Fg=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open the Poster Maker tool."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Upload your own image or use one from our #FreetoEdit library."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Edit any design details using our Editing Tools."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Download your online poster."}]],Lg=[{description:"<p>Professional posters are a fresh way to get your message out into the world. Whether you’re announcing a new product or service, a special event, or a new class, let PicsArt’s Poster Maker help you out with the design details. You don’t need any professional experience or skills to get your online poster done in minutes. The best part is that you also don’t need to spend a penny to create something special. Make an online poster with PicsArt for your social media channels, blog, or website. You can also choose to print your one-of-a-kind custom poster to share it at your office or shop.</p>",title:"Design Professional Posters Online",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/84270222623702321664.png",imageAlt:"tropical party with dj poster design template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Customization is key when it comes to creating something truly outstanding for your business or brand. At PicsArt, we’ve done all the designing for your online poster needs, now all you have to do is personalize with our easy-to-use editing tools. Design unique posters using your brand colors, beautiful fonts, fun stickers, effects, backgrounds, icons, and more. Incorporate your own images into your online poster or pick a photo from our extensive #FreetoEdit library. Each of our online tools is intuitive and simple, so you don’t have to spend hours figuring them out. Just click on the tools you’d like to use, then make any changes to reflect your brand’s signature aesthetic.</p>",title:"Customize Posters for Your Brand",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/44078997100995096459.png",imageAlt:"new season spring/summers sales poster design template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>At PicsArt we understand that creating a professional online presence is important. Presenting sleek, eye-catching content will help you stand apart from a sea of competition. Online posters are one way to achieve an expert look in your industry, whether you’re using it to announce a new product, an upcoming event or class, or anything else pertaining to your business. PicsArt’s Poster Maker makes it easy to stand out because it offers up the best online editing tools to help you create something that will impress your audiences on social media and beyond.</p>",title:"Online Posters Lend a Professional Look",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/94244215382607920193.png",imageAlt:"summer pool party poster design template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>When creating an online poster, you can upload your own image to get started or you can choose a photo from our extensive #FreetoEdit image library. With millions of assets available to you at no cost, there is no limit to what you can create with PicsArt. We have high-quality images for any topic under the moon, so when creating your online poster, you’ll have no shortage of options to choose from. If you can’t think of an image to use for your custom online poster, just turn to PicsArt for all the inspiration you need.</p>",title:"Use Our #FreetoEdit Image Library for Your Online Poster",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/87200468312869845679.png",imageAlt:"pop art poster design template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:"<p>If you’d rather not create a custom online poster from scratch, turn to PicsArt’s handy poster templates designed by our talented team to help your brand stand out. Pick from hundreds of easy-to-use poster templates in a variety of designs and colors, then personalize your pick using our easy-to-use editing tools. From simple to bold, we’ve got a style that will match your brand’s signature look. Love a template but want to edit a few details? Not a problem. All of our templates are fully customizable at any time. </p>",title:"Try Poster Templates Designed by PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/47428374180487390795.png",imageAlt:"fashoin show poster design template",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"6"}}],Vg={description:"<p>With our online Poster Maker, your online content will stand out with custom posters that you can share on social channels and beyond. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Poster Maker Is Convenient and Customizable",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/05737859783682991454.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=poster",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Create Poster",gtmValue:"1"}},zg="poster_maker",qg=!0,Bg=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(zg),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Dg({},Vg,{screenName:zg,isPremium:qg,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"PicsArt’s Poster Maker will give you a head start on creating your custom poster for social media, websites, blogs, and printing. Design a poster for your business or brand with the help of our easy-to-use editing tools. Create posters online from the convenience of your own home and spend nothing to get it done right. Share announcements, events, and new products or services with eye-catching custom posters specially made by PicsArt. Then personalize the look of your professional poster to fit your needs.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Lg,screenName:zg,isPremium:qg,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Make a Poster Online",data:Fg}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Hg=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload an image or choose from PicsArt’s stock images."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Add your heading, subheading, and body."},{index:3,pointDescription:"Choose a font for your text."}],[{index:4,pointDescription:"Pick a color for your letters."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Apply shadows or an outline to your text."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Download your work."}]],Yg=[{description:"<p>Imagery is a powerful tool. However, language can be just as important and impactful. Our online Text Editor is a great way to add texts onto images — whether it’s an inspiring quote, your brand slogan, or a funny phrase. Everything from simple to fancy fonts, designs, and customizations - we've got you covered. With a photo Text Editor, you will be able to give more meaning and context to your edits. All the tools you need to make your message stand out can be found here. </p>",title:"Why Text Editor?",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/59907096938772746327.png",imageAlt:"urban future text on a skyscraper building",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Add Text to Your Pics!",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s Text Editor comes with a large library of custom fonts. Choose from hundreds of unique and free fonts to give your texts more personality. From bold and chunky lettering to soft, cursive, and fancy text fonts, you will find the visual representation of your voice. Don’t underestimate the importance of a good font. Create images with text to improve the effectiveness of promotional activities on your website and social media. Just think of all the brands that stand out just due to their fonts. </p>",title:"Custom Fonts",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/14051729633918504299.png",imageAlt:"victory text on a photo of a man sitting at the top of the rock",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Add Text to Your Pics!",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>Having difficulty deciding what your paragraph or sentence should look like? Luckily, we have a bunch of pre-designed templates for you. All you have to do is choose the one you like the most. Make sure to check the left panel of the Text Editor for small previews. This will help you easily navigate through the different styles. Typography matters when it comes to the readability of your text. Spacing is also an important aspect of text structure people tend to overlook. With PicsArt’s Text Editor you can easily write on images and adjust your leading, kerning, and tracking for more precision in layout. </p>",title:"Text Designs",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/87630650582721178653.png",imageAlt:"you are perfect text on a photo of a blond hair girl with black glasses",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Add Text to Your Pics!",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>You have full creative control over your words. Add shadows to your letters for dramatic effect. Borders and contouring will make your texts stand out. Make sure to choose  unique colors for your texts. Since colors convey certain emotions, choose them wisely. You can interweave your sentences in front of, behind, and around objects. There are so many ways you can play around with our free online Text Editor. For example, we really like the idea of your favorite quote or words <a href="/photo-effects/sketch" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="creating-an-outline-of-your-selfie-hypertext">creating an outline of your selfie or portrait.</a> You can even layer your preferred words on top of yourself for something artsy. There are no mistakes or rules when it comes to adding texts on photos. When you have something to say, write on your pictures and add texts on your photos to take your favorite images from silent to stand-out.</p>',title:"Shadows, Borders, Contours, Colors ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/42878522739635107414.png",imageAlt:"say it with style text on a green leaves image with blue background",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Add Text to Your Pics!",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>Set and edit backgrounds for your texts with <a href="/photo-editor" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="PicsArt-photo-editor-hypertext">PicsArt’s Photo Editor.</a> We provide all the necessary tools for you to edit your images like a pro. Choose from a range of unique filters and <a href="/add-stickers-to-photos" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="creative-stickers-to-add-to-your-images-hypertext">creative stickers to add to your images.</a> If you want to be more minimalistic, simply play around with the colors and tones of your pictures. Nothing is off-limits. As soon as you’re done editing your image, start adding text to your photos. There are many design techniques you can use to make your text pop. You can blur or darken your image so the letters stand out more. Visually, this creates a nice contrast and your text will be right under the spotlight. Adjust the size of your text. Larger text grabs more attention compared to smaller text. This way, you can emphasize the important parts of your content. If you have an empty space in your image, use that area to place your text. This will make it more visible and readable to your audience. </p>',title:"Don’t Forget to Edit Your Photos",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/21295889661306491117.png",imageAlt:"stay cool text on a photo of a man with black glasses",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Add Text to Your Pics!",gtmValue:"6"}}],Gg={description:"<p>Everyone has a story to tell. Put your thoughts into words with our Text Editor.</p>",title:"Speak Your Mind by Adding Text to Photos",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/36102596020674394974.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=text",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/kcNNVmvkt8",label:"Try Text Editor Now!",gtmValue:"1"}},Xg="text_editor",Qg=!0,Kg=function(){return(Kg=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},$g=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Hg,n=Yg,a=Gg,i=Xg,s=Qg;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Kg({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Add Text to an Image",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Jg=[{description:'<p>One of the best ways to add dimension and individuality to your social media visuals is by adding stickers to photos. Your posts will automatically become more lively and eye-catching! PicsArt offers a <a href="/stickers" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="large-library-of-stickers-hypertext">large library of stickers</a> — from cute stickers like hearts and kisses, to holiday-themed stickers, emoji stickers, and even stickers of your favorite movie and television characters. To make navigation easier, you’ll see many sticker hashtags that are popular at the moment. Once you’ve found your perfect sticker, simply click on it and start editing! </p>',title:"Free Stickers for Your Social Media Content ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/39071795160907491196.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl with cactus, heart, avocado and cut stickers ",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Start Adding Stickers",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>You don’t have to be a graphic designer to make quality content for your business. In fact, using stickers can save you both time and resources. You can find free stickers online for absolutely any occasion. If you’re making social media posts for the holiday season or any other thematic occasion, simply input your search query and PicsArt will provide you with thousands of cute stickers. Add the stickers to your photo and start editing your work. You can adjust the opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast of the sticker, as well as its size and positioning. You have full creative control over what you want your work to look like. You will surely be able to find the sticker you are looking for in PicsArt’s extensive library. Stickers are great for complementing and elevating your designs, as well as provoking thoughts and feelings in your audience. </p>",title:"Add Stickers Online and Improve Your Designs ",bgPosition:"bgToRight",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/10275268677457221048.png",imageAlt:"man on the boat with meduza stickers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Start Adding Stickers",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>PicsArt not only allows you to add stickers to your images but you can <a href="/sticker-maker" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="make-your-own-stickers-hypertext">make your own stickers</a> too. Create custom stickers, add them to your images, or use them for later. To create your own sticker, simply upload the image of your choice, our AI will automatically detect the background of the image and remove it for you, and you’ll have your foreground object ready and waiting. Your new sticker will be saved in PNG format on a transparent background. You can use this tool to create clipart of your company logo, products, slogan, etc. The possibilities are endless. Custom stickers are a great way to promote brand awareness. Start making them <a href="/create/remove-background" class="inline-link" target="_blank">here.</a> </p>',title:"Customize Photo Stickers for Your Needs",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/43920898567833906133.png",imageAlt:"girl pouring water on the cup with rose stickers",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Start Adding Stickers",gtmValue:"4"}}],Zg={description:"<p>Discover a huge library of photo stickers.</p>",title:"Add Stickers to Photos to Level Up Your Content",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/88120741574757948585.png",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=stickers",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TLdg4uKit8",label:"Start Adding Stickers",gtmValue:"1"}},ef=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your image or choose from our free-to-edit collection "},{index:2,pointDescription:"Search for stickers"},{index:3,pointDescription:"Adjust the opacity, saturation, brightness, and contrast of your sticker"},{index:4,pointDescription:"Smooth out edges with the Eraser tool"}],[{index:5,pointDescription:"Flip it around or rotate it around its axis."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Adjust the positioning of the sticker."},{index:7,pointDescription:"Add many, many more stickers to your image."},{index:8,pointDescription:"Download your created image."}]],tf=!0,of="add_to_sticker",rf=function(){return(rf=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},nf=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=ef,n=Jg,a=Zg,i=of,s=tf;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,rf({},a,{screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isPremium:s,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Add Stickers to Photos",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},af=function(){return(af=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},sf=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload an image to use as a backdrop or choose from one of our #FreetoEdit images to begin."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Personalize the look by adding text, effects, stickers, and more."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Once you’re done, download the flyer to your computer."}]],lf=[{description:'<p>The best part about PicsArt’s Flyer Maker is that it’s so intuitive and easy to use that you’ll know your way around it even if you’ve never designed anything before. Even better, every single flyer you create is fully customizable — and it doesn’t take any design experience to get it done. The first step is to pick your perfect background image that will fit the theme of your event or sale. Upload your own image or choose from one of our millions of #FreetoEdit images. For a little extra help, you can choose one of our <a href="/design-templates/flyer" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="designer-flyer-templates-hypertext">designer Flyer templates.</a> Then it’s time for the fun part: personalization. Spend a few more minutes giving your flyer your signature touch with text using over 200 fonts, frames, effects, and more. From start to finish, you’ll enjoy the creative process sans the headache and hefty price tag. </p>',title:"Our Flyers Are All Customizable and Easy to Use",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/85526294431907693553.png",imageAlt:"spring summer fashion show flyer template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make Flyer",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>When designing something worth looking at, it’s a myth that you should hire a professional that will charge thousands of dollars. PicsArt’s free Flyer Maker is proof of that. There are pages and pages of beautiful backgrounds you can choose to start with. Shout your message or event from the virtual rooftops without breaking the bank. With the money you’ll save, you can put it toward getting more supplies or fare for your special affair. We are always adding new tools and effects, so be sure to check back each time you have a new event or sale to promote. </p>",title:"Our Flyer Maker Won’t Cost a Penny",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/12656402557444510328.png",imageAlt:"valentine's day sale flyer template",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make Flyer",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>The main goal of PicsArt’s Flyer Maker is to help you design a high-quality and professional flyer without headaches, so rest assured that no matter which way your design goes, you’ll end up with a top-notch result. Your message and event details will be sleek and stylish with PicsArt. From start to finish, we help you think of every little detail that will make you stand out from the competitors. Once you’re done personalizing your flyer design with our tools and effects, it will be nothing short of impressive. </p>",title:"Create Professional, High-Quality Flyers",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/13896651289029582014.png",imageAlt:"make up models needed flyer template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make Flyer",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:'<p>No matter what you’re trying to publicize, PicsArt’s Flyer Maker is here to help create the look you desire. We even have tons of general <a href="/design-templates" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="design-templates-hypertext">design templates</a> you can start with. Every type of industry professional can take advantage of our Flyer Maker. Whether you’re promoting a new store location, announcing a new chef or menu at your restaurant, throwing an upscale event at a nightclub, or getting the word out about a local charity event, we will inspire you to create a flyer that will appeal to your brand’s aesthetic. Once you’re done, you can change your flyer size accordingly, be it a small online coupon or a large poster. Print it or post it on your social media accounts for maximum exposure. </p>',title:"Make Flyers for Any Purpose and Occasion",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/66155561313678591968.png",imageAlt:"join our yoga class text on a flyer template",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make Flyer",gtmValue:"5"}}],cf={description:"<p>Create custom-made flyer designs for any business or industry. </p>",title:"PicsArt’s Flyer Maker Helps You Promote Your Product in Style",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/15842904208848290037.png",imageAlt:"electro pop party flyer template",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?templateSearch=flyer",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/oFFRNlXkt8",label:"Make Flyer",gtmValue:"1"}},uf="flyer_maker",pf=!0,df=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(uf),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,af({},cf,{screenName:uf,isPremium:pf,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Any time you need to create a stylish flyer to promote your product or service, look no further than PicsArt’s free online Flyer Maker. Instead of paying tons of money for a professional designer, you can design a flyer in no time — that will leave an impression for a long time. Choose a background image to start with — you can upload your own or pick one from our extensive #FreetoEdit library — then take a few extra minutes to customize your template’s look with our unique effects and fonts. With PicsArt’s Flyer Maker, you’re guaranteed a sleek, one-of-a-kind aesthetic that will speak to your customers.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:lf,screenName:uf,isPremium:pf,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create a Flyer With PicsArt’s Flyer Maker",data:sf}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},mf=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Upload your video."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Edit the length of your video, trim specific scenes, and adjust its size."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Add text, images, and music to your videos."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Export your video and start sharing."}]],hf=[{description:"Choose pictures for your videos from a massive library of images. Simply put in your search query and easily add the images to your videos. Our online video maker also offers a library of stock music to upgrade your videos with.",title:"Library of Images and Music"},{description:"Editing videos doesn’t have to take up too much of your time. With our video maker, you can achieve substantial results in as little as 2 minutes.",title:"Fast Results"},{description:"PicsArt’s video maker comes with an intuitive interface. Easily create videos online without the difficulty of learning how to use professional software. All the necessary tools are at your fingertips. ",title:"Easy-to-Use Interface"}],gf=[{description:"<p>You can easily assemble eye-catching slideshows with our video maker. Upload your images, videos, add music and start editing! We provide all the tools you need to create professional slideshow videos.</p>",title:"Slideshows",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/28346094886268607828.jpg",imageAlt:"boy jumping through the lake in sunset",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Create videos for all of your social media channels. You can resize your videos for platforms like Instagram, YouTube, and Facebook. Our video maker allows you to create content in both story and post format. </p>",title:"Social Media Videos",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/77468920618713422116.jpg",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s video maker is the perfect tool for creating presentation videos. Easily add text, videos, and images to your presentations to get your message across.</p>",title:"Presentation Videos",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/41779149433041104670.jpg",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Create exceptional promo videos for your business. You can make videos that will help your products/services stand out. Put your best features on display and build your brand with our video maker. </p>",title:"Promo Videos",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/96074017686460269457.jpg",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"5"}}],ff=[{description:'<p>With PicsArt, you can create videos that are engaging, memorable, informative, and cohesive. Videos are the perfect way to further promote your business and your marketing efforts. Our video creator is equipped with all the necessary tools to make your videos stand out. You can quickly trim your video, adjust its size and length, add images, text and music. You can choose pictures from our extensive <a href="/images" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="image-library-hypertext">image library</a> to add to your videos. In addition to our image library, PicsArt also offers a large library of stock music. This way, you can easily enrich your content by finding the perfect track that complements your videos and messages. As a final touch, add text throughout your video to make your message more prominent.</p>',title:"Make Videos for Your Business",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/07887472487435331807.jpg",imageAlt:"girl getting her nails done",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:"<p>Real estate agents can benefit greatly from using videos to showcase listings. Ask any marketing professional, and you will be convinced that creating videos on a regular basis has a great return on investment. Videos are powerful visual tools, and surprisingly, not as popular in this specific industry. Easily differentiate yourself from your competitors by creating videos for houses and apartments – showing details that could be interesting to your buyers. PicsArt’s easy video maker will help you achieve stunning results. </p>",title:"Create Videos Online for Real Estate",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/31776479278333160291.jpg",imageAlt:"houses near the greenery",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"7"}},{description:"<p>Simple product shots don’t do the trick anymore. Consumers are much more educated and aware of their purchases, therefore, detailed explanations and showcases of products are essential to your online business. With video, you can dive deep into your product descriptions and put all of your differentiating factors on display. You can create explanatory videos, slideshows, and videos that show consumers how to use your products. PicsArt’s video maker facilitates the process of video creation and editing. You can achieve professional-looking edits with its easy-to-use tools.</p>",title:"Upgrade Your E-Commerce Business",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/82018984059287135224.jpg",imageAlt:"food photography",bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"8"}},{description:"<p>Educational videos are perfect for teachers and instructors of various fields. Regardless of the age group you are teaching, videos can drive your message home, and can aid your students in fully comprehending the topic you are discussing. With PicsArt’s online video maker, you can create educational videos that are entertaining and informative. Our tools allow you to add images and subtitles to your videos without any hassle . You can also create impressive slideshows and presentations that you can later send out to your students. You don’t have to be a professional to create exceptional videos. PicsArt makes this process easy and enjoyable.</p>",title:"Create Videos for Educational Purposes",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/10235381891728413693.jpg",imageAlt:"woman throwing stock papers",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"9"}}],yf={description:"<p>Easily create videos for your social media, promotions, presentations, and more.</p>",title:"Create Videos for Your Business With PicsArt’s Online Video Maker",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/22834634539458894540.jpg",imageAlt:"boy taking a photo in sunset",bgImage:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/video/",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/Sw1HvRaEocb",label:"Make a Video",gtmValue:"1"}},bf="video_maker",vf=!0,kf=o(80),wf=o.n(kf),Pf=function(){return(Pf=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Ef=mf,xf=hf,Tf=gf,Af=ff,Nf=yf,Of=bf,_f=vf,jf=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Of),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Pf({screenName:Of,isPremium:_f},Nf,{isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Videos are an essential part of the current media landscape. More and more businesses are opting to promote themselves through video content as opposed to just using simple images. With PicsArt’s online video maker, you can easily create professional-looking content like slideshows, presentation videos, social media videos, stories, and promotional videos. This free video maker allows you to easily "