ith a solid white background (this is important later)."},{index:5,pointDescription:"Position the sticker over the lower half of your edit and apply the “lighten” blend mode. This is the exciting part: when the edit really comes together."},{index:6,pointDescription:"Add halo crown, neon, paint splatter, and/or star stickers until you’re happy with the end result."}]],Lb=[{description:"<p>One of the coolest things about the drip art selfie trend with PicsArt Replay is that it takes a simple selfie or portrait to totally new heights — all in a matter of seconds! And the best part is that it’s so artistic and impressive that it’ll look like you spent hours on it. Run any of your selfies through our PicsArt Replays dedicated to the drip effect trend and you’re sure to get lots of adoring comments. You can choose to customize your drip art selfie even further to make it even more standout. You can add all the editing steps we recommend or you can skip any step that doesn’t go with your aesthetic. Then add even more fun by layering on our unique effects, stickers, backgrounds, and fonts.</p>",title:"The Drip Art Selfie Will Make You Pop",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/42407470871148147433.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/get-the-app",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/SSJtZ1CuI5",label:"Try Drip Art",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>It’s never been easier to achieve a complex edit in seconds than with PicsArt Replay. Your hardest task will be to pick the best selfie or portrait to work with. Once you do, upload it in the editor in-app or our web editor, then tap through each step to add it to your image. With our drip art selfie Replays, the first step involves removing the backdrop of your photo with our <a href="/background-remover" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="background-remover-tool-hypertext">Background Remover tool</a>. But don’t worry, you don’t have to do anything but click and our Artificial Intelligence does it for you. Then for the fun part, continue with each editing step to add the eye-catching designs to your selfie. You can either choose to accept the designs in each step or you can skip it if it’s not your thing. </p>',title:"It’s SO Easy to Achieve",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/70111112688245834193.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/get-the-app",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XhMUKVTnt8",label:"Try Drip Art",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>If you’re in the position to influence through social media, it’s important to always stay on top of the latest photo editing trends. The drip art selfie is the perfect way to show your audience and fans that you can create something inspirational and beautiful. It’s up to you if you want to let them in on your secret: that it didn’t take hours. In a matter of seconds, you can come out with a stunning drip art selfie that will take your basic photos to new heights with PicsArt Replay. To personalize your look even further, add one of our <a href="/photo-effects" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="trendy-photo-effects-hypertext">trendy photo effects</a> that will speak to your signature aesthetic. \n</p>',title:"Drip Art Selfies Are Perfect for Influencers ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/03443662782556035754.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/get-the-app",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/vBhy04tuI5",label:"Try Drip Art",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>The fastest and easiest way to create something artistic is with PicsArt’s drip art selfie Replays. Take any portrait and give it major pizazz by following a few easy editing steps that will transfer to your photo. The dripping paint effect in the drip art selfie trend adds a unique look on its own, but with all the other design details we have created for you, the result is nothing short of awesome. Your drip art selfie will definitely make your social media ooze with artistic flair.</p>",title:"Drip Art Selfies Give Instant Artistic Flair",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/22157812746788202149.png",imageAlt:"",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/get-the-app",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XhMUKVTnt8",label:"Try Drip Art",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>Speaking of standing out, with any social media feed, be it a professional or personal page, it’s ideal to create something one-of-a-kind so that it reflects your unique style. PicsArt’s drip art selfie Replays help you do just that — stand apart from the crowd. And it’s so easy to do in a few steps that you can use it to liven as many selfies and portraits as you wish. Personalize things even more by using our impressive <a href="/editing-tools?source=landing_pages" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="editing-tools-hypertext">editing tools</a> within our <a href="/photo-editor" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="photo-editor-hypertext">Photo Editor.</a> </p>',title:"Drip Art Selfies Will Make Your Socials Stand Out\n",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/86290026253756942437.png",imageAlt:"",buttonProps:{url:"/get-the-app",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/vBhy04tuI5",label:"Try Drip Art",gtmValue:"6"}}],Vb={description:"<p>Drip art is fast and easy to achieve with exclusive Replays featuring the drip effect.</p>",title:"Get in on the Drip Art Selfie Trend With PicsArt",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/50532011395294916249.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl face on a blue background with drop art effect",buttonProps:{url:"/get-the-app",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/XhMUKVTnt8",label:"Try Drip Art",gtmValue:"1"}},zb="drip_art",qb=function(){return(qb=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Bb=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Fb,n=Lb,a=Vb,i=zb;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,qb({},a,{screenName:i,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"The ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/blog/post/how-to-get-in-on-the-drip-art-selfie-trend/",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"drip-art-selfie-hypertext"},"drip art Selfie")," continues to blow up all over social media feeds around the world. Want to get in on the",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/hashtag/drip",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"drip-effect-hypertext"}," drip effect")," craze? The easiest way is with ",l.a.createElement(Re,{href:"/replay-image",target:"_blank",className:"inline-link","data-test":"PicsArt-replays-hypertext"},"PicsArt Replays.")," You can create the perfect selfie art with Replays we’ve created just for the popular drip art trend. And we’ve made it super easy for you to use. This PicsArt exclusive feature allows you to recreate awesome edits on your own photos by going through each step on tap at a time. You can accept all the editing steps we have designed for you or opt to skip any steps that don’t speak to your style. In a few seconds and a few taps, you’ll have the perfect drip art selfie to spotlight on your socials. They’ll definitely turn heads and get all the “Likes.”")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create a Drip Art Selfie",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Hb={editingStepsData:[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Open the photo editor and choose one of your own photos or scroll down to “Free Photos” and search for the perfect photo."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Start editing your image by going through each Replay step."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Save your Replay edit and share it with the world."}]],landingData:[{description:"<p>There are many reasons why once you try Replay, you’ll be instantly addicted, but the main one is that it’s beyond easy to follow and the results are so worth it. It only takes a few taps — and mere seconds — to create a Replay that’s so stunning, you won’t be able to wait to share it with your friends and fans. It’s as simple as clicking “Next” a few times to follow the one-tap editing steps.</p>",title:"It Only Takes a Few Taps to Create Beautiful Images",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/22472029567443160476.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl with black glasses and butterflies",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:'<p>Every single day, you can find a brand-new Replay on PicsArt. That’s 365 different Replays that you can use on your simple images to give them an entirely new look. If you’re ever in a creative rut, all you have to do is look to Replay to instantly inject excitement into your edits. <a href="/hashtag/replays" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="PicsArt-replays-hypertext">PicsArt Replays</a> are so one-of-a-kind, they’ll open up a whole new world of creativity and inspiration for you! You won’t ever regret using Replay to up your editing game. </p>',title:"Find Inspiring New Replays Daily",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/81669796445338835217.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl face in a frame and around statues",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:'<p>With each Replay you use on your images, you’re simultaneously discovering new design aspects that are trending in the creative world around you. Perhaps you didn’t realize that you can instantly edge up any photo with our <a href="/blog/post/dispersion-photo-effect-picsart-photo-editor/" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="dispersion-tool-hypertext">Dispersion tool.</a> Or maybe you’ve been wanting to spice up your portrait or selfie but don’t know where to begin. This is when Replay comes in handy to lend an artsy hand that will make your edits look up-to-date. </p>',title:"Discover a Whole New World of Editing",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/36272280452970080758.png",imageAlt:"blue eyed girl face in a frame with flowers",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"4"}},{description:"<p>Even the most avid PicsArt user can sometimes miss a brand-new tool or feature that just came out. You definitely don’t want to deny your edits like that. One of the best ways to stay up on all things PicsArt is to keep up with Replay on a daily or weekly basis. That way, when a new tool or effect comes out, you’ll be one of the first PicsArtists to use it. What’s more, you’ll learn some cool new tricks for editing that you may not have ever dabbled with before. </p>",title:"Find Exciting Tools and Tricks For Editing",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/28931822823994144335.png",imageAlt:"Girl with summer hat on with sketch effect and pink background",imageToRight:!0,bgPosition:"bgToRight",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"5"}},{description:'<p>With so many holidays to celebrate throughout the year, it’s always fun to give your photos a festive touch. Whether it’s Valentine’s Day, St. Patrick’s Day, Fourth of July, or Christmas, there is a <a href="/hashtag/replays" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="themed-replay-hypertext">themed Replay</a> that will help you get in the mood by duplicating it in just a few steps.</p>',title:"Have Fun With Replay for Holidays",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/28393999110337516099.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl in field around leaves in the air",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"6"}},{description:'<p>While Replay is a pro at providing photo editing tips and guiding you through steps that you can easily apply to your images, there is the option of personalizing your Replay to make it even more you. Just click on the tools at the bottom toolbar to change the look with <a href="/photo-effects" target="_blank" class="inline-link" data-test="PicsArt-effects-hypertext">PicsArt’s effects,</a> borders, frames, and more. It’s up to you how involved and creative you want to get with it. But should you want to stick with the original Replay steps and not tweak them, that works too.</p>',title:"Customize Replays to Your Liking ",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/81055782112324285451.png",imageAlt:"man and woman romantic photo in a blue phrame with background of starts",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"7"}}],bannerData:{description:"<p>For easy photo editing, just go through each step of the featured edit one tap at a time. The result is so aesthetically pleasing, it’ll look like you spent hours on it! </p>",title:"Recreating Trendy Edits Is Easy With PicsArt Replay",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/07668382302872916357.png",imageAlt:"blond hair girl in black dress in field with moons",buttonProps:{qrModal:Wc.picsArt,mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/JJ7v8lslt8",label:"Replay Image",gtmValue:"1"}},screenName:"replay"},Yb=function(){return(Yb=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Gb=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t,r=Hb.editingStepsData,n=Hb.landingData,a=Hb.bannerData,i=Hb.screenName;return It(i),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Yb({},a,{screenName:i,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Replay is an exclusive feature on PicsArt that allows even the most amateur artists to create masterpieces in just a few taps. With each unique Replay, you’ll be able to recreate each photo editing step to add the same tools and effects to your own image. Simply put, Replay is the best way to achieve quick photo editing! All you need to get started is a photo. Then, follow the quick editing steps that have been laid out by clicking through each one. There are usually anywhere from three to five steps in each Replay. Once you’re done, the same edit will be easily applied to your photo. It takes mere seconds to get the look, but is impressive enough to garner lots of “Likes” on social.")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:n,screenName:i,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Create a PicsArt Replay",data:r}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},Xb=function(){return(Xb=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},Qb=[[{index:1,pointDescription:"Choose “Canvas” from Editing Tools on web or from in-app effects."},{index:2,pointDescription:"Tap on the Canvas effect you’d like to try."}],[{index:3,pointDescription:"Click “Shuffle” for more options."},{index:4,pointDescription:"Click “Apply” and save the Canvas edit."}]],Kb=[{description:'<p>The <a href="/blog/post/become-regular-michelangelo-inspiration-renaissance-selfies/" class="inline-link" target="_blank" data-test="renaissance-selfie-trend-hypertext">Renaissance selfie trend</a> has been brewing for some time, but with PicsArt’s Canvas effects, your selfies are about to get cultured on a whole other level. The effect is quick and easy to use, and there is no limit to how many times you can turn yourself into artwork. After each shuffle, the geometric crop of beautiful paintings and sculptures sits over different parts of your face: eyes, mouth, nose, and cheeks. This results in a new masterpiece each time. With PicsArt\'s Canvas Effects, you get eight unique presets. Upload your selfie or choose a free to edit image and let AI apply the effect. You can easily shuffle through different paintings and artwork. Personalize your look by toning the effects down or up, then layer on additional filters, stickers, and backgrounds.</p>',title:"Canvas Effects: Endless Classical Selfies",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/65296523312598845679.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl photo with canvas effect applied",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=canvas-effect",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/OHjBWzAlt8",label:"Try Canvas Effects",gtmValue:"2"}},{description:"<p>Playing your own muse with PicsArt is fast and fun! As soon as you upload the selfie or portrait you want to transform into artwork and click on the effect you’d like to use, our impressive Artificial Intelligence detects your face to map a classic painting or sculpture to the outline of your photo. Each time your shuffle for a new result, the crop can sit over your eyes, mouth, nose, or cheeks. If you’re not satisfied with the first edit you’re presented with, you can simply click the “Shuffle” button as many times as you wish to get a new option until you’re happy. If you don’t love the chosen effect, you can choose to tone it down or up. Then customize things even further by layering on other trendy filters, stickers, and backgrounds. All it takes to transform yourself into a painting is a few taps. </p>",title:"How Does Canvas Effects Work?",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/30728486304119921917.png",imageAlt:"black hair boy photo with canvas effect ",imageToRight:!0,buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=canvas-effect",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/OHjBWzAlt8",label:"Try Canvas Effects",gtmValue:"3"}},{description:"<p>It’s so much fun to take your own pictures to picturesque, but another exciting way to play with PicsArt’s Canvas effects is to try them on your friends, as well as favorite celebrities and musicians. Talk about turning your besties and idols into art muses. You can upload photos of them that you already have on your desktop or search from our millions of #FreetoEdit image library. Personalize things by adding trendy effects, stickers, backgrounds, and text, then share it with your friends or on your social pages. Your friends, and fan art, have never been more cultured.</p>",title:"Use Canvas Effects on Your Friends and Favorite Celebs",imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/63900673546322204978.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl photo with canvas effect on eye",bgPosition:"bgToLeft",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=canvas-effect",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/OHjBWzAlt8",label:"Try Canvas Effects",gtmValue:"4"}}],$b={description:"<p>Morph into a mural and achieve an avante-garde look in a single tap. </p>",title:"Canvas Effects: The Renaissance of Selfies ",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/06423894400788434672.png",imageAlt:"black hair girl photo gace photo with canvas effect on lips",buttonProps:{url:"/create/editor?category=canvas-effect",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/OHjBWzAlt8",label:"Try Canvas Effects",gtmValue:"1"}},Jb="canvas_effect",Zb=!0,ev=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(Jb),l.a.createElement(fn,{isAmp:o},l.a.createElement(Tn,Xb({},$b,{screenName:Jb,isPremium:Zb,isAmp:o,dataTests:{actionButton:"primary-button"}})),l.a.createElement(Hr,{isAmp:o,description:l.a.createElement("p",{"data-test":"description"},"Ready for a Renaissance? Turn your portraits into paintings and selfies into sculptures with one tap by magically transforming part of your face with PicsArt’s cutting-edge Canvas effects. With 8 on web and 4 in-app state-of-the-art effects and over 4,000 classical and baroque artworks available, you can shuffle to achieve a new avant-garde look every time. To customize even further, you can layer on any of our filters, effects, stickers, backgrounds, text, and more. With Canvas effects, it’s easy to become your own masterpiece!")}),l.a.createElement(kr,{productData:Kb,screenName:Jb,isPremium:Zb,isAmp:o}),l.a.createElement(Gn,{isAmp:o,title:"How to Apply Canvas Effects",data:Qb}),l.a.createElement(ha,{isAmp:o}))},tv={promotionData:{description:"Whether you’re new to the editing game or a certified pro — or anything in between — PicsArt’s tight-knit family of editing apps will soon be your favorites. Say hello to all the members: PicsArt Photo & Video Editor, PicsArt Animator GIF & Video, PicsArt Color Paint, PicsArt Video Maker & Movie Editor, PicsArt GIF & Sticker Maker, and PixelArt. Simply put, we’ve got the best free editing apps in the game. There is a cool editing app for every type of person out there. If you want to add trending effects and filters to your photos and videos, turn to PicsArt Photo & Video Editor. If you’re into cartoons, the animation app is perfect for you. Get in on the GIF and sticker game with our PicsArt GIF & Sticker maker app and start creating content worthy of going viral. Pick the PicsArt app that’s right for you and start getting your creative juices flowing today. All you need is a phone, and a desire to have fun and be creative! "},landingData:[{description:"<p>PicsArt is the leading free photo editing app with over 1 billion downloads to date. Spark your creativity with the most popular photo editor app on mobile. PicsArt offers all the editing tools and one-of-a-kind photo effects you need to create awesome edits right from your phone. PicsArt Photo & Video Editor is a photo collage app, video editor, meme maker app, and sticker app all rolled into one. The all-in-one photo and video editor on mobile is also home to the hugely popular Sketch, Canvas, Drip, Glitch, and Magic effects, iMessage stickers, Doodle Art trend, and more. Get access to amazing drawing tools, collage maker, sticker maker, meme maker, high-quality camera, trendy photo filters, and selfie-enhancing Beautify tools. Start with your own picture or choose one from our free image library. Use PicsArt’s impressive Video Editor to bring your best moments to life by adding unique filters and fun stickers to your videos. Upload them to your TikTok page and go viral.</p>",title:{text:{title:"PicsArt",description:"Photo & Video Editor"},logoUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/34664534299086336342.png",buttonProps:Dc.picsArt,additionalButtonProps:Dc.picsArtPhotoStudio},imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/24714096235980601214.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"black hair girl with black glasses photo retro effect applied",buttonProps:Dc.picsArt,additionalButtonProps:Dc.picsArtPhotoStudio},{description:"<p>PicsArt Color is the best free drawing app that allows you to bring out your inner artist. Color, paint, and draw digital illustrations with no limits and no experience required. PicsArt Color is kid-friendly, too, so the whole family can hone their creativity together. Our illustrator app offers a comprehensive drawing suite where you can mix colors, play with different customizable paint brushes, work with multiple layers, use varying blending modes, draw and erase texts, and do so much more. Doodle and paint away or create a digital sketchbook if that’s more your speed. A handy auto-recovery tool ensures that you’ll never lose your hard work. What’s more, PicsArt’s Color features a user-friendly interface so you’ll have less time for headaches and more time for coloring.</p>",title:{text:{title:"PicsArt",description:"Color Paint"},logoUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/57673908360727994569.png",buttonProps:Dc.picsArtColor},imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/90017077673567024829.png",imageAlt:"editing process of image of an owl on a yellow background",buttonProps:Dc.picsArtColor},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s newest coloring app! Creating amazing pixel images is as easy as filling in the number boxes. PixelArt is designed for any experience level, even kids, so get the whole family in on the fun. Get hours of relaxation and fun by using this paint by numbers app. Discover tons of 2D and 3D artworks or create your own pixel art. Access tons of designs that are constantly updated to ensure you’ll never tire of our library of coloring pages. Anyone can find images they’ll love to color with this paint by numbers app. If you have an awesome image you think would look great as a drawing, you can create your own coloring pages by picking photos from your personal gallery. Go over the edges? No problem, our coloring game app will keep you within the borders. Done with coloring one part? Just one tap and you’re ready to progress with another color. When you’re done, just save your final image or video to your library and share it with your friends. Get coloring with PicsArt’s PixelArt app today!</p>",title:{text:{title:"PixelArt",description:"by PicsArt"},logoUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/40089235056484296081.png",buttonProps:Dc.pixelArt},imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/70197171671987641476.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"editing process of a pink butterfly on a black background via pixelart",buttonProps:Dc.pixelArt},{description:"<p>EFEKT Video Maker app by PicsArt layers 20+ unique motion reacting effects over your videos to help you create something truly stunning. Play with cool glitch video effects and distortion video effects. Other popular effects include Dream, Rainbow, Shine, Bubbles, Flame, Displace and more. New effects are added monthly so you’ll never run out of inspiration and ideas for your video edits. Upload clips to the video editor app from your phone or shoot new videos directly from a high-quality in-app camera. Each effect is made to be easily customized with 60+ parameters to fit your specific needs. For added personalization, try interactive objects like shapes, text, and drawings. Access 20+ shapes, 10+ fonts, and an easy-to-use drawing tool that allows you to doodle on specific parts of your edit with your finger. With the audio reactivity feature, effects react to sound both in the in-app camera and imported videos. When the human mode is enabled, you can apply effects on yourself or people around you or on everything but people (this feature only works on iPhone Xs and later). Everything in the EFEKT video effects app works in real-time so it’s possible to play with the controls while recording. Once you’re done, export your full HD videos and share them on Instagram, Snapchat, YouTube, and TikTok. </p>",title:{text:{title:"EFEKT",description:"Video Maker"},logoUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/43481820874473097409.png",buttonProps:Dc.efekt},imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/85106848234977958177.png",imageAlt:"pixelated effect on an image of a black hair girl in a red tshirt",buttonProps:Dc.efekt},{description:"<p>PicsArt Animator GIF & Video is a top cartoon maker app that takes the complications out of animation and makes it completely easy to achieve for any level of experience. The video animator app offers a quick and simple way to create animations right on your phone! Bring your snapshots and sketches to life with moving stickers and doodles, image overlays, sound effects, and more. PicsArt Animator GIF & Video has everything you need to make frame-by-frame cartoon clips and animated GIFs and photos. The possibilities for fun are endless when you use this app to create hilarious videos and cute cartoons. The best part is that you don’t need any experience to dive right in. But more advanced animators shouldn't shy away, as our animation maker app also features impressive comprehensive drawing tools that pros use. Whether you’re animating selfies or sketching cartoons, PicsArt’s animation creator app is the only animation and cartoon-making app you’ll ever need. </p>",title:{text:{title:"PicsArt Animator",description:"Gifs & Video"},logoUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/28128519680872185544.png",buttonProps:Dc.animator},imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/14531925259941263390.png",imageToRight:!0,imageAlt:"image of a drawn boy with black bow waving",buttonProps:Dc.animator},{description:"<p>PicsArt’s GIF & Sticker Maker offers the capability to make awesome animated GIFs and stickers in one app. Why download two apps when you can get away with one? Use the sticker maker app to create fun stickers out of any image! Personalize your GIFs and stickers with trendy effects and filters, speak your mind using text with stylish fonts, and layer on cute animated masks. PicsArt GIF & Sticker Maker is the best GIF maker app out there. We take the guessing game out of creating GIFs and stickers from scratch. Just use the high-quality in-app camera to capture images and videos to get started. Our photo stickers app allows you to work with photos, GIFs, and videos to make something truly one-of-a-kind right from your phone. You can even import your favorite GIFs from Giphy with ease. Share your awesome PicsArt-made GIFs and stickers to your social networks to spotlight your creative side.</p>",title:{text:{title:"PicsArt Gif",description:"& Sticker Maker"},logoUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/66547809990447043627.png",buttonProps:Dc.gif},imageUrl:"https://cdn130.picsart.com/55706539579499110841.png",imageAlt:"happy girl in orange sweater posing on a colorful background with a wow sticker on a photo",buttonProps:Dc.gif}],bannerData:{title:"Meet the Only Editing Apps You’ll Ever Need",imageUrl:"https://cdn140.picsart.com/08388222099365697474.png",imageAlt:"collage of photos with different photo effects applied",buttonProps:{label:"Start Free Trial",url:"/gold",mobileUrl:"/gold",gtmValue:"1",extraSpacing:!0},additionalButtonProps:{label:"Get the App",mobileUrl:"https://picsart.app.link/TIVYc9ZjNu",qrModal:Wc.picsArt,gtmValue:"2"}},screenName:"apps",category:"apps"},ov=function(){return(ov=Object.assign||function(e){for(var t,o=1,r=arguments.length;o<r;o++)for(var n in t=arguments[o])Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(t,n)&&(e[n]=t[n]);return e}).apply(this,arguments)},rv=tv.promotionData,nv=tv.landingData,av=tv.screenName,iv=tv.bannerData,sv=tv.category,lv=function(e){var t=e.isAmp,o=void 0!==t&&t;return It(av,sv),l.a.createElement(fn,{isA